(23, 'Pidgin', 'Terms', '<div><strong>1.1 Welcome to Kaci.</strong> Di following Terms of Use (wey dem go refer to as \"Terms of Use\" afta dis) na part of di agreement between you and Kaci App and WhatsApp/SMS Notification (wey we go call \"Kaci,\" \"we,\" \"our,\" or \"us\"), di people wey dey operate platform wey give you (wey we go refer to as \"you,\" \"your,\" or \"User\") access to our Mobile Application, WhatsApp/SMS Notification and any related services. Di Kaci Mobile Application and WhatsApp/SMS Notification get many waka waka wey include: TravelSafe, Ambulance, Climate, InfoBank, Suggestion, Feedback, SOS, Press Releases and plenty odas. Abeg note say di Kaci mobile application and notification no dey provide security services or ambulance services. If you wan take ambulance service, abeg ask medical professional or government agency wey dey responsible. If any emergency show, you suppose contact di emergency services for your country sharp sharp. Always dey ask your doctor or qualified health care provider if you get any question about medical issue. No use information wey you read from Kaci automated assistant replace doctor advice or cancel appointment with doctor. Kaci mobile application and notification fit use only information wey dem don give am and information wey dey online already take provide some information and services for you.</div><div><br></div><div>1.2 Dis privacy policy go explain to you di personal information wey we dey collect, how we dey use and share di information, and how you fit control how we dey use and share di information. E go tell you wetin Healthcare Professionals and oda members fit see when you dey use our Sites and Services. E go tell you your rights and choices wey concern your personal information and how you fit contact us if you get any question or something dey worry you.</div><div><br></div><div>1.3 Kaci dey run under FactCheck Initiative (FCI), wey be registered non-governmental development organization wey dem register for Nigeria with registration number CAC/IT/NO 130560. Dem dey focus on check say tori dey correct, dey sensitize pipo and dey provide solutions to fight misleading tori, stories, agendas or manifestos for Africa and di world.</div><div><br></div><div>1.4 If you wan holla us, abeg send mail go our Customer Service team for info@kaci.help.</div><div><br></div><div>1.5 You suppose don reach at least 10 years before you fit use di App. But if you dey below 13 years, you need consent from your guardian before you fit use Kaci and agree to these Terms of Use.</div><div><br></div><div>1.6 To fit use di complete power wey dey inside Kaci, you must agree say you go dey bound by these Terms of Use. If you no gree, you no fit use or access any part of di Kaci Automated assistant and mobile application.</div><div><br></div><div>1.7 Di language wey we go take arrange contract na English, but di Mobile Application dey available for 9 different languages wey be English, Arabic, French, Chinese, Fula, Igbo, Hausa, Portuguese, Yoruba, Pidgin and Spanish.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>2. Legal relationship between you and Kaci</strong></div><div><br></div><div>2.1 These Terms of Use dey cover how you fit use Kaci and e contain di terms wey dey control how you fit use di App. E dey important make you don read and understand di Terms of Use and our Privacy Policy before you begin use di App. If you no understand anything for these documents, abeg contact us for info@kaci.help, we go fit explain everything well well.</div><div><br></div><div>2.2 You fit only use Kaci if you agree to these Terms of Use. If you no gree with di Terms of Use, you no fit create User account for di app.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>3. Information wey we collect about you</strong></div><div><br></div><div>3.1 To protect your privacy and any data wey relate to you (wey we go call \"Personal Data\"), e dey very important to us. For dat reason, any Personal Data wey Kaci gather from your use, we go only collect am, store am and process am according to di relevant General Data Protection Regulations. Abeg read our Privacy Policy make you sabi how and why we dey collect and use your information so we fit give you di best possible service.</div><div><br></div><div>3.2 You dey give us right to use data wey we don anonymize according to data protection law. You dey accept say we go own any data wey we gather from di anonymized data.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>4. Kaci Services</strong></div><div><br></div><div>4.1 Kaci give you information wey go help you sabi wetin dey happun for news and confirm tori for internet. E dey use information wey don already dey available for public. Kaci Mobile Application fit also alert people wey you dey depend on (emergency contacts).</div><div><br></div><div>4.2 We dey provide Kaci for free through di App and WhatsApp/SMS.</div><div><br></div><div>4.3 Make you sabi say we dey provide Kaci just for information purposes. E no dey replace medical consultation.</div><div><br></div><div>4.4 Kaci no fit find information wey no dey already accessible online.</div><div><br></div><div>4.5 If you get medical issue wey relate to di information wey you enter for Kaci, na you suppose decide whether you wan see medical professional or seek medical advice.</div><div><br></div><div>4.6 Kaci no be weather app, betting app, and e no get power to predict anything.</div><div><br></div><div>4.7 Kaci Notification dey work on WhatsApp/SMS, e no dey work for Instagram, Facebook or any oda social media platform. Kaci no go fit work if you no get internet connection.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>5. Monthly Carbon Footprint usage</strong></div><div><br></div><div>E dey important make individuals contribute to help, and one of di ways wey you fit take achieve dis na by sabi how much carbon you dey contribute. You fit calculate your own carbon emission; dis na one of di benefits wey we dey offer. Through our app and partner websites, we dey provide platform wey no dey collect money to calculate your personal CO2. You fit set am to know your emission for daily, weekly, monthly and yearly. With simple question wey you go answer, you fit get correct result for your emission. Di exact formula wey we dey use na our secret, and e fit change or adapt anytime. As you sabi, wetin you dey do everyday, your food preference and oda habits na wetin go determine di result of di calculation. With all dis for mind, make you know and agree with di following:</div><div><br></div><div>a) Di result wey you go get, even though e go correct well well, e still go be estimate.</div><div>b) To calculate your exact specific carbon footprint fit no dey possible, so we no fit guarantee am.</div><div>c) Di carbon footprint calculator fit calculate wetin you go fit produce for future, but e no fit predict future. E go only give estimate based on di information wey you give.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>6. Creating User account</strong></div><div><br></div><div>6.1 Registration: You must finish di registration process by give di Company correct information like dem ask you for di registration form. For registration, you gree say you go provide correct, current, and complete information, and you go dey update</div><div><br></div><div>&nbsp;am anytime. You go choose username and password. Abeg no choose username and email address wey no follow rule or wey dey offend, or wey violate dis Agreement or any law wey dey apply.</div><div><br></div><div>6.2 Responsibility for Account: E dey your hand to make sure say your password and account dey secret. Plus, e dey your hand to make sure say no action wey you no know happen for your account. If you see say person use your account without your permission, abeg tell di Company sharp sharp.</div><div><br></div><div>6.3 Sharing: You fit share your Content with anybody you wan. If you decide say you wan share your Content, we go send person wey you wan give the Content instructions on how to see am. You sabi and gree say you decide who go see your Content and we no dey responsible for how person wey you give am take use am.</div><div><br></div><div>6.4 Liability for Account Misuse: Di Company no go fit blame if you lose something based on another pesin use your password or account, either with your permission or without. You fit also dey responsible if Company or another pesin get loss based on another pesin use your account or password.</div><div><br></div><div>6.5 Use of Other Accounts: You no fit use another person account unless di owner give you permission.</div><div><br></div><div>6.6 Risk: You gree say you go carry all di risk wey relate to your Content and any activity wey follow. Any action wey you do based on your Content, you go dey responsible for am. We no go dey responsible for your Content or any loss or damage wey happen as a result of how person take use your Content wey dey available for di Service. We no promise say your Content go dey available anytime you wan see am or we go keep am for specific time. You gree say you no get any remedy against us for any incomplete, wrong, or missing Content.</div><div><br></div><div>6.7 Account Security: The Company dey care for your personal information security. But we no fit guarantee say pesin wey no get permission fit use your personal information for bad purpose. You sabi say you provide your personal information at your own risk. You dey responsible to keep your information secret and to dey line with WhatsApp/SMS rules and privacy provisions. If you think say pesin misuse your User Account, abeg tell us quick quick for info@kaci.help.</div><div><br></div><div>6.8 How to register: Before you fit use the App, you need Apple ID or Google account. You fit download the App from Apple App Store or Google Play Store to your phone or tablet.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>7. Kaci Code</strong></div><div>Kaci Codes be series of numbers wey you fit collect as benefit from our partners wey dey company level, if you create user account after you download our app. Di Kaci Codes go increase di number of requests wey fit dey made for one day, one week, one month or any time period wey dem allot. Di Kaci Code wey you get go dey valid for di time wey dem allocate am and e no fit dey valid pass dat time.</div><div><br></div><div>Some of di terms wey you suppose follow when you dey use Kaci Code include;</div><div>a) You dey legally authorized to use di redemption as e dey within di terms of use of di redemption code.</div><div>b) You gree to di terms and conditions wey relate to di app and di redemption code and how to use am.</div><div>c) Di terms wey di specific corporation wey give you di Code fit apply based on di Kaci Code.</div><div>You fit contact di entity wey give you your Kaci Code if you wan know wetin dey inside am well well. You fit also holla our support team for assistance.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>8. Your right to use the Kaci Mobile Application and WhatsApp/SMS Notification</strong></div><div>8.1 Kaci and all di things wey dey inside am na our property or property of di people wey grant us di license (dis one still apply to third-party software wey dey for Kaci App). We give you right to use these things, but e fit only be for di purpose of using Kaci according to these Terms of Use.</div><div>8.2 We give you right to personally access and use Kaci. You no fit transfer dis right give another pesin, or sell, give away or transfer your User Account give another pesin. Your right to access Kaci no stop us from giving other pipo right to access am.</div><div>8.3 Your right to use di name \"Kaci\" or any trademarks, logos, domain names or any other kind of trademarks no fit pass wetin dey inside these Terms of Use.</div><div>8.4 As you comply with these Terms of Use, we give you small, non-transferable, non-sublicensable, personal, non-exclusive, revocable right to interact with Kaci for your device or to access di Website or di Screening Tool under di conditions wey dey inside these Terms of Use or di privacy policy, or under any terms wey apply to di App (WhatsApp/SMS or web browser) wey you dey use interact with Kaci.</div><div>8.5 As di User, unless e dey appropriately permitted according to these Terms of Use or according to necessary copyright law for di use of Kaci according to its purpose and/or necessary to get information wey go allow am work with other programs, you suppose no do di following:</div><div>a. You, as di User, gree say you no go copy Kaci, either as whole or part.</div><div>b. You, as di User, gree say you no go sell or make Kaci, either as whole or part, available give another pesin.</div><div>c. You, as di User, gree say you no go modify Kaci, either as whole or part, any way at all.</div><div>d. You, as di User, dey give assurance say you no go try find or access di source code of Kaci, either as whole or part, unless we expressly publish am and release am into public domain.</div><div>8.6 You sabi say we and/or di people wey grant us license for this fit claim any confidential information, rights of use, exploitation and recovery, plus any oda intellectual property rights wey dey fully or partially exist, regarding Kaci.</div><div>8.7 Feedback/surveys. If you give us feedback, ideas or suggestions, or if you answer surveys wey concern our Services (wey we go call \"Feedback\"), you sabi say di Feedback no dey secret and you give us worldwide, non-exclusive, irrevocable, perpetual, royalty-free and unlimited license to use your Feedback anyhow, for any purpose, and through any medium or technology wey dem know or wey dem no know, whether as whole or part, and whether as modified or not. We go always use your Feedback according to these Terms of Use, our Privacy Policy and any other law wey apply.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>9. Your use of the Kaci Mobile Application and WhatsApp/SMS Notification</strong></div><div>9.1 Apart from oda things wey dey these Terms of Use, this section get some regulations wey concern di use of Kaci (wey we go call \"Regulations\").</div><div>9.2 Here na list of things wey no dey allow when you dey use Kaci. You no fit do di following:</div><div>a. You no fit comot, disable or manipulate any security features wey Kaci get, or any features wey dey prevent or restrict di use or copying of di content wey dey available through Kaci,</div><div>b. You no fit create many User Accounts for Kaci (but if Kaci fit do am, you fit connect your social networks or oda accounts wey we support with your User account for Kaci),</div><div>c. You no fit give false or misleading information for User Account details or registration,</div><div>d. You no fit allow another pesin use Kaci on your behalf or for your place, especially for medical &amp; other services wey dey personalize,</div><div>e. You no fit use Kaci if we don temporarily stop your right to use am, or we tell you say make you no continue use am,</div><div>f. You no fit send junk mail, spam or repeated messages,</div><div>g. You no fit act in any unlawful or illegal manner,</div><div>h. You no fit modify, disturb, hack or scatter Kaci, or intercept messages,</div><div>i. You no fit misuse Kaci or put virus, trojan, worms, logic bombs or any oda thing wey fit damage Kaci or any oda pesin wey dey use Kaci equipment,</div><div>j. You no fit collect data from Kaci unless e dey permitted for these Terms of Use,</div><div>k. You no fit post or contribute abusive, threatening, obscene, misleading, untruthful, or offensive content, or content wey get nudity or violence inside,</div><div>l. You no fit enter information or comments about any third-party without di consent of di third-party wey dey concerned.</div><div>9.3 If you no comply with di Regulations wey dey for paragraph 9.2, e be like say you breach these Terms of Use well well, and we fit take action wey we choose – either individually or together:</div><div>a. We fit stop you from accessing Kaci immediately, whether e go be temporary or permanent,</div><div>b. We fit send warning give you,</div><div>c. We fit begin legal action against you, wey fit include claim for money to cover costs wey we spend because of di breach (including reasonable administrative costs and legal fees), and</div><div>d. We fit share your information give law enforcement authorities, if we sabi say e dey allowed by law and we think say e dey necessary.</div><div>9.4 If you breach dis agreement, e no mean say we go limit our response to the actions wey we describe for paragraph 9.3. We fit take any oda action wey dey these Terms of Use or law permit.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>10. How to end our agreement</strong></div><div>10.1 If you feel say you no fit agree with these Terms of Use or di Privacy Policy again, you fit stop to use Kaci any time.</div><div>10.2 You fit stop to use Kaci anytime and end your agreement with Kaci, even if you no gree with the changes wey we propose. Make you follow Kaci instructions to deactivate your User Account. If you dey use Kaci through di Kaci App, you fit delete your User Account through settings menu.</div><div>10.3 If we wan end our agreement with you, we go give you two weeks notice.</div><div>10.4 Any party fit end the agreement for cause. We fit end the agreement for your breach of important agreement provisions (especially paragraph 7.2), and if, based on external circumstances, we believe say you dey use our services wrongly. If good reason dey, we fit block your access to Kaci, without any notice, provided say no oda way wey less severe fit work.</div><div><br></div><div>10.5 If you or we end your User Account as I talk for this paragraph or you withdraw your right to access Kaci, we go delete any Personal Data wey we store about you based on our Privacy Policy (and as stipulated in law), provided say our rights to use di data in anonymized form, as I talk for section 3.2, no dey affected. You also lose any rights wey we give you to access Kaci.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>11. Our promise to you</strong></div><div>11.1 Any information wey you talk, or wey we give you for text form through Kaci – either as statement wey you make or by how you take talk am – na for information purposes only. We dey provide di information as e be, without warranty, guarantee or representation of any kind.</div><div>11.2 You no suppose take action based on di information wey Kaci provide without consulting di necessary professional first.</div><div>11.3 Because of di nature of internet and technology, we no fit promise say you go dey use Kaci all di time without interruption, or without delay or fault, or say Kaci go always meet your expectations. So, we no fit promise any obligation for Kaci performance or availability for these Terms of Use. We exclude any strict liability wey law fit enforce based on Kaci defects wey dey exist when you and us agree say you go dey use Kaci.</div><div>11.4 If you get any damage as you dey use Kaci, we fit only dey responsible for intentional and serious negligence. We fit also dey responsible for negligent breach of important contractual obligations, wey e suppose happen for us to even execute this agreement well, and the breach fit affect the purpose of the agreement and you as the User suppose fit trust say we go fulfil am. For the last matter wey I talk, we fit only dey responsible for damages wey we fit calculate. We no fit dey responsible for violation by simple negligence of any oda obligations wey no dey for di sentences wey I talk.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>12. Third-party services</strong></div><div>12.1 If, and to the extent, our Kaci Mobile Application and WhatsApp/SMS Notification contain links to oda websites or resources wey third parties dey operate, make you sabi say we dey provide these links only to give you information.</div><div>12.2 We no fit control the content of these websites or resources wey third parties dey provide, and we no fit dey responsible for the content of information or websites wey dem link put for inside frames. We no fit dey responsible for any financial or physical damage wey you fit get as you use these websites or resources.</div><div>12.3 You sabi say Kaci availability depend on the third-party wey you use download di Kaci App. You sabi say these Terms of Use apply for di agreement between you and Kaci, no be your agreement with the App Store.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><strong>13. Links to oda websites&nbsp;</strong></div><div>Make you sabi say we dey use links to third-party and partner websites wey fit be di responsibility of these third parties.</div><div>Di terms and privacy policy of these third parties no be our responsibility as we no fit control dem or how dem operate and serve. As e dey so, di things wey dem dey offer and services wey dem dey provide na their responsibility.</div><div>You gree say we no go fit hold us responsible for any damage or loss wey e fit cause as you use our content, services, goods or any product.</div><div>You also gree say we no go fit hold us responsible for any inconvenience, damage or loss wey e fit cause as you rely directly or indirectly on any of these third-party or partner websites wey you dey use.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>14. Kaci App and WhatsApp/SMS Notification updates</strong></div><div>14.1 We dey always dey update and improve Kaci. We dey always try to give you new innovative services and features. We also dey make changes and updates to dey up to date with new technology, how people dey behave, and how dem dey use internet.</div><div>14.2 We get the right to change some specific things about specific features as we dey update Kaci, wey fit include reset of that feature and stopping support or service for that feature. These changes fit affect wetin you dey do for Kaci. Changes fit include removing, modifying, or resetting the features wey you dey use. We go let you know about the changes and your rights if there are any changes through separate notification, to the extent wey you sign up for those notifications (see paragraph 15.3).</div><div>14.3 Updates fit dey released from time to time by us or through the App Store where you download the Kaci App. Sometimes, you fit need to update third-party software to dey able to use Kaci.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>15. Changes to these Terms of Use</strong></div><div>15.1 We get the right to change, adapt, or add to these Terms of Use from time to time.</div><div>15.2 Any changes to these Terms of Use fit happen because we wan add new features to Kaci or based on changes for the law or regulations wey apply.</div><div>15.3 We go contact you to inform you about any changes or additions to these Terms of Use at least 30 calendar days before the changes or additions take effect. If you no object within 30 days from when you receive the notice, those changes and additions go dey effective and we go assume say you agree to them from that time. We go tell you about your right to object and the results of the objection for the notice wey we go send about the changes to the Terms of Use. If, based on your objection, we feel say e no dey reasonable for us to continue providing Kaci, we fit end the agreement, but no go earlier than the effective date wey we put for the notice. Any other right to end the agreement no dey affected.</div><div>16. Documents wey dey control the agreement between you and us</div><div>The current version of the Terms of Use na the one wey get all the rules wey control the agreement between you and us. Any old versions of the Terms of Use no go dey applicable to our agreement again, and dem go dey fully replaced by the current version.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>17. Laws wey apply and jurisdiction</strong></div><div>17.1 Our headquarters dey for Nigeria. Any agreement wey dey based on these Terms of Use dey subject to the laws of the Federal Republic of Nigeria. If trader and consumer dey involved, the law of the country where the consumer dey reside go dey applicable and e fit no dey changed under the law of that country. This one fit apply if:</div><div>a. The trader dey do business for the country where the consumer dey reside, or</div><div>b. The trader dey direct business to that country or even different countries wey include that country, and the agreement na part of those activities.</div><div>17.2 Only Nigeria courts fit settle any disputes wey dey connected to, or wey dey result from, your use of Kaci.</div><div>17.3 Kaci no dey involved for dispute settlement for any consumer arbitration board.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>18. Your Privacy</strong></div><div>The Kaci Help privacy policy go show you the data wey we collect, how we dey use am, where we dey keep am, and how we dey process am when you dey use and access our Services. As you dey use our Services, you don read, understand, and agree to the terms wey dey our privacy policy. You agree say we fit use your data like that based on the terms wey dey our privacy policy. If you get question about our privacy policy, you fit contact us for help@kaci.help.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>19. Compliance with Policies</strong></div><div>As you dey use the Services, you agree say you go follow all the policies wey we post and wey we fit update from time to time. If you no follow any policy, we fit stop you from using the services.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>20. User Content and Links to other Websites</strong></div><div>20.1 Kaci Help dey encourage people to contribute for the website. You fit submit descriptions of services, comments, posts, advice, and recommendations through the features wey dey for the website (we go call am \"User Generated Content\"). You dey responsible for any User Generated Content wey you submit, and you agree say you no go provide any false or misleading information, abusive, defamatory, obscene, or anything wey go invade another person\'s privacy, or violate person\'s intellectual property rights, or break any laws or regulations.</div><div>20.2 As you provide User Generated Content to Kaci Help, you agree say Kaci Help fit use am as e be for the provision of its Services and the website, without paying you any money.</div><div>20.3 Kaci Help fit reject, no fit publish, or fit remove any User Generated Content as dem like.</div><div>20.4 Kaci Help no dey responsible for and no dey support statements, comments, or any other information wey dey User Generated Content wey other people submit. Anything wey you dey believe based on those information go dey your own risk. User-Generated Content wey you or others submit fit carry links to oda websites. Kaci Help no dey monitor or verify the content of any websites wey dey link to the website, and e no dey responsible for the correctness of the content or any opinions wey dey there. When you dey access those third-party sites, you do am at your own risk.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>21. Intellectual Property Rights</strong></div><div>21.1 The Company na the one wey own the website and the Services (including any updates or changes). All rights, title, and interest, including intellectual property rights, for Kaci Help\'s website, the Services, the software, and the content on the website, still belong to the Company and their licensors if applicable. Unless we expressly give you permission, you no fit reproduce, modify, distribute, license, sell, transfer, publicly display, transmit, or do any other thing with Kaci Help\'s website, the Services, the software, or the content on the website.</div><div>21.2 The Kaci Help name, logo, and the names of products wey dey related to the Services na trademarks of the Company, our affiliated companies, or other third parties, and we no give you any permission or license to use them. Any logo, trademark, domain name, or trade name wey you see for the Services, whether dem register am or not, na their property or the property of their owners. You no fit use any of dem unless we give you express permission.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>22. Your Mobile Device</strong></div><div>The agreement wey you get with your mobile network provider still apply if you dey use the Services for your mobile device. You sabi say your mobile provider fit charge you money for using their network to access or use the Services, for data, email, text messages, roaming, and other charges. The quality and availability of the Services fit dey affected by things wey dey outside our control.</div><div>We no fit guarantee say the Services go work well with the service plans wey your mobile provider get, or with any specific mobile device or other things wey you install or use with your mobile device. We no go responsible if the Services no dey available or if you no fit download or access the Services or the content, or any issues wey relate to compatibility or interoperability, or any communication system failure wey fit cause the app no dey available.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>23. Communication Preferences and Consent</strong></div><div>23.1 From time to time, we fit send you messages to the email address wey you use for your account. The messages fit include tips, special offers, and other things wey relate to your account or transactions.</div><div>23.2 Also, our mobile apps fit allow you receive SMS and push notifications in connection with the apps and the Services. If you wan change how you take receive push notifications from our apps, you fit control the settings for each device wey you use. By accepting this Agreement and using the Services, you agree say you go receive all these messages from Kaci Help. You fit change your communication preferences anytime for the settings for our website or apps. You no fit choose to stop account-related or transactional messages.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>24. Authorized Jurisdictions</strong></div><div>Kaci Help make the Services available for Nigeria. We fit add or remove countries from the list of place