no like how the Services dey, just stop to use am.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>27. Limitation Of Liability</strong></div><div>27.1 To the extent wey the law fit allow, we no go liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or exemplary damages, wey fit include things like loss of money, profits, goodwill, use, data, or other intangible losses, wey come from or get link to your use of the apps or the Services, whether based on contract, tort (including negligence and strict liability), warranty, statute, or any other thing.</div><div>27.2 If the law no fit allow us to disclaim any implied warranty or limit our liabilities, we go only dey responsible for the minimum wey the law fit allow.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>28. Assignment</strong></div><div>Di Company fit handova dis Agreement or delegate any of our rights or obligations wey dey inside am, or any part of am, to any third party, including our successor wey dey interested, without needing your written consent. You no fit handova dis Agreement as a whole or in part, for any reason. Dis Agreement go dey binding for di parties and dia heirs, executors, administrators, successors, and assigns.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>29. Suspension and Termination</strong></div><div>29.1 We fit suspend, disable, or close your account or stop to provide the Services to you as a whole or in part, anytime and for any reason. We go try notify you through di email address or phone number wey you use register your account if we ever need to suspend, disable, or close your account. We no go get any responsibility to you or any third party if we suspend, disable, or close your account. You no go fit access any Content or di Services once your access don dey suspended or terminated or if di Services don close.</div><div>29.2 You fit deactivate your Account and end your registration any time if you contact Kaci Help Support. At di time wey you deactivate, you dey fully responsible to get any Content Informat