rm or provision inside dis Agreement go dey consider as waived and no breach go dey pardoned unless dem write am down and we sign am. Anytime we no enforce any right wey we give here, e no go mean say we don give up on that right completely.</div><div>31.3 Nothing for dis Terms of Use go create or give any party wey no be Kaci Help or you any legal or fair rights, remedies, responsibilities, or claims concerning dis Terms of Use.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>32. Notices</strong></div><div>32.1 We fit put notices give you for inside di Services. We fit also send you notices about products and services to di email address wey you give us. You don agree say you go dey collect notices from us through di ways wey we talk so, and you go don collect di notice at most two (2) business days after we put or send di notice. You get responsibility to dey update your account info, including your email address.</div><div>32.2 Kaci Help no go get any responsibility for any wahala wey dey come from you provide or use outdated, incomplete, or false information for connection to di Services. Apart from how dem talk here, any notices wey we suppose send to Kaci Help under dis Terms of Use fit dey deliver through di contact info wey dem give under.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><strong>33. Support and Feedback</strong></div><div>33.1 You don agree say we fit communicate with you by electronic means (like email or any other text form like Nigerian law talk).</div><div>33.2 We fit send you notices electronically to di email address wey you give when you first use Kaci features and services, or through other electronic ways wey dey Kaci when dem dey available.</div><div>33.3 No enforce of our rights no mean say we don give up on those rights.</div><div>33.4 If any provision for these Terms of Use dey or later become void or no fit enforce, e no go affect the power wey di remaining provisions get.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>34. Contact</strong></div><div>If you wan contact us about 