INSERT INTO `setting` (`id`, `language`, `type`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(28, 'English', 'Privacy', '<div>Kaci&nbsp;Website, Mobile Application&nbsp;(“<strong>us</strong>”, “<strong>our</strong>”, “<strong>Kaci</strong>”&nbsp;“<strong>Kaci App</strong>”&nbsp;or “<strong>we</strong>”) and its affiliates value the privacy of individuals who access our Sites and use our Services, thus protecting your data, privacy and personal data is very important&nbsp;us. It is vitally important to us that our customers (the “<strong>users</strong>”) feel secure when using our products and services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This privacy policy (the “<strong>Privacy Policy</strong>”), together with our Terms &amp; Conditions, our Cookie Policy&nbsp;and any other documents referred therein, sets out the basis on which any personal data we collect from you, or that you provide to us, will be processed. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand the types of data we collect from you, how we use it, the circumstances under which we will share it with third parties, and your rights in relation to your personal data.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">You can use “Kaci” through our Mobile Applicationlication (the “<strong>App</strong>”).&nbsp;This Privacy Policy describes our data processing when using our&nbsp;App,&nbsp;or simply accessing our website Kaci.help (the “<strong>Website</strong>”) or any service and/or product we may provide you (Website together with the Mobile Applicationlication and any of our product and services, the “<strong>Services</strong>”). Where certain processing activities relate only to a specific product such as the App or the Enterprise solution, this will be clearly indicated.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Who we are</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This Privacy Policy applies to any personal data processed by Kaci&nbsp;or Factcheck Initiative,&nbsp;being the data controller of all processing activities in connection with the Services&nbsp;offered on the Kaci Mobile Application, or the Kaci Website.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Questions, comments and requests regarding this Privacy Policy are welcome and should be addressed through our&nbsp;information desk info@kaci.help.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This privacy policy explains to you the personal information we collect, how we use and share that information, and the ways in which you can control how we use and share that information. It informs you what information the Healthcare Professionals or other member can see when you use our Sites and Services. It informs you of your rights and choices with respect to your personal information and how you can contact us should you have any questions or concerns.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">KACI&nbsp;MOBILE APPLICATION &amp; WEBSITE&nbsp;WILL BE COLLECTING AND TRANSMITTING PERSONAL, MEDICAL AND HEALTH-RELATED INFORMATION ABOUT YOU. BY USING THE APP&nbsp;AND OUR WEBSITE, YOU AGREE THAT WE CAN COLLECT AND USE YOUR PERSONAL AND OTHER INFORMATION AS DESCRIBED IN THIS SITE PRIVACY POLICY. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE, PLEASE DO NOT USE THE APP AND OUR WEBSITE.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>YOU MUST BE 10&nbsp;YEARS OR OLDER TO&nbsp;USE KACI’S&nbsp;SERVICES.</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2.&nbsp;Important Definitions</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1“Personal Information” in this Privacy Policy, means information about you that is personally identifiable to you, such as your contact information (e.g. name, address, email address, or telephone number), personally identifiable health or medical information (“Health Information”),&nbsp;personal identification&nbsp;documents (such as driver’s license, voter’s card etc.)&nbsp;and any other non-public information that is associated with such information.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">“De-Identified Information”, means information that is neither used nor intended to be used to personally identify an individual.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2&nbsp;Information We Receive or Collect from You</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Registration Data: When you register or create an account, you provide us with certain information, which includes your email address, telephone number, date of birth, gender, and zip or postal code (the “Registration Data”), as well as a password for your account.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Payment Information: If you choose to use a fee-based Service&nbsp;such as advertisement or make a donation, you will be requested to provide (at a minimum) your name and payment information including payment card information (“<em>Payment Information</em>“). A third-party service provider that handles payments for us will also receive your payment card information.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Information You Choose to Provide to Us: You have the ability to provide a variety of information during your interactions with us and the Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App, such as emails you may send us, information you respond to, and emails or newsletters that you sign up to receive. Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App or third parties acting on our behalf receive data from you whenever you provide us with information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Contact Information: If you choose to participate in research studies, or sign up for certain features, you may provide us, and we may collect, your contact information, including your name, mailing address, and phone number (“Contact Information”).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;De-identified Data.&nbsp;We use de-identified data for research and development of new products or tools, to refine our algorithms and machine learning applications, and to improve the App and the services we provide. We may disclose such information publicly and to third parties, for example, in public reports about health, to partners under agreement with us, or in benchmarking information we provide to the medical community.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3&nbsp;Information We Receive from Third Parties</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Social Media Accounts: We may obtain Personal Information about you&nbsp;through the Mobile Application, or other&nbsp;third party social media services, such as Facebook and Twitter, if you choose to link our Services with third party social media accounts (“Social Media Account”) by either: (i) providing your Social Media Account login information to us through the Services; or (ii) allowing us to access your Social Media Account, as is permitted under the applicable terms and conditions that govern your use of the respective Social Media Account.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4&nbsp;Information we collect via technology</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Activity on the app, the automated assistant and our websites: We may keep track of some of the actions you take on the app, the automated assistant and our websites, such as the content of searches you perform&nbsp;via the Mobile Application or&nbsp;on the app, the automated assistant and our website.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Access Device and Browser Information: When you access the app, the automated assistant and our website from a computer or other device, we may collect anonymous information from that device, such as your Internet protocol address, browser type, connection speed and access times (collectively, “Anonymous Information”).&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Cookies: We may use both session Cookies (which expire once you close your web browser) and persistent Cookies to make the app, the automated assistant and our website and Services easier to use, to make our advertising better, and to protect both you and Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App. You can instruct your browser, by changing its options, to stop accepting Cookies or to prompt you before accepting a Cookie from the websites you visit. If you do not accept Cookies, however, you will not be able to stay logged in to the app, the automated assistant and our websites. We may also use Pixels to make the app, the automated assistant and our websites and Services easier to use and to make our advertising better by, for example, summarizing usage patterns. We presently do not honor “Do Not Track” requests across all parts of our Sites.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Real Time Location: Certain features of the app, the automated assistant and our website use GPS technology to collect real-time information about the location of your device so that the app, the automated assistant and our website can connect you to a&nbsp;Security Agency,&nbsp;Healthcare ProfessionalServices or Ambulance&nbsp;service&nbsp;which&nbsp;are&nbsp;licensed or authorized to provide Services in the area or jurisdiction where you are located. When accessing Google Maps services on our Sites, you are agreeing to Google’s&nbsp;<u>Terms of Service</u>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<u>Privacy Policy</u>.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Mobile Services: We may collect non-personal information from your mobile device or computer. This information is generally used to help us deliver the most relevant information to you. Examples of information that may be collected and used include how you use&nbsp;the Kaci app, other&nbsp;application(s) and information about the type of device or computer you use. In addition, in the event our application(s) crashes on your mobile device we will receive information about your mobile device model software version and device carrier, which allows us to identify and fix bugs and otherwise improve the performance of our application(s).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3.&nbsp;How We Use Information We Receive or Collect</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1&nbsp;Generally, Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App uses the information we collect for the following purposes:</div><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">To operate, provide, maintain, improve and enhance our Services;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">To understand and analyze how you use our Services and to develop new products, services, features, and functionality;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">To personalize your experience on our Services, such as by providing tailored content. For example, we use your email address to help you create, log into, and manage your account on our Services. This lets us personalize your experience and give you relevant information. It also powers the features that help you better understand, engage with, and track your health and to present you with personalized, relevant information;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">For marketing and advertising purposes, such as developing and providing promotional and advertising materials that may be relevant, valuable or otherwise of interest to you. We also may use the information that we learn about you to assist us in advertising our Services on third party websites. Where required under applicable law, we will only send you marketing communications with your consent;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">To communicate with you via email, text messages, push notifications and phone calls, in order to provide you with updates and other information relating to our Services, provide information that you request, respond to comments and questions, and otherwise provide customer support;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">To facilitate transactions and payments;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">To facilitate the connection of Social Media Accounts to our Services to provide information from Social Media Accounts to your Profile. Depending on the Social Media Accounts you choose and subject to the privacy settings that you have set in such Social Media Accounts, we will access, make available and store (if applicable and as permitted by the social media service and authorized by you) the information in your Social Media Accounts so that it is available on and through your Profile on the Services;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">For our business purposes, such as audits, for quality assurance purposes, to find and prevent fraud, and respond to trust and safety issues that may arise;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">For compliance purposes, including enforcing our&nbsp;<u>Terms of Use</u>&nbsp;or other legal rights, or as may be required by applicable laws and regulations or requested by any judicial process or governmental agency;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">For other purposes for which we provide specific notice at the time the information is collected; and</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">To aggregate or otherwise de-identify information collected through the Services and use and disclose it for other business purposes after the data can no longer be reasonably linked to an identifiable person.</li></ul><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.2&nbsp;De – Identified Information</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">We may use de-identified information without any restrictions.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.3&nbsp;Information You Share with Third Parties.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This Privacy Policy applies only to information we collect through our Sites and in email, text and other electronic communications set through or in connection with our Sites. This Policy DOES NOT apply to information collected by any third party. When you click on links on the app, the automated assistant&nbsp;or&nbsp;our website you may leave our Site. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of other sites, and we encourage you to read their privacy statements.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>4.&nbsp;How we share the Personal Information we collect</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App may share or otherwise disclose Personal Information in the circumstances described below.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.1&nbsp;Affiliates: We may disclose Personal Information to our affiliates or partners to provide the Services or for other purposes for which the information was collected.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.2&nbsp;Vendors and Service Providers: We may share Personal Information we receive with vendors, relevant authority (emergency services or law enforcement upon your request)&nbsp;and service providers in connection with the provision of the Services&nbsp;and features of Kaci. In the event Personal Information is (a) to be used for a purpose that is materially different from the purposes for which the Personal Information was originally collected or subsequently authorized, or (b) transferred to a third party acting as a data controller, Members will be given, where practical and appropriate, an opportunity to opt out of having non-sensitive Personal Information used or transferred. For sensitive information, including health related information, members will opt in before such use or transfer.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">In some instances, Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App may retain other service providers to perform functions on our behalf, including, but not limited to, website developers and IT services providers.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.3&nbsp;Analytics Partners:&nbsp;We may make certain Personal Information available to third parties for analytics purposes, including: (a) for Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App business or marketing purposes, or (b) to leverage third-party tools to understand Members’ interests, habits, and usage patterns, and/or functionality available through our Services. We only share your Personal Information with analytics partners to improve our own Services and/or to deliver healthcare to you. We do not sell your Personal Information to advertisers.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.4&nbsp;As Required by Law and Similar Disclosures:&nbsp;We may access, preserve, and disclose Personal Information if we believe doing so is required or appropriate, in our sole discretion, to: (a) comply with any applicable law, regulation, legal process or governmental requests, such as a court order or summons, or otherwise cooperate with law enforcement or governmental agencies; (b) take precautions against liability; (c) protect your, our, or others’ rights, property, or safety; (d) investigate and defend ourselves against any third-party claims or allegations; and (e) protect the security or integrity of our Services and any facilities or equipment used to make our Services available. For the avoidance of doubt, the disclosure of Personal Information may occur if you post any objectionable content on or through the Services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.5&nbsp;Social Media Services:&nbsp;Our Services may allow you to, upon your direction, share Personal Information with certain social media services, such as Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, and Google Plus. Please consider any impact on your privacy and anonymity when posting content to any and all social media services. You understand and agree that the use of Personal Information by any social media services will be governed by the respective privacy policies of those social media services and your settings on their platforms. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.6&nbsp;Marketing:&nbsp;We do not rent, sell, or share Personal Information about you with nonaffiliated companies for their direct marketing purposes, unless we have your permission.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.7&nbsp;Mergers, Sales, or Other Asset Transfers:&nbsp;We may disclose and otherwise transfer Personal Information to service providers, advisors, potential transactional partners, or other third parties in connection with the consideration, negotiation, or completion of a corporate transaction in which we are acquired by or merged with another company or we sell, liquidate, or transfer all or a portion of our assets.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>5.&nbsp;Security and Data Integrity</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.1&nbsp;Data Security:&nbsp;Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App makes commercially reasonable efforts to protect Personal Information by using physical and electronic safeguards designed to protect the integrity and security of the Personal Information we maintain. We take commercially reasonable precautions, considering the risks involved in the processing and the nature of the Personal Information, designed to protect Personal Information from loss, misuse and unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration and destruction. However, as no electronic transmission or storage of Personal Information can be entirely secure, we can make no guarantees as to the security or privacy of Personal Information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.2&nbsp;Data Integrity:&nbsp;We use the information we collect in ways that are relevant and compatible with the purpose for which that information was collected or provided to us as disclosed in this policy. We will take steps to ensure that all information collected, processed, and/or stored is protected from destruction, corruption, or use in a manner inconsistent with our policies or the purpose for which we received it.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>6.&nbsp;Our Policy concerning Children</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App prohibits registration by and does not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under the age of 10&nbsp;years.&nbsp;However, sensitive, personal information relating to a child&nbsp;less than&nbsp;18 years is only&nbsp;to be&nbsp;collected using an account set up and managed by an adult parent or guardian. In the event we come to the knowledge that we have collected information from a child under the age of 10&nbsp;years we will take all measures necessary to remove such information from our servers. If you believe that we might have any personal information from a child under 10, please contact our team&nbsp;at info@kaci.help.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>7.&nbsp;Information Retention</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">We take measures to retain your Personal Information for a period that is no longer than necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law. When determining the retention period, we take into account various criteria, such as the type of Services provided to you, the nature and length of our relationship with you, the impact on the Services we provide to you if we delete some Personal Information from or about you, and mandatory retention periods provided by law and the relevant statute of limitations.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>8.&nbsp;Your Privacy Rights and Choices</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Sharing Preferences.</strong>&nbsp;We provide you with settings to allow you to set your sharing preferences for content you post to our Services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.1&nbsp;Optional Profile Information:&nbsp;You can add, edit, or delete optional Personal Information appearing in your Profile at any time in your account settings under edit profile link.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.2&nbsp;Required Account Information:&nbsp;Certain Personal Information is required for account functionality and can be edited but not deleted. For example, you can edit, but not remove, the email address and password required for login.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.3Health Records:&nbsp;You can amend your health information and can add information to make your information more accurate or complete. Accordingly, if you would like to request access to, or to limit the use or disclosure of Personal Information, please contact&nbsp;us.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.4&nbsp;Public Content:&nbsp;You can request the removal of Public Content by contacting&nbsp;us.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.5&nbsp;Marketing Communications:&nbsp;You can unsubscribe from our marketing communications, such as announcements of new features or special offers, via the link provided in the promotional emails.&nbsp;We&nbsp;will never share your email address or other contact information to third parties for their own marketing purposes without your explicit permission. Even if you opt out of receiving promotional messages from us, you will continue to receive administrative messages from us.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.6&nbsp;Notifications:&nbsp;We will ask you if you want to receive notifications when you open an account with us. If you agree, we may send you email, SMS, or mobile push notices, providing you with account-related reminders or updates, or letting you know that you have a message on our Services. You may opt out at any time by adjusting your notification settings in the settings page.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.7&nbsp;Do Not Track:&nbsp;There is no accepted standard on how to respond to Do Not Track signals, and we do not respond to such signals.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.8&nbsp;Log Out of&nbsp;Your Account:&nbsp;you may deactivate your account at any time. To do this, sign in, go to the settings page, and choose the&nbsp;logout&nbsp;option. Your public questions that have received answers will continue to appear anonymously on our Services even if you deactivate your account.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>9.&nbsp;Changes to this Policy</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.1&nbsp;We will continue to evaluate this policy against new technologies, business practices, changes in law, and our member needs, and may make changes to the policy accordingly. Please check this page periodically for updates. If we make any material changes to this policy, we will post the updated terms of the policy on the Services, and provide you notice of such changes, which may include notice by email through a message sent to the email address you use to access the Services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.2&nbsp;Any material changes to this policy will be effective within thirty (30) calendar days following our dispatch of an email notice to you. These changes will be effective immediately for new users of the Services.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.3&nbsp;Please note that at all times you are responsible for updating your information to provide us with your most current email address. In the event that the last email address that you have provided us is not valid, or for any reason is not capable of delivering to you the notice described above, our dispatch of the email containing such notice will nonetheless constitute effective notice of the changes described in the notice.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.4&nbsp;If you do not wish to permit changes in our use of your information, you must notify us prior to the effective date of the changes that you wish to deactivate your account.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.5&nbsp;Continued use of the Services following notice of such changes shall indicate your acknowledgement of such changes and agreement to be bound by the terms and conditions of such changes.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>10.&nbsp;Governance&nbsp;</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.1&nbsp;Enforcement: Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App will conduct compliance audits of our relevant privacy practices to verify adherence to this policy. Further, we will conduct follow-up investigations to verify that attestations and assertions regarding our privacy practices are accurate. You may inquire about an inaccuracy or make a complaint about a potential violation to us via the contact information provided below. We do engage in training to support the implementation and compliance with our privacy practices; any employee that we determine is in violation of this policy may be subject to disciplinary action.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.2&nbsp;Dispute Resolution: Questions or concerns regarding our use or disclosure of information may be directed to our team&nbsp;at info@kaci.help.&nbsp;We&nbsp;will investigate and attempt to resolve complaints and disputes regarding use and disclosure of information in accordance with the principles contained in this policy. Any dispute regarding this Policy shall be resolved following the dispute resolution mechanisms outlined in out&nbsp;Terms of Use.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>11.&nbsp;Support and Feedback</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">If you have any questions or would like further clarification about the app, the automated assistant and our websites or Services, please contact us at&nbsp;info@kaci.help.&nbsp;We love to hear from you. If you have an idea that can make Kaci better any feedback concerning our services, contact&nbsp;us&nbsp;at&nbsp;info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 05:05:56');
INSERT INTO `setting` (`id`, `language`, `type`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(29, 'Hausa', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci&nbsp;Website, Mobile Application&nbsp;(\"&nbsp;<strong>us&nbsp;</strong>\", \"&nbsp;<strong>our&nbsp;</strong>\"&nbsp;, \"&nbsp;<strong>Kaci&nbsp;</strong>\"&nbsp;“&nbsp;<strong>Kaci App&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;ko “&nbsp;<strong>mu&nbsp;</strong>”) da masu haɗin gwiwa suna daraja sirrin mutanen da ke shiga rukunin yanar gizon mu kuma suna amfani da Sabis ɗinmu&nbsp;, don haka&nbsp;daidaita bayanan ku, sirrin ku da bayanan ku yana da mahimmancin&nbsp;mu&nbsp;. Yana da mahimmanci a gare mu cewa abokan cinikinmu (\"&nbsp;<strong>masu amfani&nbsp;</strong>\") su sami kwanciyar hankali yayin amfani da samfuranmu da ayyukanmu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Wannan manufar keɓantawa (\"&nbsp;<strong>Manufar Sirri&nbsp;</strong>\"), tare da Sharuɗɗanmu &amp; Sharuɗɗa, Dokar Kuki da duk wasu takaddun da aka ambata a ciki, sun tsara tushen abin da duk wani bayanan sirri da muka tattara daga gare ku, ko kuma wanda kuka ba mu, zai kasance. a sarrafa. Da fatan za a karanta wannan Dokar Sirri a hankali don fahimtar nau\'ikan bayanan da muke tattarawa daga gare ku, yadda muke amfani da su, yanayin da za mu raba shi tare da wasu mutane, da haƙƙoƙin ku dangane da bayanan ku.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kuna iya amfani da \"Kaci\" ta hanyar aikace-aikacen wayar hannu (\"&nbsp;<strong>App&nbsp;</strong>\")&nbsp;.&nbsp;Wannan Dokar Sirri tana bayyana sarrafa bayanan mu lokacin amfani da&nbsp;App ɗin mu,&nbsp;ko kawai shiga gidan yanar gizon mu Kaci.help (“&nbsp;<strong>Yanar gizo&nbsp;</strong>”) ko kowane sabis da/ko samfurin da za mu iya ba ku (Shafin yanar gizon tare da Aikace-aikacen Wayar hannu da kowane samfurinmu ayyuka, da \"&nbsp;<strong>Sabis&nbsp;</strong>\". Inda wasu ayyukan sarrafawa ke da alaƙa da takamaiman samfuri kamar App ko Maganin Kasuwanci, wannan za a nuna a sarari.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Wanene mu</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Wannan Dokar Sirri ta shafi duk wani bayanan sirri da Kaci ke sarrafa&nbsp;ko Factcheck Initiative,&nbsp;kasancewa mai sarrafa bayanai na duk ayyukan sarrafawa dangane da Sabis ɗin&nbsp;da aka bayar akan Kaci Mobile Application, ko Gidan Yanar Gizo na Kaci&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Tambayoyi, sharhi da buƙatun game da wannan Manufar Sirri ana maraba da su kuma yakamata a magance su ta wurin&nbsp;bayanin mu info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Wannan tsarin sirri yana bayyana muku keɓaɓɓen bayanin da muke tattarawa, yadda muke amfani da raba wannan bayanin, da kuma hanyoyin da zaku iya sarrafa yadda muke amfani da raba wannan bayanin. Yana sanar da ku irin bayanin da Ma\'aikatan Kiwon Lafiya ko wani memba zasu iya gani lokacin da kuke amfani da Shafukanmu da Sabis ɗinmu. Yana sanar da ku game da haƙƙoƙinku da zaɓinku dangane da keɓaɓɓen bayanin ku da kuma yadda zaku iya tuntuɓar mu idan kuna da wasu tambayoyi ko damuwa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">KACI&nbsp;MOBILE APPLICATION &amp; WEB&nbsp;SIT&nbsp;E&nbsp;ZA SU TARTARA DA SAYARWA DA BAYANIN KAI. TA HANYAR AMFANI DA APP&nbsp;DA SHAFIN MU, KA YARDA ZAMU IYA TARTAWA DA AMFANI DA KAN KA DA SAURAN BAYANIN KA KAMAR YADDA AKA BAYANI A CIKIN WANNAN SIYASAR SIRRIN SHAFIN. IDAN BAKU YARDA BA, KAR KUYI AMFANI DA APP DA SHAFIN MU.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>DOLE KA KASANCE SHEKARU 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;KO WUCE DOMIN&nbsp;AMFANI DA AYYUKAN KACI&nbsp;.</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2.&nbsp;Ma\'anoni masu mahimmanci</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1&nbsp;\"Bayanin Mutum\" a cikin wannan Sirri na Sirri, yana nufin bayani game da ku wanda ke iya gane ku da kansa, kamar bayanan tuntuɓarku ( misali suna, adireshin, adireshin imel, ko lambar tarho), lafiyar mutum ko bayanin likita (\"Bayanin Lafiya). ”),&nbsp;tantancewar mutum&nbsp;takardu (kamar lasisin tuƙi, katin zabe da sauransu)&nbsp;da duk wani bayanan da ba na jama\'a ba wanda ke da alaƙa da irin waɗannan bayanan.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">“Bayanin da aka Gano”, yana nufin bayanin da ba a yi amfani da shi ba kuma ba a yi nufin amfani da shi don gano mutum da kansa ba.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2&nbsp;Bayanin da Muke Karɓawa ko Tara daga gare ku</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Bayanan Rijista: Lokacin da kayi rajista ko ƙirƙirar asusu, kuna samar mana da wasu bayanai, waɗanda suka haɗa da adireshin imel, lambar tarho, ranar haihuwa, jinsi, da zip ko lambar akwatin gidan waya (“Data Rijista”), haka nan. azaman kalmar sirri don asusun ku.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Bayanin Biyan Kuɗi: Idan kun zaɓi yin amfani da Sabis na tushen kuɗi&nbsp;kamar talla ko bayar da gudummawa&nbsp;, za a buƙaci ku samar da (aƙalla) sunan ku da bayanin biyan kuɗi gami da bayanin katin biyan kuɗi (“&nbsp;<em>Bayanin Biyan Kuɗi&nbsp;</em>“). Mai ba da sabis na ɓangare na uku wanda ke kula da biyan kuɗi a gare mu kuma zai karɓi bayanin katin kuɗin ku.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Bayanin da kuka zaɓa don Bayar da mu: Kuna da ikon samar da bayanai iri-iri yayin hulɗar ku da mu da Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App, kamar imel ɗin da zaku iya aiko mana, bayanan da kuke amsawa, da imel ko wasiƙun labarai da ka yi rajista don karɓa. Kaci Automated Mataimakin &amp; App ko wasu kamfanoni masu aiki a madadinmu suna karɓar bayanai daga gare ku a duk lokacin da kuka ba mu bayani.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Bayanin Tuntuɓa: Idan kun zaɓi shiga cikin binciken bincike, ko yin rajista don wasu fasaloli, kuna iya ba mu, kuma muna iya tattara bayanan tuntuɓarku, gami da sunan ku, adireshin imel, da lambar waya (“Bayanin Tuntuɓi” ).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Bayanan da ba a tantance ba. Muna amfani da bayanan da ba a tantance ba don bincike da haɓaka sabbin samfura ko kayan aiki, don daidaita algorithms da aikace-aikacen koyon injin, da haɓaka App da ayyukan da muke samarwa. Za mu iya bayyana irin wannan bayanin a bainar jama\'a da ga wasu kamfanoni, misali, a cikin rahotannin jama\'a game da lafiya, ga abokan hulɗa da ke ƙarƙashin yarjejeniya da mu, ko a cikin bayanan ƙididdiga da muke bayarwa ga ƙungiyar likitocin.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3&nbsp;Bayanin da Muke Samu Daga Ƙungiyoyin Na Uku</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Social Media Accounts: Za mu iya samun Keɓaɓɓen Bayani game da ku&nbsp;ta hanyar Mobile Application, ko wasu&nbsp;sabis na kafofin watsa labarun na ɓangare na uku, kamar Facebook da Twitter, idan kun zaɓi haɗa Sabis ɗinmu tare da asusun kafofin watsa labarun na ɓangare na uku (\"Asusun Social Media Account). ”) ta ko dai: (i) samar mana da bayanan shiga na Social Media Account ta Sabis; ko (ii) ba mu damar samun damar shiga Asusunku na Social Media, kamar yadda aka ba da izini a ƙarƙashin sharuɗɗa da sharuɗɗan da suka dace waɗanda ke tafiyar da amfanin ku na Social Media Account.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4&nbsp;Bayanan da muke tattarawa ta hanyar fasaha</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Ayyuka akan app, mataimaki mai sarrafa kansa da gidajen yanar gizon mu: Za mu iya ci gaba da bin diddigin wasu ayyukan da kuke yi akan app, mataimaki na atomatik da gidajen yanar gizon mu, kamar abun cikin binciken da kuke yi ta Aikace-aikacen Wayar hannu ko&nbsp;akan&nbsp;. app, mataimaki mai sarrafa kansa da gidan yanar gizon mu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Samun Na\'ura da Bayanin Mai Binciken Bincike: Lokacin da ka shiga app, mataimaki na atomatik da gidan yanar gizon mu daga kwamfuta ko wata na\'ura, ƙila mu tattara bayanan da ba a san su ba daga waccan na\'urar, kamar adireshin ka\'idar Intanet, nau\'in burauza, saurin haɗin kai da shiga. lokuta (tare, \"Bayanin da ba a sani ba\").</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Kukis: Za mu iya amfani da kukis ɗin zaman biyu (wanda ke ƙarewa da zarar kun rufe burauzar gidan yanar gizon ku) da kuma kukis masu tsayi don sauƙaƙe aikace-aikacen, mataimaki mai sarrafa kansa da gidan yanar gizon mu da Sabis ɗinmu da sauƙin amfani, don inganta tallanmu, kuma don kare duka biyun. kai da Kaci Automated mataimakin &amp; App. Kuna iya umurtar mai binciken ku, ta hanyar canza zaɓukan sa, da ya daina karɓar Kukis ko kuma faɗakar da ku kafin karɓar kuki daga gidajen yanar gizon da kuke ziyarta. Idan ba ku karɓi Kukis ba, duk da haka, ba za ku iya ci gaba da shiga cikin app ɗin ba, mataimaki na atomatik da gidajen yanar gizon mu. Hakanan muna iya amfani da Pixels don sanya ƙa\'idar, mataimaki mai sarrafa kansa da gidajen yanar gizon mu da Sabis ɗinmu mafi sauƙin amfani da kuma inganta tallanmu ta hanyar, misali, taƙaita tsarin amfani. A halin yanzu ba mu girmama buƙatun \"Kada a Bibiya\" a duk sassan rukunin yanar gizon mu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Wuri na Gaskiya: Wasu fasalulluka na ƙa\'idar, mataimaki mai sarrafa kansa da gidan yanar gizon mu suna amfani da fasahar GPS don tattara bayanan ainihin lokacin game da wurin da na\'urar ku take domin app, mataimaki mai sarrafa kansa da gidan yanar gizon mu su iya haɗa ku zuwa Tsaro&nbsp;. Hukumar, Sabis na&nbsp;Ƙwararrun Kiwon Lafiya&nbsp;ko Ambulance&nbsp;sabis&nbsp;wanda&nbsp;ich&nbsp;suna&nbsp;da lasisi ko izini don samar da Sabis a yanki ko ikon da kuke. Lokacin samun damar ayyukan Taswirorin Google akan Shafukanmu, kuna yarda da&nbsp;<u>Sharuɗɗan Sabis&nbsp;</u>da&nbsp;<u>Manufar Keɓancewa na Google&nbsp;</u>.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Sabis na Waya: Za mu iya tattara bayanan da ba na sirri ba daga na\'urar hannu ko kwamfutarku. Ana amfani da wannan bayanin gabaɗaya don taimaka mana isar da mafi dacewa bayanan zuwa gare ku. Misalan bayanan da za a iya tattarawa da amfani da su sun&nbsp;haɗa&nbsp;da yadda kuke amfani da&nbsp;Kaci app, o&nbsp;r application(s) da bayanai game da nau\'in na\'ura ko kwamfutar da kuke amfani da su. Bugu da kari, idan aikace-aikacenmu (s) ya yi karo a kan na\'urarku ta hannu za mu sami bayani game da sigar software na na\'urarku ta hannu da mai ɗaukar na\'urar, wanda ke ba mu damar ganowa da gyara kwari da kuma inganta aikin aikace-aikacen mu. .</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3.&nbsp;Yadda Muke Amfani da Bayanan da Muke Karɓawa ko Tara</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1&nbsp;Gabaɗaya, Mataimakin Kaci Automated &amp; App yana amfani da bayanan da muke tattarawa don dalilai masu zuwa:</div><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don aiki, samarwa, kulawa, haɓakawa da haɓaka Ayyukanmu;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don fahimta da nazarin yadda kuke amfani da Ayyukanmu da haɓaka sabbin samfura, ayyuka, fasali, da ayyuka;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don keɓance ƙwarewar ku akan Sabis ɗinmu, kamar ta samar da abubuwan da aka keɓance. Misali, muna amfani da adireshin imel ɗin ku don taimaka muku ƙirƙira, shiga, da sarrafa asusunku akan Sabis ɗinmu. Wannan yana ba mu damar keɓance ƙwarewar ku kuma mu ba ku bayanai masu dacewa. Hakanan yana ba da ikon fasalulluka waɗanda ke taimaka muku ƙarin fahimta, aiki tare, da bin diddigin lafiyar ku da gabatar muku da keɓaɓɓen bayanan da suka dace;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don dalilai na tallace-tallace da tallace-tallace, kamar haɓakawa da samar da kayan talla da kayan talla waɗanda ƙila su dace, masu mahimmanci ko kuma na sha\'awar ku. Hakanan ƙila mu yi amfani da bayanan da muka koya game da ku don taimaka mana wajen tallata Sabis ɗinmu akan gidajen yanar gizo na ɓangare na uku. Inda ake buƙata a ƙarƙashin dokar da ta dace, za mu aiko muku da sadarwar talla ne kawai tare da yardar ku;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don sadarwa tare da ku ta hanyar imel, saƙonnin rubutu, sanarwar turawa da kiran waya, don samar muku da sabuntawa da sauran bayanan da suka shafi Sabis ɗinmu, samar da bayanan da kuke buƙata, amsa tsokaci da tambayoyi, da kuma ba da tallafin abokin ciniki;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don sauƙaƙe ma\'amaloli da biyan kuɗi;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don sauƙaƙe haɗin Asusun Social Media zuwa Sabis ɗinmu don samar da bayanai daga Asusun Social Media zuwa Fayil ɗin ku. Dangane da Asusun Social Media da kuka zaɓa kuma kuna bin saitunan sirrin da kuka saita a cikin irin waɗannan Asusu na Social Media, za mu shiga, samar da samuwa da adana (idan an zartar kuma kamar yadda sabis na kafofin watsa labarun ya ba da izini kuma ku ba ku izini) bayanan. a cikin Asusunku na Social Media don samun samuwa akan kuma ta hanyar Bayanan ku akan Sabis;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don dalilai na kasuwancin mu, irin su binciken bincike, don dalilai na tabbatar da inganci, don nemowa da hana zamba, da kuma ba da amsa ga amana da batutuwan aminci waɗanda za su iya tasowa;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don dalilai na yarda, gami da aiwatar da&nbsp;<u>Sharuɗɗan Amfaninmu&nbsp;</u>ko wasu haƙƙoƙin doka, ko kamar yadda dokoki da ƙa\'idodi na iya buƙata ko kowane tsarin shari\'a ko hukumar gwamnati ta buƙata;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don wasu dalilai waɗanda muke ba da takamaiman sanarwa a lokacin tattara bayanan; kuma</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Don tara ko in ba haka ba ba za a iya gano bayanan da aka tattara ta Sabis ɗin da amfani da bayyana shi don wasu dalilai na kasuwanci bayan bayanan ba za a iya haɗa su da ma\'ana ga mutum mai iya ganewa ba.</li></ul><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.2&nbsp;De - Bayanin Gano</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Za mu iya amfani da bayanan da ba a tantance ba ba tare da wani hani ba.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.3&nbsp;Bayanin da kuke rabawa tare da Ƙungiyoyin Na uku.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Wannan Dokar Sirri tana aiki ne kawai ga bayanan da muke tattarawa ta Shafukanmu da imel, rubutu da sauran hanyoyin sadarwar lantarki da aka saita ta ko dangane da Shafukanmu. Wannan Manufar ba ta shafi bayanin da kowane ɓangare na uku ya tattara ba. Lokacin da kuka danna hanyoyin haɗi akan app ɗin, mataimaki na atomatik&nbsp;ko&nbsp;gidan yanar gizon mu zaku iya barin rukunin yanar gizon mu. Ba mu da alhakin ayyukan sirri na wasu rukunin yanar gizon, kuma muna ƙarfafa ku don karanta bayanan sirrinsu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>4.&nbsp;Yadda muke raba bayanan Keɓaɓɓen da muke tattarawa</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated Mataimakin &amp; App na iya raba ko in ba haka ba bayyana keɓaɓɓen Bayani a cikin yanayin da aka bayyana a ƙasa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.1&nbsp;Ƙungiyoyi: Za mu iya bayyana keɓaɓɓen Bayani ga abokan haɗin gwiwarmu ko abokan haɗin gwiwarmu don samar da Sabis ko don wasu dalilai waɗanda aka tattara bayanan.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.2&nbsp;Dillalai da Masu Ba da Sabis: Za mu iya raba keɓaɓɓun Bayanin da muka karɓa tare da masu siyarwa&nbsp;, ikon da ya dace (sabis na gaggawa ko tilasta bin doka akan buƙatar ku)&nbsp;da masu ba da sabis dangane da samar da Sabis&nbsp;da fasali na Kaci&nbsp;. A cikin taron Bayanin Keɓaɓɓen (a) za a yi amfani da shi don wata manufa wacce ta bambanta ta zahiri da dalilan da aka samo asali na Bayanan Keɓaɓɓen ko kuma aka ba da izini daga baya, ko (b) canjawa wuri zuwa wani ɓangare na uku da ke aiki azaman mai sarrafa bayanai, Membobi. za a ba shi, inda mai amfani kuma ya dace, damar ficewa daga samun amfani ko canja wurin bayanan sirri marasa hankali. Don mahimman bayanai, gami da bayanan da suka danganci lafiya, membobi zasu shiga kafin irin wannan amfani ko canja wuri.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">A wasu lokuta, Mataimakin Kaci Automated &amp; App na iya riƙe wasu masu ba da sabis don yin ayyuka a madadinmu, gami da, amma ba\'a iyakance ga, masu haɓaka gidan yanar gizo da masu samar da sabis na IT ba.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.3&nbsp;Abokan Tattaunawa: Za mu iya samar da wasu keɓaɓɓun Bayani ga wasu kamfanoni don dalilai na nazari, gami da: (a) don Kaci Automated mataimakin &amp; Kasuwancin App ko tallace-tallace, ko (b) don yin amfani da kayan aikin ɓangare na uku don fahimtar abubuwan Membobi, halaye, da tsarin amfani, da/ko ayyuka da ake samu ta Sabis ɗinmu. Mu kawai muna raba keɓaɓɓen Bayanin ku tare da abokan ƙirƙira don haɓaka Sabis ɗin mu da/ko don isar muku da lafiyar ku. Ba ma sayar da keɓaɓɓen bayanin ku ga masu talla.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.4&nbsp;Kamar yadda Doka ta Bukata da Bayyanawa makamantan: Za mu iya samun dama, adanawa, da bayyana bayanan Keɓaɓɓen idan mun gaskanta yin haka ana buƙata ko dacewa, a cikin ikonmu kawai, zuwa: (a) bi kowace doka, ƙa\'ida, tsarin shari\'a ko buƙatun gwamnati, kamar umarnin kotu ko sammaci, ko kuma ba da haɗin kai tare da tilasta bin doka ko hukumomin gwamnati; (b) yin taka-tsan-tsan daga abin alhaki; (c) kare hakkin ku, mu, ko wasu, dukiya, ko amincin ku; (d) bincika da kare kanmu daga duk wani iƙirari ko zargi na ɓangare na uku; da (e) kare tsaro ko mutuncin Sabis ɗinmu da duk wani wuri ko kayan aiki da ake amfani da su don samar da Sabis ɗinmu. Don guje wa shakku, bayyana bayanan Keɓaɓɓen na iya faruwa idan kun buga duk wani abun ciki mara ƙima akan ko ta Sabis ɗin.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.5&nbsp;Sabis na Watsa Labarai: Ayyukanmu na iya ba ku damar, bisa jagorancin ku, raba Bayanin Keɓaɓɓu tare da wasu ayyukan kafofin watsa labarun, kamar Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, da Google Plus. Da fatan za a yi la\'akari da duk wani tasiri kan sirrin ku da rashin sanin sunan ku yayin buga abun ciki zuwa kowane sabis na kafofin watsa labarun. Kun fahimci kuma kun yarda cewa amfani da Bayanin Keɓaɓɓen mutum ta kowane sabis na kafofin watsa labarun za a sarrafa shi ta hanyar manufofin keɓantawa na waɗannan ayyukan kafofin watsa labarun da saitunanku akan dandamalin su. Muna ƙarfafa ku da ku sake duba manufofinsu na sirri.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.6&nbsp;Talla: Ba ma yin hayan, siyarwa, ko raba Bayanin Keɓaɓɓu game da ku tare da kamfanoni marasa alaƙa don manufar tallan su kai tsaye, sai dai idan mun sami izinin ku.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.7&nbsp;Haɗa, Talla, ko Canje-canjen Kayayyaki: Za mu iya bayyanawa da in ba haka ba canja wurin keɓaɓɓen Bayani ga masu ba da sabis, masu ba da shawara, abokan hulɗar ma\'amala, ko wasu ɓangarori na uku dangane da la\'akari, shawarwari, ko kammala ma\'amalar kamfani wanda muke ciki. samu ta ko hade tare da wani kamfani ko mu sayar, mai da ruwa, ko canja wurin duk ko wani ɓangare na kadarorin mu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>5.&nbsp;Tsaro da amincin Data</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.1&nbsp;Tsaron Bayanai: Mataimakin Kaci Mai sarrafa kansa &amp; App yana yin ƙoƙarin kasuwanci mai ma\'ana don kare Bayanin Keɓaɓɓu ta amfani da kariyar jiki da na lantarki da aka tsara don kare mutunci da amincin bayanan Keɓaɓɓen da muke kiyayewa. Muna ɗaukar matakan tsaro masu ma\'ana ta kasuwanci, la\'akari da haɗarin da ke tattare da sarrafawa da yanayin Bayanin Keɓaɓɓen, wanda aka ƙera don kare Bayanin Keɓaɓɓu daga asara, rashin amfani da samun izini mara izini, bayyanawa, canji da lalacewa. Koyaya, kamar yadda babu watsawa ta lantarki ko adana bayanan Keɓaɓɓun da zai iya zama gaba ɗaya amintattu, ba za mu iya ba da garantin tsaro ko keɓaɓɓen Bayanin Keɓaɓɓen ba.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.2&nbsp;Data Integrity: Muna amfani da bayanan da muka tattara ta hanyoyin da suka dace kuma sun dace da manufar da aka tattara ko aka ba mu wannan bayanin kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin wannan manufar. Za mu ɗauki matakai don tabbatar da cewa duk bayanan da aka tattara, sarrafawa, da / ko adana an kiyaye su daga lalacewa, cin hanci da rashawa, ko amfani da su ta hanyar da ba ta dace da manufofinmu ko manufar da muka karɓa ba.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>6.&nbsp;Manufar Mu Game da Yara</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Mataimakin Kaci Automated &amp; App ya haramta yin rajista ta kuma ba ya karɓar bayanan sirri da gangan daga duk wanda bai kai shekara 1&nbsp;0 ba&nbsp;.&nbsp;Koyaya, m,&nbsp;bayanan sirri da suka shafi yaron&nbsp;da bai wuce&nbsp;shekara 18 kawai za&nbsp;a&nbsp;tattara shi ta amfani da asusu kafa da gudanarwa ta babban iyaye ko mai kulawa. Idan muka zo ga sanin cewa mun tattara bayanai daga yaron da bai kai shekara 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;ba, za mu ɗauki duk matakan da suka dace don cire irin waɗannan bayanai daga sabar mu. Idan kun yi imani cewa muna iya samun kowane bayanin sirri daga yaro a ƙasa da 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;, da fatan za a tuntuɓi ƙungiyarmu&nbsp;a info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>7.&nbsp;Riƙe Bayani</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Muna ɗaukar matakan riƙe Bayanin Keɓaɓɓen ku na tsawon lokacin da bai wuce buƙata ba don cika manufofin da aka tsara a cikin wannan Manufar Keɓancewar, sai dai in an buƙaci ƙarin lokacin riƙewa ko doka ta ba da izini. Lokacin ƙayyade lokacin riƙewa, muna la\'akari da ma\'auni daban-daban, kamar nau\'in Sabis ɗin da aka ba ku, yanayi da tsawon dangantakarmu da ku, tasirin Sabis ɗin da muke ba ku idan muka share wasu Bayanan Keɓaɓɓu daga ko game da ku, da lokutan riƙewa na wajibi da doka ta tanadar da ƙa\'idar da ta dace.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>8.&nbsp;Haƙƙin Keɓantawa da Zaɓuɓɓukanku</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Zaɓuɓɓukan Rabawa.&nbsp;</strong>Mun samar muku da saituna don ba ku damar saita abubuwan da kuka zaɓa don abubuwan da kuka aika zuwa Sabis ɗinmu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.1&nbsp;Bayanin Bayanan Bayani na zaɓi: Za ka iya ƙara, gyara, ko share bayanan sirri na zaɓin da ke bayyana a cikin Bayanan martaba a kowane lokaci a cikin saitunan asusunka a ƙarƙashin hanyar haɗin bayanin martaba.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.2&nbsp;Bayanin Asusu da ake Bukata: Ana buƙatar takamaiman keɓaɓɓen Bayani don aikin asusu kuma ana iya gyarawa amma ba a share su ba. Misali, zaku iya gyara, amma kar a cire, adireshin imel da kalmar wucewa da ake buƙata don shiga.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.3Bayanan Kiwon Lafiya: Kuna iya gyara bayanin lafiyar ku kuma kuna iya ƙara bayani don sa bayanin ku ya zama daidai ko cikakke. Don haka, idan kuna son neman samun dama ga, ko iyakance amfani ko bayyana bayanan sirri, da fatan za a tuntuɓe&nbsp;mu&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.4&nbsp;Abun cikin Jama\'a: Kuna iya buƙatar cire Abubuwan Jama\'a ta hanyar tuntuɓar&nbsp;mu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.5&nbsp;Sadarwar Talla: Kuna iya cire rajista daga hanyoyin sadarwar tallanmu, kamar sanarwar sabbin abubuwa ko tayi na musamman, ta hanyar hanyar haɗin da aka bayar a cikin imel ɗin talla. Ba za&nbsp;mu&nbsp;taɓa raba adireshin imel ɗin ku ko wasu bayanan tuntuɓar ga wasu ba don dalilai na tallan su ba tare da takamaiman izinin ku ba. Ko da kun daina karɓar saƙonnin talla daga gare mu, za ku ci gaba da karɓar saƙonnin gudanarwa daga gare mu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.6&nbsp;Fadakarwa: Za mu tambaye ku ko kuna son karɓar sanarwa lokacin da kuka buɗe asusu tare da mu. Idan kun yarda, za mu iya aiko muku da imel, SMS, ko sanarwar turawa ta hannu, samar muku da tunatarwa ko sabuntawa masu alaƙa da asusun, ko sanar da ku cewa kuna da saƙo akan Sabis ɗinmu. Kuna iya ficewa a kowane lokaci ta hanyar daidaita saitunan sanarwarku a cikin shafin saiti.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.7&nbsp;Karka Bibiya: Babu wani ma\'auni da aka yarda akan yadda ake amsawa Kar a bi sigina, kuma ba ma amsa irin waɗannan sigina.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.8&nbsp;Log Out of&nbsp;Your Account: za ka iya kashe asusunka a kowane lokaci. Don yin wannan, shiga, je zuwa shafin saitunan, kuma zaɓi zaɓin&nbsp;fita&nbsp;. Tambayoyin ku na jama\'a waɗanda suka sami amsoshi za su ci gaba da bayyana ba tare da sunansu ba akan Sabis ɗinmu ko da kun kashe asusunku.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>9.&nbsp;Canje-canje ga wannan Manufar</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.1&nbsp;Za mu ci gaba da kimanta wannan manufar a kan sabbin fasahohi, ayyukan kasuwanci, canje-canje a cikin doka, da bukatun membobinmu, kuma za mu iya yin canje-canje ga manufofin daidai. Da fatan za a duba wannan shafin lokaci-lokaci don sabuntawa. Idan muka yi wasu canje-canje na kayan aiki ga wannan manufar, za mu sanya sabbin sharuɗɗan manufofin akan Sabis ɗin, kuma mu ba ku sanarwar irin waɗannan canje-canje, wanda ƙila ya haɗa da sanarwa ta imel ta saƙon da aka aika zuwa adireshin imel ɗin da kuke amfani da shi don samun dama ga Ayyuka.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.2&nbsp;Duk wani canji na kayan aiki ga wannan manufar zai yi tasiri a cikin kwanaki talatin (30) na kalanda bayan aikawa da sanarwar imel zuwa gare ku. Waɗannan canje-canjen za su yi tasiri nan da nan ga sababbin masu amfani da Sabis.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.3&nbsp;Lura cewa a kowane lokaci kuna da alhakin sabunta bayanan ku don ba mu adireshin imel ɗinku na yanzu. A yayin da adireshin imel na ƙarshe da kuka ba mu bai yi aiki ba, ko kuma saboda kowane dalili ba zai iya isar muku da sanarwar da aka bayyana a sama ba, aika imel ɗin da ke ɗauke da irin wannan sanarwar zai zama ingantaccen sanarwa na canje-canjen da aka bayyana. a cikin sanarwar.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.4&nbsp;Idan ba ku son ba da izinin canje-canje a cikin amfani da bayanan ku, dole ne ku sanar da mu kafin ranar da aka yi amfani da canje-canjen da kuke son kashe asusun ku.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.5&nbsp;Ci gaba da amfani da Sabis bayan sanarwar irin waɗannan canje-canje zai nuna amincewar ku na irin waɗannan canje-canje da yarjejeniyar da za a ɗaure ta da sharuɗɗan canje-canjen.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>10.&nbsp;Mulki</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.1&nbsp;Tilasta: Mataimakin Kaci Automated &amp; App za su gudanar da binciken bin ka\'idojin sirrinmu masu dacewa don tabbatar da bin wannan manufar. Bugu da ari, za mu gudanar da bincike-bincike don tabbatar da cewa shaidu da ikirari game da ayyukan sirrinmu daidai ne. Kuna iya yin tambaya game da kuskure ko yin korafi game da yuwuwar cin zarafi a gare mu ta hanyar bayanin tuntuɓar da aka bayar a ƙasa. Muna yin horo don tallafawa aiwatarwa da bin ka\'idodin sirrinmu; duk wani ma\'aikaci da muka tantance ya saba wa wannan manufar na iya fuskantar hukuncin ladabtarwa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.2&nbsp;Ƙwararriyar Rigima: Tambayoyi ko damuwa game da amfaninmu ko bayyana bayananmu ana iya kaiwa ga ƙungiyarmu&nbsp;a info@kaci.help&nbsp;. Za&nbsp;mu&nbsp;bincika da ƙoƙarin warware korafe-korafe da jayayya game da amfani da bayyana bayanai daidai da ƙa\'idodin da ke cikin wannan manufar. Duk wata takaddama game da wannan Manufofin za a warware ta bin hanyoyin warware takaddama da aka zayyana a cikin Sharuɗɗan Amfani.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>11.&nbsp;Taimako da Raddi</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Idan kuna da wasu tambayoyi ko kuna son ƙarin bayani game da app, mataimaki na atomatik da gidajen yanar gizon mu ko Sabis, da fatan za a tuntuɓe mu a&nbsp;info@kaci.help.&nbsp;Muna son ji daga gare ku. Idan kuna da ra\'ayin da zai iya inganta Kaci duk wani ra\'ayi game da ayyukanmu, tuntuɓe&nbsp;mu&nbsp;a&nbsp;info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 05:28:36');
INSERT INTO `setting` (`id`, `language`, `type`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(30, 'French', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci&nbsp;, Application mobile&nbsp;(«&nbsp;<strong>nous&nbsp;</strong>», «&nbsp;<strong>nos&nbsp;</strong>»&nbsp;, «&nbsp;<strong>Kaci&nbsp;</strong>»&nbsp;«&nbsp;<strong>Kaci App&nbsp;</strong>»&nbsp;ou «&nbsp;<strong>nous&nbsp;</strong>») et ses sociétés affiliées attachent de l\'importance à la vie privée des personnes qui accèdent à nos Sites et utilisent nos Services&nbsp;, la protection de vos données, de votre vie privée et de vos données personnelles est donc&nbsp;très importante&nbsp;pour nous&nbsp;. Il est pour nous d\'une importance vitale que nos clients (les «<strong>&nbsp;utilisateurs</strong>&nbsp;») se sentent en sécurité lorsqu\'ils utilisent nos produits et services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Cette politique de confidentialité (la «<strong>&nbsp;Politique de confidentialité</strong>&nbsp;»), ainsi que nos conditions générales, notre politique en matière de cookies et tout autre document qui y est mentionné, définissent la base sur laquelle toutes les données personnelles que nous recueillons auprès de vous ou que vous nous fournissez, seront en traitement. Veuillez lire attentivement cette politique de confidentialité pour comprendre les types de données que nous recueillons auprès de vous, comment nous les utilisons, les circonstances dans lesquelles nous les partagerons avec des tiers et vos droits concernant vos données personnelles.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Vous pouvez utiliser «&nbsp;Kaci&nbsp;» via notre application mobile (l\'«<strong>&nbsp;application</strong>&nbsp;»)&nbsp;.&nbsp;Cette politique de confidentialité décrit notre traitement des données lors de l\'utilisation de notre&nbsp;application,&nbsp;ou simplement en accédant à notre site Web Kaci.help (le \"&nbsp;<strong>site Web&nbsp;</strong>\") ou à tout service et/ou produit que nous pouvons vous fournir (site Web avec l\'application mobile et l\'un de nos produits et services, les «<strong>&nbsp;Services</strong>&nbsp;»). Lorsque certaines activités de traitement ne concernent qu\'un produit spécifique tel que l\'application ou la solution d\'entreprise, cela sera clairement indiqué.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Qui sommes-nous ?</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Cette politique de confidentialité s\'applique à toutes les données personnelles traitées par Kaci&nbsp;ou Factcheck Initiative,&nbsp;étant le responsable du traitement de toutes les activités de traitement en relation avec les services&nbsp;proposés sur l\'application mobile Kaci ou le site Web Kaci&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Les questions, commentaires et demandes concernant cette politique de confidentialité sont les bienvenus et doivent être adressés à notre&nbsp;bureau d\'information info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Cette politique de confidentialité vous explique les informations personnelles que nous collectons, comment nous utilisons et partageons ces informations, et les façons dont vous pouvez contrôler la façon dont nous utilisons et partageons ces informations. Il vous informe des informations que les professionnels de la santé ou les autres membres peuvent voir lorsque vous utilisez nos sites et services. Il vous informe de vos droits et choix concernant vos informations personnelles et de la manière dont vous pouvez nous contacter si vous avez des questions ou des préoccupations.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">L\'APPLICATION MOBILE ET&nbsp;LE SITE WEB KACI&nbsp;COLLECTERONT&nbsp;ET TRANSMETTERONT DES INFORMATIONS PERSONNELLES, MÉDICALES ET RELATIVES À LA SANTÉ VOUS CONCERNANT. EN UTILISANT L\'APPLICATION&nbsp;ET NOTRE SITE WEB, VOUS ACCEPTEZ QUE NOUS POUVONS COLLECTER ET UTILISER VOS INFORMATIONS PERSONNELLES ET AUTRES COMME DÉCRIT DANS LA POLITIQUE DE CONFIDENTIALITÉ DE CE SITE. SI VOUS N\'ÊTES PAS D\'ACCORD, VEUILLEZ NE PAS UTILISER L\'APPLICATION ET NOTRE SITE WEB.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>VOUS DEVEZ AVOIR 10&nbsp;ANS&nbsp;OU PLUS POUR&nbsp;UTILISER LES SERVICES KACI&nbsp;.</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2.&nbsp;Définitions importantes</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1&nbsp;«&nbsp;Informations personnelles&nbsp;» dans la présente politique de confidentialité, désigne les informations vous concernant qui vous sont personnellement identifiables, telles que vos informations de contact ( par exemple , nom, adresse, adresse e-mail ou numéro de téléphone), des informations médicales ou de santé personnellement identifiables («&nbsp;Informations sur la santé ”),&nbsp;identification personnelle&nbsp;documents (tels que permis de conduire, carte d\'électeur, etc.)&nbsp;et toute autre information non publique associée à ces informations.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">«&nbsp;Informations anonymisées&nbsp;» désigne les informations qui ne sont ni utilisées ni destinées à être utilisées pour identifier personnellement un individu.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2&nbsp;Informations que nous recevons ou collectons auprès de vous</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Données d\'inscription&nbsp;: Lorsque vous vous inscrivez ou créez un compte, vous nous fournissez certaines informations, notamment votre adresse e-mail, votre numéro de téléphone, votre date de naissance, votre sexe et votre code postal (les «&nbsp;Données d\'inscription&nbsp;»), ainsi que comme mot de passe pour votre compte.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Informations de paiement : Si vous choisissez d\'utiliser un service payant&nbsp;tel que la publicité ou de faire un don&nbsp;, il vous sera demandé de fournir (au minimum) votre nom et vos informations de paiement, y compris les informations de carte de paiement («&nbsp;<em>Informations de paiement&nbsp;</em>»). Un fournisseur de services tiers qui gère les paiements pour nous recevra également les informations de votre carte de paiement.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Informations que vous choisissez de nous fournir : Vous avez la possibilité de fournir une variété d\'informations lors de vos interactions avec nous et l\'assistant et l\'application Kaci Automated, tels que les e-mails que vous pouvez nous envoyer, les informations auxquelles vous répondez et les e-mails ou newsletters. que vous vous inscrivez pour recevoir. Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App ou des tiers agissant en notre nom reçoivent des données de votre part chaque fois que vous nous fournissez des informations.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Coordonnées&nbsp;: si vous choisissez de participer à des études de recherche ou de vous inscrire à certaines fonctionnalités, vous pouvez nous fournir, et nous pouvons collecter, vos coordonnées, y compris votre nom, votre adresse postale et votre numéro de téléphone («&nbsp;Coordonnées&nbsp;» ).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Données anonymisées. Nous utilisons des données anonymisées pour la recherche et le développement de nouveaux produits ou outils, pour affiner nos algorithmes et nos applications d\'apprentissage automatique, et pour améliorer l\'application et les services que nous fournissons. Nous pouvons divulguer ces informations publiquement et à des tiers, par exemple, dans des rapports publics sur la santé, à des partenaires sous contrat avec nous, ou dans des informations de référence que nous fournissons à la communauté médicale.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3&nbsp;Informations que nous recevons de tiers</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Comptes de réseaux sociaux&nbsp;: nous pouvons obtenir des informations personnelles vous concernant&nbsp;via l\'application mobile ou d\'autres&nbsp;services de réseaux sociaux tiers, tels que Facebook et Twitter, si vous choisissez de lier nos services à des comptes de réseaux sociaux tiers (\"Compte de réseaux sociaux ”) soit : (i) en nous fournissant les informations de connexion de votre Compte de Réseaux Sociaux via les Services ; ou (ii) nous permettant d\'accéder à votre compte de médias sociaux, comme le permettent les conditions générales applicables qui régissent votre utilisation du compte de médias sociaux respectif.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4&nbsp;Informations que nous collectons via la technologie</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Activité sur l\'application, l\'assistant automatisé et nos sites Web&nbsp;: nous pouvons suivre certaines des actions que vous effectuez sur l\'application, l\'assistant automatisé et nos sites Web, telles que le contenu des recherches que vous effectuez via l\'application mobile&nbsp;ou&nbsp;sur l\'application, l\'assistant automatisé et notre site Web.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Accéder aux informations sur l\'appareil et le navigateur&nbsp;: lorsque vous accédez à l\'application, à l\'assistant automatisé et à notre site Web à partir d\'un ordinateur ou d\'un autre appareil, nous pouvons collecter des informations anonymes à partir de cet appareil, telles que votre adresse de protocole Internet, le type de navigateur, la vitesse de connexion et l\'accès. fois (collectivement, les «&nbsp;Informations anonymes&nbsp;»).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Cookies&nbsp;: nous pouvons utiliser à la fois des cookies de session (qui expirent une fois que vous fermez votre navigateur Web) et des cookies persistants pour rendre l\'application, l\'assistant automatisé et notre site Web et nos services plus faciles à utiliser, pour améliorer notre publicité et pour protéger les deux. vous et Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App. Vous pouvez demander à votre navigateur, en modifiant ses options, de ne plus accepter les Cookies ou de vous avertir avant d\'accepter un Cookie des sites que vous visitez. Toutefois, si vous n\'acceptez pas les cookies, vous ne pourrez pas rester connecté à l\'application, à l\'assistant automatisé et à nos sites Web. Nous pouvons également utiliser des pixels pour faciliter l\'utilisation de l\'application, de l\'assistant automatisé et de nos sites Web et services et pour améliorer nos publicités, par exemple en résumant les habitudes d\'utilisation. À l\'heure actuelle, nous n\'honorons pas les demandes «&nbsp;Ne pas suivre&nbsp;» dans toutes les parties de nos sites.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Localisation en temps réel&nbsp;: certaines fonctionnalités de l\'application, de l\'assistant automatisé et de notre site Web utilisent la technologie GPS pour collecter des informations en temps réel sur l\'emplacement de votre appareil afin que l\'application, l\'assistant automatisé et notre site Web puissent vous connecter à un service de sécurité&nbsp;. Agence, services&nbsp;professionnels de la santé&nbsp;ou ambulance&nbsp;service&nbsp;qui&nbsp;_&nbsp;êtes&nbsp;licencié ou autorisé à fournir des Services dans la zone ou la juridiction où vous vous trouvez. Lorsque vous accédez aux services Google Maps sur nos sites, vous acceptez&nbsp;<u>les conditions d\'utilisation&nbsp;</u>et&nbsp;<u>la politique de confidentialité de Google&nbsp;</u>.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Services mobiles&nbsp;: nous pouvons collecter des informations non personnelles à partir de votre appareil mobile ou de votre ordinateur. Ces informations sont généralement utilisées pour nous aider à vous fournir les informations les plus pertinentes. Des exemples d\'informations qui peuvent être collectées et utilisées incluent la façon dont vous utilisez&nbsp;l\'application Kaci, ou la ou&nbsp;les applications&nbsp;r et des informations&nbsp;sur le type d\'appareil ou d\'ordinateur que vous utilisez. De plus, en cas de plantage de nos applications sur votre appareil mobile, nous recevrons des informations sur la version du logiciel de votre modèle d\'appareil mobile et sur l\'opérateur de votre appareil, ce qui nous permet d\'identifier et de corriger les bogues et d\'améliorer les performances de nos applications. .</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3.&nbsp;Comment nous utilisons les informations que nous recevons ou collectons</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1&nbsp;En règle générale, Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App utilise les informations que nous recueillons aux fins suivantes :</div><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pour exploiter, fournir, maintenir, améliorer et améliorer nos Services&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pour comprendre et analyser la façon dont vous utilisez nos Services et pour développer de nouveaux produits, services, caractéristiques et fonctionnalités&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pour personnaliser votre expérience sur nos Services, par exemple en fournissant un contenu personnalisé. Par exemple, nous utilisons votre adresse e-mail pour vous aider à créer, vous connecter et gérer votre compte sur nos Services. Cela nous permet de personnaliser votre expérience et de vous donner des informations pertinentes. Il alimente également les fonctionnalités qui vous aident à mieux comprendre, interagir avec et suivre votre santé et à vous présenter des informations personnalisées et pertinentes&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">À des fins de marketing et de publicité, telles que le développement et la fourniture de matériel promotionnel et publicitaire qui peut être pertinent, précieux ou autrement intéressant pour vous. Nous pouvons également utiliser les informations que nous apprenons à votre sujet pour nous aider à faire la publicité de nos Services sur des sites Web tiers. Lorsque la loi applicable l\'exige, nous ne vous enverrons des communications marketing qu\'avec votre consentement&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pour communiquer avec vous par e-mail, SMS, notifications push et appels téléphoniques, afin de vous fournir des mises à jour et d\'autres informations relatives à nos Services, fournir les informations que vous demandez, répondre aux commentaires et questions, et autrement fournir un support client&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pour faciliter les transactions et les paiements&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pour faciliter la connexion des comptes de médias sociaux à nos services afin de fournir des informations des comptes de médias sociaux à votre profil. En fonction des comptes de médias sociaux que vous choisissez et sous réserve des paramètres de confidentialité que vous avez définis dans ces comptes de médias sociaux, nous accéderons , mettrons à disposition et stockerons (le cas échéant et dans la mesure permise par le service de médias sociaux et autorisé par vous) les informations dans vos comptes de médias sociaux afin qu\'ils soient disponibles sur et via votre profil sur les services&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pour nos besoins commerciaux, tels que les audits, à des fins d\'assurance qualité, pour détecter et prévenir les fraudes et répondre aux problèmes de confiance et de sécurité qui peuvent survenir&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">À des fins de conformité, y compris l\'application de nos&nbsp;<u>conditions d\'utilisation&nbsp;</u>ou d\'autres droits légaux, ou tel que requis par les lois et réglementations applicables ou demandé par toute procédure judiciaire ou agence gouvernementale&nbsp;;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">À d\'autres fins pour lesquelles nous fournissons un avis spécifique au moment où les informations sont collectées&nbsp;; et</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pour agréger ou autrement anonymiser les informations collectées via les Services et les utiliser et les divulguer à d\'autres fins commerciales une fois que les données ne peuvent plus être raisonnablement liées à une personne identifiable.</li></ul><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.2&nbsp;De – Informations Identifiées</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Nous pouvons utiliser des informations anonymisées sans aucune restriction.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.3&nbsp;Informations que vous partagez avec des tiers.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Cette politique de confidentialité s\'applique uniquement aux informations que nous collectons via nos sites et dans les e-mails, SMS et autres communications électroniques établies via ou en relation avec nos sites. Cette politique NE s\'applique PAS aux informations collectées par un tiers. Lorsque vous cliquez sur des liens sur l\'application, l\'assistant automatisé&nbsp;ou&nbsp;notre site Web, vous pouvez quitter notre site. Nous ne sommes pas responsables des pratiques de confidentialité des autres sites et nous vous encourageons à lire leurs déclarations de confidentialité.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>4.&nbsp;Comment nous partageons les informations personnelles que nous collectons</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App peut partager ou autrement divulguer des informations personnelles dans les circonstances décrites ci-dessous.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.1&nbsp;Affiliés : Nous pouvons divulguer des Informations personnelles à nos affiliés ou partenaires pour fournir les Services ou à d\'autres fins pour lesquelles les informations ont été collectées.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.2&nbsp;Fournisseurs et prestataires de services&nbsp;: nous pouvons partager les informations personnelles que nous recevons avec les fournisseurs&nbsp;, les autorités compétentes (services d\'urgence ou forces de l\'ordre à votre demande)&nbsp;et les prestataires de services dans le cadre de la fourniture des services&nbsp;et des fonctionnalités de Kaci&nbsp;. Dans le cas où les informations personnelles sont (a) destinées à être utilisées à des fins matériellement différentes de celles pour lesquelles les informations personnelles ont été initialement collectées ou autorisées par la suite, ou (b) transférées à un tiers agissant en tant que contrôleur de données, les membres aura, lorsque cela est possible et approprié, la possibilité de refuser que des informations personnelles non sensibles soient utilisées ou transférées. Pour les informations sensibles, y compris les informations relatives à la santé, les membres s\'engageront avant une telle utilisation ou un tel transfert.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Dans certains cas, Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App peut faire appel à d\'autres fournisseurs de services pour exécuter des fonctions en notre nom, y compris, mais sans s\'y limiter, les développeurs de sites Web et les fournisseurs de services informatiques.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.3&nbsp;Partenaires d\'analyse&nbsp;: nous pouvons mettre certaines informations personnelles à la disposition de tiers à des fins d\'analyse, notamment&nbsp;: (a) à des fins commerciales ou de marketing pour l\'assistant automatisé Kaci et l\'application, ou (b) pour tirer parti d\'outils tiers pour comprendre les intérêts des membres, les habitudes et les modèles d\'utilisation et/ou les fonctionnalités disponibles via nos Services. Nous ne partageons vos informations personnelles qu\'avec des partenaires d\'analyse pour améliorer nos propres services et/ou vous fournir des soins de santé. Nous ne vendons pas vos informations personnelles aux annonceurs.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.4&nbsp;Tel que requis par la loi et les divulgations similaires&nbsp;: nous pouvons accéder, conserver et divulguer des informations personnelles si nous pensons que cela est nécessaire ou approprié, à notre seule discrétion, pour&nbsp;: (a) nous conformer à toute loi, réglementation, procédure judiciaire ou les demandes gouvernementales, telles qu\'une ordonnance d\'un tribunal ou une convocation, ou autrement coopérer avec les forces de l\'ordre ou les agences gouvernementales&nbsp;; (b) prendre des précautions contre la responsabilité&nbsp;; (c) protéger vos droits, votre propriété ou votre sécurité, les nôtres ou ceux d\'autrui&nbsp;; (d) enquêter et nous défendre contre toute réclamation ou allégation de tiers&nbsp;; et (e) protéger la sécurité ou l\'intégrité de nos Services et de toute installation ou équipement utilisé pour rendre nos Services disponibles. Pour éviter tout doute, la divulgation d\'informations personnelles peut se produire si vous publiez un contenu répréhensible sur ou via les services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.5&nbsp;Services de médias sociaux&nbsp;: nos services peuvent vous permettre, sur votre demande, de partager des informations personnelles avec certains services de médias sociaux, tels que Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest et Google Plus. Veuillez tenir compte de tout impact sur votre vie privée et votre anonymat lorsque vous publiez du contenu sur tous les services de médias sociaux. Vous comprenez et acceptez que l\'utilisation des informations personnelles par tout service de médias sociaux sera régie par les politiques de confidentialité respectives de ces services de médias sociaux et vos paramètres sur leurs plateformes. Nous vous encourageons à consulter leurs politiques de confidentialité.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.6&nbsp;Marketing&nbsp;: Nous ne louons, ne vendons ni ne partageons les informations personnelles vous concernant avec des sociétés non affiliées à des fins de marketing direct, sauf si nous avons votre autorisation.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.7&nbsp;Fusions, ventes ou autres transferts d\'actifs&nbsp;: nous pouvons divulguer et autrement transférer des informations personnelles à des prestataires de services, des conseillers, des partenaires transactionnels potentiels ou d\'autres tiers dans le cadre de l\'examen, de la négociation ou de l\'achèvement d\'une transaction d\'entreprise dans laquelle nous sommes acquis par ou fusionné avec une autre société ou nous vendons, liquidons ou transférons tout ou partie de nos actifs.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>5.&nbsp;Sécurité et intégrité des données</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.1&nbsp;Sécurité des données : Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App fait des efforts commercialement raisonnables pour protéger les informations personnelles en utilisant des protections physiques et électroniques conçues pour protéger l\'intégrité et la sécurité des informations personnelles que nous conservons. Nous prenons des précautions commercialement raisonnables, compte tenu des risques liés au traitement et de la nature des informations personnelles, conçues pour protéger les informations personnelles contre la perte, l\'utilisation abusive et l\'accès non autorisé, la divulgation, l\'altération et la destruction. Cependant, comme aucune transmission ou stockage électronique de renseignements personnels ne peut être entièrement sécurisé, nous ne pouvons offrir aucune garantie quant à la sécurité ou à la confidentialité des renseignements personnels.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.2&nbsp;Intégrité des données&nbsp;: nous utilisons les informations que nous collectons de manière pertinente et compatible avec l\'objectif pour lequel ces informations ont été collectées ou nous ont été fournies, comme indiqué dans la présente politique. Nous prendrons des mesures pour nous assurer que toutes les informations collectées, traitées et/ou stockées sont protégées contre la destruction, la corruption ou l\'utilisation d\'une manière incompatible avec nos politiques ou le but pour lequel nous les avons reçues.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>6.&nbsp;Notre politique concernant les enfants</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App interdit l\'enregistrement et ne collecte pas sciemment des informations personnelles de toute personne de moins de 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;ans.&nbsp;Toutefois, les&nbsp;informations personnelles sensibles relatives à un enfant&nbsp;de moins de&nbsp;18 ans ne peuvent&nbsp;être&nbsp;collectées qu\'à l\'aide d\'un compte créé et géré par un parent ou tuteur majeur. Si nous apprenons que nous avons collecté des informations auprès d\'un enfant de moins de 10 ans,&nbsp;nous&nbsp;prendrons toutes les mesures nécessaires pour supprimer ces informations de nos serveurs. Si vous pensez que nous pourrions avoir des informations personnelles sur un enfant de moins de 10 ans&nbsp;,&nbsp;veuillez contacter notre équipe&nbsp;à info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>7.&nbsp;Conservation des informations</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Nous prenons des mesures pour conserver vos informations personnelles pendant une période qui n\'est pas plus longue que nécessaire pour atteindre les objectifs décrits dans la présente politique de confidentialité, à moins qu\'une période de conservation plus longue ne soit requise ou autorisée par la loi. Lors de la détermination de la période de conservation, nous prenons en compte divers critères, tels que le type de Services qui vous sont fournis, la nature et la durée de notre relation avec vous, l\'impact sur les Services que nous vous fournissons si nous supprimons certaines Informations personnelles de ou vous concernant, ainsi que les délais de conservation obligatoires prévus par la loi et le délai de prescription applicable.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>8.&nbsp;Vos droits et choix en matière de confidentialité</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Préférences de partage.&nbsp;</strong>Nous vous fournissons des paramètres pour vous permettre de définir vos préférences de partage pour le contenu que vous publiez sur nos Services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.1&nbsp;Informations de profil facultatives : Vous pouvez ajouter, modifier ou supprimer des informations personnelles facultatives apparaissant dans votre profil à tout moment dans les paramètres de votre compte sous le lien modifier le profil.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.2&nbsp;Informations de compte requises&nbsp;: certaines informations personnelles sont requises pour la fonctionnalité du compte et peuvent être modifiées mais pas supprimées. Par exemple, vous pouvez modifier, mais pas supprimer, l\'adresse e-mail et le mot de passe requis pour la connexion.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.3Dossiers médicaux : Vous pouvez modifier vos informations médicales et ajouter des informations pour rendre vos informations plus précises ou complètes. Par conséquent, si vous souhaitez demander l\'accès ou limiter l\'utilisation ou la divulgation des informations personnelles, veuillez&nbsp;nous contacter&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.4&nbsp;Contenu public&nbsp;: vous pouvez demander la suppression du contenu public en&nbsp;nous contactant.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.5&nbsp;Communications marketing : vous pouvez vous désinscrire de nos communications marketing, telles que les annonces de nouvelles fonctionnalités ou offres spéciales, via le lien fourni dans les e-mails promotionnels.&nbsp;Nous&nbsp;ne partagerons jamais votre adresse e-mail ou d\'autres informations de contact avec des tiers à des fins de marketing sans votre autorisation explicite. Même si vous refusez de recevoir des messages promotionnels de notre part, vous continuerez à recevoir des messages administratifs de notre part.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.6&nbsp;Notifications&nbsp;: nous vous demanderons si vous souhaitez recevoir des notifications lorsque vous ouvrez un compte chez nous. Si vous êtes d\'accord, nous pouvons vous envoyer des e-mails, des SMS ou des notifications push mobiles, vous fournissant des rappels ou des mises à jour liés à votre compte, ou vous informant que vous avez un message sur nos Services. Vous pouvez vous désinscrire à tout moment en ajustant vos paramètres de notification dans la page des paramètres.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.7&nbsp;Ne pas suivre : Il n\'existe aucune norme acceptée sur la façon de répondre aux signaux Ne pas suivre, et nous ne répondons pas à ces signaux.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.8&nbsp;Déconnectez-vous de&nbsp;votre compte : vous pouvez désactiver votre compte à tout moment. Pour ce faire, connectez-vous, accédez à la page des paramètres et choisissez l\' option&nbsp;de déconnexion&nbsp;. Vos questions publiques ayant reçu des réponses continueront d\'apparaître de manière anonyme sur nos Services même si vous désactivez votre compte.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>9.&nbsp;Modifications de cette politique</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.1&nbsp;Nous continuerons d\'évaluer cette politique par rapport aux nouvelles technologies, aux pratiques commerciales, aux modifications de la législation et aux besoins de nos membres, et nous pourrons apporter des modifications à la politique en conséquence. Veuillez consulter cette page périodiquement pour les mises à jour. Si nous apportons des modifications importantes à cette politique, nous publierons les conditions mises à jour de la politique sur les Services et vous informerons de ces modifications, qui peuvent inclure un avis par e-mail via un message envoyé à l\'adresse e-mail que vous utilisez pour accéder au Prestations de service.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.2&nbsp;Toute modification importante de cette politique entrera en vigueur dans les trente (30) jours calendaires suivant l\'envoi d\'un avis par courrier électronique. Ces modifications entreront en vigueur immédiatement pour les nouveaux utilisateurs des Services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.3&nbsp;Veuillez noter qu\'à tout moment, vous êtes responsable de la mise à jour de vos informations afin de nous fournir votre adresse e-mail la plus récente. Dans le cas où la dernière adresse e-mail que vous nous avez fournie n\'est pas valide ou, pour quelque raison que ce soit, n\'est pas en mesure de vous envoyer l\'avis décrit ci-dessus, notre envoi de l\'e-mail contenant cet avis constituera néanmoins un avis effectif des changements décrits. dans l\'avis.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.4&nbsp;Si vous ne souhaitez pas autoriser les changements dans notre utilisation de vos informations, vous devez nous informer avant la date d\'entrée en vigueur des changements que vous souhaitez désactiver votre compte.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.5&nbsp;L\'utilisation continue des Services après notification de tels changements indiquera que vous reconnaissez ces changements et que vous acceptez d\'être lié par les termes et conditions de ces changements.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>10.&nbsp;Gouvernance</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.1&nbsp;Application : Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App effectuera des audits de conformité de nos pratiques de confidentialité pertinentes pour vérifier le respect de cette politique. De plus, nous mènerons des enquêtes de suivi pour vérifier que les attestations et les affirmations concernant nos pratiques de confidentialité sont exactes. Vous pouvez vous renseigner sur une inexactitude ou déposer une plainte concernant une violation potentielle auprès de nous via les coordonnées fournies ci-dessous. Nous organisons des formations pour soutenir la mise en œuvre et le respect de nos pratiques de confidentialité&nbsp;; tout employé dont nous déterminons qu\'il enfreint cette politique peut faire l\'objet de mesures disciplinaires.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.2&nbsp;Résolution des litiges : Les questions ou préoccupations concernant notre utilisation ou divulgation d\'informations peuvent être adressées à notre équipe&nbsp;à info@kaci.help&nbsp;.&nbsp;Nous&nbsp;enquêterons et tenterons de résoudre les plaintes et les litiges concernant l\'utilisation et la divulgation d\'informations conformément aux principes contenus dans cette politique. Tout litige concernant cette politique sera résolu en suivant les mécanismes de résolution des litiges décrits dans nos conditions d\'utilisation.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>11.&nbsp;Assistance et commentaires</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Si vous avez des questions ou souhaitez obtenir des précisions sur l\'application, l\'assistant automatisé et nos sites Web ou services, veuillez nous contacter à&nbsp;info@kaci.help.&nbsp;Nous aimons avoir de vos nouvelles. Si vous avez une idée qui peut améliorer les commentaires de Kaci concernant nos services, contactez-&nbsp;nous&nbsp;à&nbsp;info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 05:21:23');
INSERT INTO `setting` (`id`, `language`, `type`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(31, 'Portuguese', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci&nbsp;, Aplicativo Móvel&nbsp;(“&nbsp;<strong>nós&nbsp;</strong>”, “&nbsp;<strong>nosso&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;, “&nbsp;<strong>Kaci&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;“&nbsp;<strong>Kaci App&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;ou “&nbsp;<strong>nós&nbsp;</strong>”) e suas afiliadas valorizam a privacidade das pessoas que acessam nossos Sites e utilizam nossos Serviços&nbsp;, assim&nbsp;proteger seus dados, privacidade e dados pessoais é muito importante&nbsp;para nós&nbsp;. É de vital importância para nós que nossos clientes (os “&nbsp;<strong>usuários&nbsp;</strong>”) se sintam seguros ao usar nossos produtos e serviços.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Esta política de privacidade (a “&nbsp;<strong>Política de Privacidade&nbsp;</strong>”), juntamente com nossos Termos e Condições, nossa Política de Cookies e quaisquer outros documentos nela referidos, estabelece a base sobre a qual quaisquer dados pessoais que coletamos de você, ou que você nos fornece, serão ser processado. Por favor, leia esta Política de Privacidade cuidadosamente para entender os tipos de dados que coletamos de você, como os usamos, as circunstâncias em que os compartilharemos com terceiros e seus direitos em relação aos seus dados pessoais.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Você pode usar o “Kaci” por meio de nosso Aplicativo Móvel (o “&nbsp;<strong>Aplicativo&nbsp;</strong>”)&nbsp;.&nbsp;Esta Política de Privacidade descreve nosso processamento de dados ao usar nosso&nbsp;aplicativo&nbsp;ou simplesmente acessar nosso site Kaci.help (o “&nbsp;<strong>site&nbsp;</strong>”) ou qualquer serviço e/ou produto que possamos fornecer a você (site junto com o aplicativo móvel e qualquer um de nossos produtos e serviços, os “&nbsp;<strong>Serviços</strong>”). Quando certas atividades de processamento estiverem relacionadas apenas a um produto específico, como o App ou a solução Enterprise, isso será claramente indicado.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Quem somos</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Esta Política de Privacidade se aplica a quaisquer dados pessoais processados pela Kaci&nbsp;ou pela Factcheck Initiative,&nbsp;sendo o controlador de dados de todas as atividades de processamento relacionadas aos Serviços&nbsp;oferecidos no Kaci Mobile Application ou no Kaci Website&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Perguntas, comentários e solicitações referentes a esta Política de Privacidade são bem-vindos e devem ser encaminhados para nosso&nbsp;balcão de informações info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Esta política de privacidade explica a você as informações pessoais que coletamos, como usamos e compartilhamos essas informações e as maneiras pelas quais você pode controlar como usamos e compartilhamos essas informações. Ele informa quais informações os Profissionais de Saúde ou outro membro podem ver quando você usa nossos Sites e Serviços. Ele informa sobre seus direitos e escolhas com relação às suas informações pessoais e como você pode entrar em contato conosco caso tenha alguma dúvida ou preocupação.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">O APLICATIVO MÓVEL&nbsp;DA KACI E&nbsp;O&nbsp;SITE DA WEB COLETARÁ E TRANSMITIRÁ INFORMAÇÕES PESSOAIS, MÉDICAS E DE SAÚDE SOBRE VOCÊ. AO USAR O APLICATIVO&nbsp;E NOSSO SITE, VOCÊ CONCORDA QUE PODEMOS COLETAR E USAR SUAS INFORMAÇÕES PESSOAIS E OUTRAS INFORMAÇÕES CONFORME DESCRITO NA POLÍTICA DE PRIVACIDADE DESTE SITE. SE VOCÊ NÃO CONCORDA, NÃO USE O APLICATIVO E NOSSO SITE.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>VOCÊ DEVE TER 10&nbsp;ANOS&nbsp;OU MAIS PARA&nbsp;USAR OS SERVIÇOS DA KACI&nbsp;.</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2.&nbsp;Definições Importantes</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1&nbsp;\"Informações Pessoais\" nesta Política de Privacidade, significa informações sobre você que são pessoalmente identificáveis para você, como suas informações de contato ( por exemplo , nome, endereço, endereço de e-mail ou número de telefone), informações médicas ou de saúde pessoalmente identificáveis (\"Informações de Saúde ”),&nbsp;identificação pessoal&nbsp;documentos (como carteira de motorista, cartão de eleitor, etc.)&nbsp;e qualquer outra informação não pública associada a tais informações.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">“Informações não identificadas” significa informações que não são usadas nem destinadas a serem usadas para identificar pessoalmente um indivíduo.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2&nbsp;Informações que recebemos ou coletamos de você</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Dados Cadastrais: Ao se registrar ou criar uma conta, você nos fornece certas informações, que incluem seu endereço de e-mail, número de telefone, data de nascimento, sexo e CEP ou código postal (os “Dados Cadastrais”), bem como como uma senha para sua conta.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Informações de pagamento: Se você optar por usar um serviço pago,&nbsp;como publicidade ou fazer uma doação&nbsp;, será solicitado que você forneça (no mínimo) seu nome e informações de pagamento, incluindo informações do cartão de pagamento (“&nbsp;<em>Informações de pagamento&nbsp;</em>”). Um provedor de serviços terceirizado que lida com pagamentos para nós também receberá as informações do seu cartão de pagamento.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Informações que você escolhe nos fornecer: Você pode fornecer uma variedade de informações durante suas interações conosco e com o aplicativo e assistente automatizado Kaci, como e-mails que você pode nos enviar, informações às quais você responde e e-mails ou boletins informativos que você se inscreve para receber. Kaci Automated Assistant &amp; App ou terceiros agindo em nosso nome recebem dados de você sempre que você nos fornece informações.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Informações de contato: Se você optar por participar de estudos de pesquisa ou se inscrever para determinados recursos, poderá nos fornecer e poderemos coletar suas informações de contato, incluindo seu nome, endereço de correspondência e número de telefone (“Informações de contato” ).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Dados não identificados. Usamos dados não identificados para pesquisa e desenvolvimento de novos produtos ou ferramentas, para refinar nossos algoritmos e aplicativos de aprendizado de máquina e para melhorar o aplicativo e os serviços que fornecemos. Podemos divulgar essas informações publicamente e para terceiros, por exemplo, em relatórios públicos sobre saúde, para parceiros sob contrato conosco ou em informações de benchmarking que fornecemos à comunidade médica.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3&nbsp;Informações que recebemos de terceiros</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Contas de mídia social: podemos obter informações pessoais sobre você&nbsp;por meio do aplicativo móvel ou de outros&nbsp;serviços de mídia social de terceiros, como Facebook e Twitter, se você optar por vincular nossos serviços a contas de mídia social de terceiros (“Conta de mídia social ”) ao: (i) fornecer as informações de login da sua conta de mídia social para nós por meio dos Serviços; ou (ii) nos permitindo acessar sua conta de mídia social, conforme permitido pelos termos e condições aplicáveis que regem o uso da respectiva conta de mídia social.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4&nbsp;Informações que coletamos por meio da tecnologia</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Atividade no aplicativo, no assistente automático e em nossos sites: podemos acompanhar algumas das ações que você executa no aplicativo, no assistente automático e em nossos sites, como o conteúdo das pesquisas que você realiza por meio do aplicativo móvel&nbsp;ou&nbsp;em o aplicativo, o assistente automatizado e nosso site.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Acessar informações do dispositivo e do navegador: quando você acessa o aplicativo, o assistente automatizado e nosso site a partir de um computador ou outro dispositivo, podemos coletar informações anônimas desse dispositivo, como seu endereço de protocolo de Internet, tipo de navegador, velocidade de conexão e acesso vezes (coletivamente, “Informações Anônimas”).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Cookies: Podemos usar cookies de sessão (que expiram quando você fecha o navegador da web) e cookies persistentes para tornar o aplicativo, o assistente automatizado e nosso site e serviços mais fáceis de usar, para melhorar nossa publicidade e proteger ambos você e o aplicativo e assistente automatizado Kaci. Você pode instruir seu navegador, alterando suas opções, para parar de aceitar Cookies ou avisá-lo antes de aceitar um Cookie dos sites que você visita. Se você não aceitar Cookies, no entanto, não poderá permanecer conectado ao aplicativo, ao assistente automatizado e aos nossos sites. Também podemos usar Pixels para tornar o aplicativo, o assistente automatizado e nossos sites e Serviços mais fáceis de usar e melhorar nossa publicidade, por exemplo, resumindo os padrões de uso. No momento, não atendemos solicitações de “Não Rastrear” em todas as partes de nossos Sites.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Localização em tempo real: Certos recursos do aplicativo, do assistente automático e do nosso site usam a tecnologia GPS para coletar informações em tempo real sobre a localização do seu dispositivo para que o aplicativo, o assistente automático e nosso site possam conectá-lo a&nbsp;um Agência, Serviços&nbsp;Profissionais de Saúde&nbsp;ou Ambulância&nbsp;serviço&nbsp;que&nbsp;_&nbsp;são&nbsp;licenciados ou autorizados a fornecer Serviços na área ou jurisdição onde você está localizado. Ao acessar os serviços do Google Maps em nossos Sites, você concorda com&nbsp;<u>os Termos de Serviço&nbsp;</u>e&nbsp;<u>a Política de Privacidade do Google&nbsp;</u>.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Serviços Móveis: Podemos coletar informações não pessoais de seu dispositivo móvel ou computador. Essas informações geralmente são usadas para nos ajudar a fornecer as informações mais relevantes para você. Exemplos de informações que podem ser coletadas e usadas incluem como você usa&nbsp;o aplicativo Kaci, ou&nbsp;seu (&nbsp;s&nbsp;) aplicativo(s) e informações sobre o tipo de dispositivo ou computador que você usa. Além disso, no caso de nosso(s) aplicativo(s) travar em seu dispositivo móvel, receberemos informações sobre a versão do software do modelo do dispositivo móvel e a operadora do dispositivo, o que nos permite identificar e corrigir bugs e melhorar o desempenho de nosso(s) aplicativo(s) .</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3.&nbsp;Como usamos as informações que recebemos ou coletamos</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1&nbsp;Geralmente, o aplicativo e assistente automatizado Kaci usa as informações que coletamos para os seguintes fins:</div><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para operar, fornecer, manter, melhorar e aprimorar nossos Serviços;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para entender e analisar como você usa nossos Serviços e desenvolver novos produtos, serviços, recursos e funcionalidades;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para personalizar sua experiência em nossos Serviços, por exemplo, fornecendo conteúdo personalizado. Por exemplo, usamos seu endereço de e-mail para ajudá-lo a criar, fazer login e gerenciar sua conta em nossos Serviços. Isso nos permite personalizar sua experiência e fornecer informações relevantes. Ele também capacita os recursos que ajudam você a entender melhor, se envolver e monitorar sua saúde e apresentar informações personalizadas e relevantes;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para fins de marketing e publicidade, como desenvolver e fornecer materiais promocionais e publicitários que possam ser relevantes, valiosos ou de interesse para você. Também podemos usar as informações que obtemos sobre você para nos ajudar a anunciar nossos Serviços em sites de terceiros. Quando exigido pela lei aplicável, enviaremos comunicações de marketing apenas com o seu consentimento;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para se comunicar com você por e-mail, mensagens de texto, notificações push e chamadas telefônicas, a fim de fornecer atualizações e outras informações relacionadas aos nossos Serviços, fornecer informações solicitadas, responder a comentários e perguntas e fornecer suporte ao cliente;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Facilitar transações e pagamentos;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para facilitar a conexão de contas de mídia social aos nossos serviços para fornecer informações de contas de mídia social ao seu perfil. Dependendo das contas de mídia social que você escolher e sujeito às configurações de privacidade que você definiu em tais contas de mídia social, iremos acessar, disponibilizar e armazenar (se aplicável e conforme permitido pelo serviço de mídia social e autorizado por você) as informações em suas contas de mídia social para que esteja disponível em e por meio de seu perfil nos serviços;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para nossos fins comerciais, como auditorias, para fins de garantia de qualidade, para encontrar e prevenir fraudes e responder a questões de confiança e segurança que possam surgir;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para fins de conformidade, incluindo a aplicação de nossos&nbsp;<u>Termos de Uso&nbsp;</u>ou outros direitos legais, ou conforme exigido pelas leis e regulamentos aplicáveis ou solicitado por qualquer processo judicial ou agência governamental;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Para outros fins para os quais fornecemos aviso específico no momento em que as informações são coletadas; e</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Agregar ou desidentificar as informações coletadas por meio dos Serviços e usá-las e divulgá-las para outros fins comerciais depois que os dados não puderem mais ser razoavelmente vinculados a uma pessoa identificável.</li></ul><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.2&nbsp;Des – Informações Identificadas</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Podemos usar informações não identificadas sem quaisquer restrições.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.3&nbsp;Informações que você compartilha com terceiros.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Esta Política de Privacidade aplica-se apenas às informações que coletamos por meio de nossos Sites e em e-mail, texto e outras comunicações eletrônicas definidas por meio ou em conexão com nossos Sites. Esta Política NÃO se aplica a informações coletadas por terceiros. Ao clicar em links no aplicativo, no assistente automatizado&nbsp;ou&nbsp;em nosso site, você pode sair do nosso Site. Não somos responsáveis pelas práticas de privacidade de outros sites e encorajamos você a ler suas declarações de privacidade.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>4.&nbsp;Como compartilhamos as informações pessoais que coletamos</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">O aplicativo e assistente automatizado Kaci pode compartilhar ou divulgar informações pessoais nas circunstâncias descritas abaixo.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.1&nbsp;Afiliados: Podemos divulgar Informações Pessoais a nossos afiliados ou parceiros para fornecer os Serviços ou para outros fins para os quais as informações foram coletadas.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.2&nbsp;Fornecedores e provedores de serviços: podemos compartilhar informações pessoais que recebemos com fornecedores&nbsp;, autoridades relevantes (serviços de emergência ou aplicação da lei mediante solicitação)&nbsp;e provedores de serviços relacionados ao fornecimento dos serviços&nbsp;e recursos da Kaci&nbsp;. No caso de as Informações Pessoais (a) serem usadas para uma finalidade materialmente diferente das finalidades para as quais as Informações Pessoais foram originalmente coletadas ou posteriormente autorizadas, ou (b) transferidas para um terceiro atuando como controlador de dados, os Membros será dada, onde for prático e apropriado, a oportunidade de optar por não ter informações pessoais não confidenciais usadas ou transferidas. Para informações confidenciais, incluindo informações relacionadas à saúde, os membros aceitarão antes de tal uso ou transferência.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Em alguns casos, o aplicativo e assistente automatizado da Kaci pode contratar outros provedores de serviços para executar funções em nosso nome, incluindo, entre outros, desenvolvedores de sites e provedores de serviços de TI.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.3&nbsp;Parceiros analíticos: podemos disponibilizar determinadas informações pessoais a terceiros para fins analíticos, incluindo: (a) para fins comerciais ou de marketing do aplicativo e assistente automatizado Kaci, ou (b) para aproveitar ferramentas de terceiros para entender os interesses dos membros, hábitos e padrões de uso e/ou funcionalidade disponíveis por meio de nossos Serviços. Apenas compartilhamos suas informações pessoais com parceiros de análise para melhorar nossos próprios serviços e/ou fornecer assistência médica a você. Não vendemos suas informações pessoais a anunciantes.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.4&nbsp;Conforme exigido por lei e divulgações semelhantes: podemos acessar, preservar e divulgar informações pessoais se acreditarmos que isso é necessário ou apropriado, a nosso exclusivo critério, para: (a) cumprir qualquer lei, regulamento, processo legal ou solicitações governamentais, como uma ordem judicial ou intimação, ou cooperar de outra forma com a aplicação da lei ou agências governamentais; (b) tomar precauções contra a responsabilidade; (c) proteger seus direitos, nossos direitos, propriedade ou segurança de terceiros; (d) investigar e nos defender contra quaisquer reivindicações ou alegações de terceiros; e (e) proteger a segurança ou integridade de nossos Serviços e quaisquer instalações ou equipamentos usados para disponibilizar nossos Serviços. Para evitar dúvidas, a divulgação de Informações Pessoais pode ocorrer se você publicar qualquer conteúdo censurável nos Serviços ou por meio deles.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.5&nbsp;Serviços de mídia social: Nossos serviços podem permitir que você, sob sua orientação, compartilhe informações pessoais com determinados serviços de mídia social, como Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest e Google Plus. Considere qualquer impacto em sua privacidade e anonimato ao postar conteúdo em todo e qualquer serviço de mídia social. Você entende e concorda que o uso de Informações Pessoais por quaisquer serviços de mídia social será regido pelas respectivas políticas de privacidade desses serviços de mídia social e suas configurações em suas plataformas. Nós encorajamos você a revisar suas políticas de privacidade.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.6&nbsp;Marketing: Não alugamos, vendemos ou compartilhamos Informações Pessoais sobre você com empresas não afiliadas para fins de marketing direto, a menos que tenhamos sua permissão.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.7&nbsp;Fusões, Vendas ou Outras Transferências de Ativos: Podemos divulgar e de outra forma transferir Informações Pessoais para prestadores de serviços, consultores, potenciais parceiros transacionais ou outros terceiros em conexão com a consideração, negociação ou conclusão de uma transação corporativa na qual estamos adquiridos ou fundidos com outra empresa ou vendemos, liquidamos ou transferimos todos ou parte de nossos ativos.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>5.&nbsp;Segurança e integridade dos dados</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.1&nbsp;Segurança de Dados: O aplicativo e assistente automatizado Kaci faz esforços comercialmente razoáveis para proteger as Informações Pessoais usando salvaguardas físicas e eletrônicas projetadas para proteger a integridade e a segurança das Informações Pessoais que mantemos. Tomamos precauções comercialmente razoáveis, considerando os riscos envolvidos no processamento e a natureza das Informações Pessoais, destinadas a proteger as Informações Pessoais contra perda, uso indevido e acesso não autorizado, divulgação, alteração e destruição. No entanto, como nenhuma transmissão ou armazenamento eletrônico de Informações Pessoais pode ser totalmente seguro, não podemos dar garantias quanto à segurança ou privacidade das Informações Pessoais.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.2&nbsp;Integridade dos dados: Usamos as informações que coletamos de maneiras relevantes e compatíveis com a finalidade para a qual essas informações foram coletadas ou fornecidas a nós conforme divulgado nesta política. Tomaremos medidas para garantir que todas as informações coletadas, processadas e/ou armazenadas sejam protegidas contra destruição, corrupção ou uso de maneira inconsistente com nossas políticas ou com a finalidade para a qual as recebemos.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>6.&nbsp;Nossa política relativa a crianças</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">O aplicativo e assistente automatizado Kaci proíbe o registro e não coleta intencionalmente informações pessoais de menores de 10&nbsp;anos&nbsp;.&nbsp;No entanto,&nbsp;informações pessoais confidenciais relacionadas a uma criança&nbsp;com menos de 18 anos devem ser coletadas&nbsp;apenas por meio de uma conta criada e gerenciada por um pai ou responsável adulto. Caso tenhamos conhecimento de que coletamos informações de uma criança com menos de 10&nbsp;anos&nbsp;, tomaremos todas as medidas necessárias para remover essas informações de nossos servidores. Se você acredita que podemos ter qualquer informação pessoal de uma criança com menos de 10 anos&nbsp;,&nbsp;entre em contato com nossa equipe&nbsp;em info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>7.&nbsp;Retenção de informações</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Tomamos medidas para reter suas Informações Pessoais por um período que não seja mais do que o necessário para cumprir os propósitos descritos nesta Política de Privacidade, a menos que um período de retenção mais longo seja exigido ou permitido por lei. Ao determinar o período de retenção, levamos em consideração vários critérios, como o tipo de Serviços prestados a você, a natureza e a duração de nosso relacionamento com você, o impacto nos Serviços que prestamos a você se excluirmos algumas Informações Pessoais de ou sobre você e os períodos de retenção obrigatórios previstos em lei e o respectivo estatuto de limitações.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>8.&nbsp;Seus direitos e escolhas de privacidade</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Preferências de Compartilhamento.&nbsp;</strong>Fornecemos configurações para permitir que você defina suas preferências de compartilhamento para o conteúdo que você publica em nossos Serviços.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.1&nbsp;Informações de perfil opcionais: você pode adicionar, editar ou excluir informações pessoais opcionais que aparecem em seu perfil a qualquer momento nas configurações de sua conta no link editar perfil.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.2&nbsp;Informações de conta necessárias: certas informações pessoais são necessárias para a funcionalidade da conta e podem ser editadas, mas não excluídas. Por exemplo, você pode editar, mas não remover, o endereço de e-mail e a senha necessários para o login.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.3Registros de saúde: você pode alterar suas informações de saúde e adicionar informações para torná-las mais precisas ou completas. Assim, se você deseja solicitar acesso ou limitar o uso ou divulgação de Informações Pessoais, entre em contato&nbsp;conosco&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.4&nbsp;Conteúdo público: você pode solicitar a remoção do Conteúdo público entrando em contato&nbsp;conosco.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.5&nbsp;Comunicações de marketing: você pode cancelar a assinatura de nossas comunicações de marketing, como anúncios de novos recursos ou ofertas especiais, por meio do link fornecido nos e-mails promocionais. Nunca&nbsp;compartilharemos&nbsp;seu endereço de e-mail ou outras informações de contato com terceiros para fins de marketing sem sua permissão explícita. Mesmo que você opte por não receber nossas mensagens promocionais, continuará recebendo nossas mensagens administrativas.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.6&nbsp;Notificações: Perguntaremos se você deseja receber notificações quando abrir uma conta conosco. Se você concordar, podemos enviar notificações por e-mail, SMS ou celular, fornecendo lembretes ou atualizações relacionadas à conta ou informando que você tem uma mensagem em nossos Serviços. Você pode cancelar a qualquer momento ajustando suas configurações de notificação na página de configurações.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.7&nbsp;Não Rastrear: Não há um padrão aceito sobre como responder aos sinais Não Rastrear, e não respondemos a esses sinais.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.8&nbsp;Sair da&nbsp;sua conta: você pode desativar sua conta a qualquer momento. Para fazer isso, faça login, vá para a página de configurações e escolha a opção de&nbsp;logout&nbsp;. Suas perguntas públicas que receberam respostas continuarão a aparecer anonimamente em nossos Serviços, mesmo que você desative sua conta.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>9.&nbsp;Alterações a esta Política</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.1&nbsp;Continuaremos avaliando esta política em relação a novas tecnologias, práticas de negócios, mudanças na lei e necessidades de nossos membros, e podemos fazer alterações na política de acordo. Por favor, verifique esta página periodicamente para atualizações. Se fizermos alterações materiais nesta política, publicaremos os termos atualizados da política nos Serviços e notificaremos você sobre essas alterações, que podem incluir aviso por e-mail por meio de uma mensagem enviada ao endereço de e-mail que você usa para acessar o Serviços.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.2&nbsp;Quaisquer alterações materiais a esta política entrarão em vigor dentro de trinta (30) dias corridos após o envio de um aviso por e-mail para você. Essas alterações entrarão em vigor imediatamente para novos usuários dos Serviços.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.3&nbsp;Observe que, em todos os momentos, você é responsável por atualizar suas informações para nos fornecer seu endereço de e-mail mais atual. Caso o último endereço de e-mail que você nos forneceu não seja válido ou, por qualquer motivo, não seja capaz de enviar a você o aviso descrito acima, nosso envio do e-mail contendo tal aviso constituirá, no entanto, um aviso efetivo das alterações descritas no aviso.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.4&nbsp;Se você não deseja permitir alterações em nosso uso de suas informações, você deve nos notificar antes da data efetiva das alterações que deseja desativar sua conta.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.5&nbsp;O uso continuado dos Serviços após a notificação de tais alterações indicará seu reconhecimento de tais alterações e concordância em se vincular aos termos e condições de tais alterações.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>10.&nbsp;Governança</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.1&nbsp;Aplicação: O aplicativo e assistente automatizado da Kaci conduzirá auditorias de conformidade de nossas práticas de privacidade relevantes para verificar a adesão a esta política. Além disso, conduziremos investigações de acompanhamento para verificar se os atestados e afirmações sobre nossas práticas de privacidade são precisos. Você pode perguntar sobre uma imprecisão ou fazer uma reclamação sobre uma possível violação por meio das informações de contato fornecidas abaixo. Nós nos envolvemos em treinamento para apoiar a implementação e conformidade com nossas práticas de privacidade; qualquer funcionário que determinarmos estar violando esta política pode estar sujeito a ação disciplinar.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.2&nbsp;Resolução de disputas: Dúvidas ou preocupações sobre nosso uso ou divulgação de informações podem ser direcionadas à nossa equipe&nbsp;em info@kaci.help&nbsp;.&nbsp;Investigaremos&nbsp;e tentaremos resolver reclamações e disputas relacionadas ao uso e divulgação de informações de acordo com os princípios contidos nesta política. Qualquer disputa referente a esta Política deve ser resolvida seguindo os mecanismos de resolução de disputas descritos em nossos Termos de Uso.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>11.&nbsp;Suporte e feedback</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Se você tiver alguma dúvida ou quiser mais esclarecimentos sobre o aplicativo, o assistente automatizado e nossos sites ou serviços, entre em contato conosco pelo e-mail&nbsp;info@kaci.help.&nbsp;Nós gostamos de ouvir de você. Se você tem uma ideia que pode melhorar o feedback da Kaci sobre nossos serviços, entre em contato&nbsp;conosco&nbsp;pelo&nbsp;e-mail info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 10:09:04');
INSERT INTO `setting` (`id`, `language`, `type`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(32, 'Pidgin', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Website, Mobile Application (\"us\", \"our\", \"Kaci\", \"Kaci App\", or \"we\") and its affiliates dey value the privacy of individuals wey dey access our Sites and dey use our Services. E dey very important to us say we dey protect your data, privacy, and personal information. E dey very important to us say our customers (wey be \"users\") feel secure when dem dey use our products and services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This privacy policy (wey dem dey call \"Privacy Policy\"), together with our Terms &amp; Conditions, our Cookie Policy, and any other documents wey dem refer inside, e show the basis wey any personal data wey we collect from you, or wey you give us, go dey processed. Make you read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand the kind of data we dey collect from you, how we dey use am, the conditions under which we go share am with third parties, and your rights regarding your personal data.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">You fit use \"Kaci\" through our Mobile Application (wey dem dey call the \"App\"). This Privacy Policy dey explain how we go process your data when you use our App or wen you access our website wey be Kaci.help (wey dem dey call the \"Website\"), or any service and/or product wey we fit give you (Website together with the Mobile Application and any other product and services wey we fit provide, the \"Services\"). If some processing activities relate only to a specific product like the App or the Enterprise solution, e go dey clearly indicated.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Who we be</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This Privacy Policy apply to any personal data wey Kaci or Factcheck Initiative process, wey be the data controller of all the activities wey dey involved with the Services wey dem offer for the Kaci Mobile Application, or the Kaci Website. If you get questions, comments, or requests about this Privacy Policy, make you contact us through our information desk at info@kaci.help.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This privacy policy explain the kind of personal information wey we dey collect, how we dey use and share that information, and the ways wey you fit control how we dey use and share that information. E inform you about wetin the Healthcare Professionals or any other member fit see wen you use our Sites and Services. E tell you about your rights and choices regarding your personal information, and how you fit contact us if you get questions or concerns.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">KACI MOBILE APPLICATION &amp; WEBSITE GO DEY COLLECT AND SEND PERSONAL, MEDICAL, AND HEALTH-RELATED INFORMATION ABOUT YOU. IF YOU USE THE APP AND OUR WEBSITE, YOU AGREE SAY WE FIT COLLECT AND USE YOUR PERSONAL AND OTHER INFORMATION AS WEY WE DESCRIBE INSIDE THIS SITE PRIVACY POLICY. IF YOU NO AGREE, ABEG NO USE THE APP AND OUR WEBSITE.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">YOU MUST BE 10 YEARS OR OLDER TO USE KACI’S SERVICES.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2. Important Definitions</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1 \"Personal Information\" for this Privacy Policy, na information about you wey fit identify you personally, like your contact information (e.g. name, address, email address, or telephone number), personally identifiable health or medical information (\"Health Information\"), personal identification documents (like driver’s license, voter’s card etc.), and any other non-public information wey dey relate to that information.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">\"De-Identified Information\" na information wey dem no dey use or wan use to personally identify one individual.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2 Information wey We Collect or Receive from You</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a) Registration Data: When you register or create one account, you go give us some information, wey include your email address, telephone number, date of birth, gender, and zip or postal code (the \"Registration Data\"), plus password for your account.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b) Payment Information: If you choose to use fee-based Service like advertisement or make donation, we go ask you to provide (at least) your name and payment information wey include payment card information (\"Payment Information\"). Another service provider wey dey handle payments for us go collect your payment card information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c) Information wey You Choose to Give Us: You get the power to give us different kinds of information during your interactions with us and the Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App, like the emails wey you fit send us, information wey you respond to, and the emails or newsletters wey you sign up to receive. Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App or third parties wey dey act on our behalf go collect data from you anytime you provide us with information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d) Contact Information: If you choose to participate for research studies, or sign up for certain features, you fit provide us, and we fit collect, your contact information, like your name, mailing address, and phone number (\"Contact Information\").</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e) De-identified Data: We fit use de-identified data for research</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;and development of new products or tools, to refine our algorithms and machine learning applications, and to improve the App and the services wey we provide. We fit also share this kind of information publicly and to third parties, for example, in public reports about health, to partners under agreement with us, or in benchmarking information wey we give the medical community.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3 Information wey We Receive from Third Parties</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a) Social Media Accounts: We fit collect Personal Information about you through the Mobile Application, or other third-party social media services like Facebook and Twitter, if you choose to link our Services with third-party social media accounts (\"Social Media Account\") either by: (i) providing your Social Media Account login information to us through the Services; or (ii) allowing us to access your Social Media Account, as e dey permitted under the terms and conditions wey govern your use of the respective Social Media Account.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4 Information wey we collect using technology</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a) Activity on the app, the automated assistant and our websites: We fit track some of the actions wey you take for the app, the automated assistant and our websites, like the searches wey you do through the Mobile Application or for the app, the automated assistant and our website.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b) Access Device and Browser Information: When you access the app, the automated assistant and our website from one computer or another device, we fit collect anonymous information from that device, like your Internet protocol address, browser type, connection speed, and access times (together, \"Anonymous Information\").</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c) Cookies: We fit use both session Cookies (wey expire when you close your web browser) and persistent Cookies to make the app, the automated assistant and our website and Services easy to use, to make our advertising better, and to protect you and Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App. You fit tell your browser, by changing the settings, to stop am from accepting Cookies or to prompt you before you accept a Cookie from the websites wey you dey visit. If you no accept Cookies, you no go fit stay logged into the app, the automated assistant, and our websites. We fit also use Pixels to make the app, the automated assistant and our website and Services easy to use and to make our advertising better, for example, by summarizing how people dey use am. For now, we no dey respect \"Do Not Track\" requests for all the parts of our Sites.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d) Real Time Location: Certain features for the app, the automated assistant and our website dey use GPS technology to collect real-time information about the location of your device, so that the app, the automated assistant and our website fit connect you with a Security Agency, Healthcare Professional Services, or Ambulance service wey dey licensed or authorized to provide Services for the area or jurisdiction wey you dey. When you access Google Maps services for our Sites, e mean say you agree to Google\'s Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e) Mobile Services: We fit collect non-personal information from your mobile device or computer. Dem generally use this information to help us give you the most relevant information. Examples of the kind of information wey dem fit collect and use include how you dey use the Kaci app, other applications, and the kind of device or computer wey you use. If our application(s) crash on your mobile device, we go receive information about your mobile device model, software version, and device carrier, so we fit identify and fix bugs and also improve the performance of our application(s).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3. How We Use the Information We Collect or Receive</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1 Generally, Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App use the information wey we collect for the following purposes:</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To operate, provide, maintain, improve, and enhance our Services;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To understand and analyze how you use our Services and to develop new products, services, features, and functionality;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To personalize your experience on our Services, by providing tailored content. For example, we fit use your email address to help you create, log into, and manage your account for our Services. This one go allow us personalize your experience and give you relevant information. E still go make us give you features wey go help you understand, interact with, and track your health, and also give you personalized and relevant information;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For marketing and advertising purposes, like developing and providing promotional and advertising materials wey fit be relevant, valuable, or of interest to you. We fit use the information wey we learn about you to help us advertise our Services on third-party websites. If applicable law require am, we go only send you marketing communications if you give us your consent;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To communicate with you through email, text messages, push notifications, and phone calls, so we fit give you updates and other information wey concern our Services, give you information wey you request, respond to comments and questions, and provide customer support;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To facilitate transactions and payments;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To connect Social Media Accounts to our Services, to provide information from Social Media Accounts to your Profile. Depending on the Social Media Accounts wey you choose, and the privacy settings wey you set for those Social Media Accounts, we go access, make available, and store (if applicable and as e dey permitted by the social media service and authorized by you) the information for your Social Media Accounts so that e go dey available on and through your Profile for the Services;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For our business purposes, like audits, quality assurance, to find and prevent fraud, and to respond to issues wey relate to trust and safety wey fit come up;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For compliance purposes, like enforcing our Terms of Use or other legal rights, or as e fit dey required by applicable laws and regulations or as e fit dey requested by any judicial process or government agency;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For other purposes wey we go provide specific notice for the time wey we collect the information; and</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To aggregate or otherwise de-identify information wey we collect through the Services, and use and share am for other business purposes after the data no fit easily link am to one identifiable person.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.2 De – Identified Information</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">We fit use de-identified information without any restrictions.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.3 Information You Share with Third Parties.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This Privacy Policy apply only to the information wey we collect through our Sites and through email, text, and other electronic communications wey dem set through or in connection with our Sites. This Policy NO APPLY to the information wey dem collect by any third party. If you click on links for the app, the automated assistant, or our website, you fit leave our Site. We no dey responsible for the privacy practices of other sites, and we go advise you to read their privacy statements.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>4. How We Share the Personal Information We Collect</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App fit share or disclose Personal Information under the circumstances wey dem describe below.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.1 Affiliates: We fit disclose Personal Information to our affiliates or partners to provide the Services or for other purposes wey dem collect the information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.2 Vendors and Service Providers: We fit share Personal Information wey we receive with vendors, relevant authority (emergency services or law enforcement upon your request), and service providers, for the provision of the Services and features of Kaci. If the Personal Information suppose be used for one different purpose from the purpose wey dem originally collect am or the purpose wey dem later authorize, or if</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;e suppose dey transferred to one third party wey dey act as data controller, Members go fit opt out (where practical and appropriate) of using or transferring non-sensitive Personal Information. For sensitive information, including health-related information, members go fit opt in before dem use or transfer am. For some cases, Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App fit keep other service providers to perform functions on our behalf, like website developers and IT services providers.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.3 Analytics Partners: We fit make some Personal Information available to third parties for analytics purposes, like: (a) for Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App business or marketing purposes, or (b) to use third-party tools to understand Members’ interests, habits, and usage patterns, and/or functionality wey dey available through our Services. We dey share your Personal Information with analytics partners to improve our own Services and/or to give you healthcare. We no dey sell your Personal Information to advertisers.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.4 As Required by Law and Similar Disclosures: We fit access, keep, and disclose Personal Information if we believe say na so we suppose do, to: (a) comply with any applicable law, regulation, legal process, or government requests, like court order or summons, or to cooperate with law enforcement or government agencies; (b) take measures to prevent liability; (c) protect your, our, or others\' rights, property, or safety; (d) investigate and defend ourselves against any third-party claims or allegations; and (e) protect the security or integrity of our Services and any facilities or equipment wey we dey use to provide our Services. For clarity, we fit disclose Personal Information if you post any objectionable content for or through our Services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.5 Social Media Services: Our Services fit allow you to, based on your direction, share Personal Information with some social media services, like Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, and Google Plus. Abeg think well before you post content to any social media service, as e fit affect your privacy and anonymity. You understand and agree say the use of Personal Information by any social media services go dey subject to the privacy policies wey dey for those social media services and the settings wey you configure for their platforms. We dey encourage you to review their privacy policies.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.6 Marketing: We no dey rent, sell, or share Personal Information about you with companies wey no be our affiliates, for their own direct marketing purposes, unless we get your permission.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.7 Mergers, Sales, or Other Asset Transfers: We fit disclose and transfer Personal Information to service providers, advisors, potential transactional partners, or other third parties, as part of the consideration, negotiation, or completion of any corporate transaction wey involve say we dey acquired by another company, or we dey merge with another company, or we dey sell, liquidate, or transfer all or part of our assets.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>5. Security and Data Integrity</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.1 Data Security: Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App dey make reasonable efforts to protect Personal Information by using physical and electronic safeguards wey dem design to protect the integrity and security of the Personal Information wey we dey keep. We dey take reasonable precautions, considering the risks wey dey involved for the processing and the nature of the Personal Information, to protect am from loss, misuse, and unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. However, as no electronic transmission or storage of Personal Information fit dey completely secure, we no fit guarantee the security or privacy of Personal Information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.2 Data Integrity: We dey use the information wey we collect for ways wey dey relevant and compatible with the purpose wey we collect or provide the information for, as we explain for this policy. We go take steps to ensure say all information wey we collect, process, and/or store dey protected from destruction, corruption, or use in one way wey no dey consistent with our policies or the purpose wey we receive am for.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>6. Our Policy about Children</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App no allow registration or collection of personal information from anybody wey dey under 10 years. However, sensitive personal information wey relate to a child wey dey less than 18 years old fit only dey collected through one account wey an adult parent or guardian set up and dey manage. If we find out say we collect information from a child wey dey under 10 years, we go do everything wey dey necessary to remove that information from our servers. If you believe say we fit get any personal information from a child wey dey under 10, please contact our team at info@kaci.help.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>7. Information Retention</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">We take measures to keep your Personal Information for one period wey no go pass the time wey we need to achieve the purposes wey we outline for this Privacy Policy, unless the law require or permit us to keep am for longer. When we wan decide how long to keep am, we dey consider different criteria, like the kind of Services wey we provide for you, the nature and length of our relationship with you, the effect on the Services wey we provide for you if we delete some Personal Information from or about you, and the mandatory retention periods wey the law provide and the relevant statute of limitations.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>8. Your Privacy Rights and Choices</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Sharing Preferences: We provide you with settings wey go allow you set how you wan share content wey you post for our Services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>9. Changes to this Privacy Policy</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">We fit update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we dey do any material changes to this Privacy Policy we go update you by sending you an email or by placing a prominent notice for our Sites before the change take effect. We go also indicate the \"Last Updated\" date of this Privacy Policy. Make you take time to review any changes for this Policy. Your continued use of our Services after any changes to this Privacy Policy, wey you consent to the practices wey dey described inside this Privacy Policy.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>10. Contact Information</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">If you get any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, you fit contact us by: Email: info@kaci.help</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>11. Consent</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">By using our Services, you consent to the collection, use, and sharing of your Personal Information and other information for the purposes wey we outline inside this Privacy Policy. You consent to receiving text messages from us, including text messages with promotional content, even if you dey on the National Do Not Call Registry. You fit download the Kaci Privacy Policy in PDF format at: [Link to PDF](insert link to PDF here)</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>12. Governing Law</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This Privacy Policy and any disputes wey relate to this Privacy Policy go dey governed by and interpreted in accordance with the laws wey dey for the Federal Republic of Nigeria.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Na the full Privacy Policy be this and e dey very important make you read and understand am well before you agree to use the Kaci App and Services. If you get any further questions or concerns about the Privacy Policy, you fit contact Kaci support for clarification.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 10:01:20');
INSERT INTO `setting` (`id`, `language`, `type`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(33, 'Yoruba', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci&nbsp;, Ohun elo Alagbeka&nbsp;(“&nbsp;<strong>wa&nbsp;</strong>”, “&nbsp;<strong>wa&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;, “&nbsp;<strong>Kaci&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;“&nbsp;<strong>Kaci App&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;tabi “&nbsp;<strong>a&nbsp;</strong>”) ati awọn alafaramo rẹ ṣe idiyele ikọkọ ti awọn ẹni-kọọkan ti o wọle si Awọn oju opo wẹẹbu wa ati lo Awọn iṣẹ wa&nbsp;, nitorinaa&nbsp;yiyi data rẹ, asiri ati data ti ara ẹni ṣe pataki pupọ&nbsp;wa&nbsp;. O ṣe pataki fun wa pe awọn alabara wa (“&nbsp;<strong>awọn olumulo&nbsp;</strong>”) ni aabo nigba lilo awọn ọja ati iṣẹ wa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ilana aṣiri yii (“&nbsp;<strong>Ilana Aṣiri&nbsp;</strong>”), papọ pẹlu Awọn ofin &amp; Awọn ipo, Ilana Kuki wa ati awọn iwe aṣẹ miiran ti a tọka si ninu rẹ, ṣeto ipilẹ eyiti eyikeyi data ti ara ẹni ti a gba lati ọdọ rẹ, tabi ti o pese fun wa, yoo wa ni ilọsiwaju. Jọwọ ka Ilana Aṣiri yii ni pẹkipẹki lati ni oye awọn iru data ti a gba lati ọdọ rẹ, bawo ni a ṣe nlo rẹ, awọn ipo labẹ eyiti a yoo pin pẹlu awọn ẹgbẹ kẹta, ati awọn ẹtọ rẹ ni ibatan si data ti ara ẹni.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">O le lo “Kaci” nipasẹ Ohun elo Alagbeka wa (“&nbsp;<strong>App&nbsp;</strong>”)&nbsp;.&nbsp;Ilana Aṣiri yii ṣapejuwe sisẹ data wa nigba lilo&nbsp;Ohun elo wa,&nbsp;tabi wọle si oju opo wẹẹbu wa nirọrun Kaci.help (“&nbsp;<strong>Oju opo wẹẹbu&nbsp;</strong>”) tabi eyikeyi iṣẹ ati/tabi ọja ti a le pese fun ọ (oju opo wẹẹbu papọ pẹlu Ohun elo Alagbeka ati eyikeyi ọja wa ati awọn iṣẹ, awọn \"&nbsp;<strong>Awọn iṣẹ&nbsp;</strong>\"). Nibiti awọn iṣẹ ṣiṣe kan ti jọmọ ọja kan pato gẹgẹbi App tabi ojutu Idawọlẹ, eyi yoo jẹ itọkasi ni kedere.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Tani awa</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ilana Aṣiri yii kan si eyikeyi data ti ara ẹni ti a ṣe nipasẹ Kaci&nbsp;tabi Factcheck Initiative,&nbsp;jẹ oludari data ti gbogbo awọn iṣẹ ṣiṣe ni asopọ pẹlu Awọn iṣẹ&nbsp;ti a nṣe lori Ohun elo Alagbeka Kaci, tabi Oju opo wẹẹbu Kaci&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Awọn ibeere, awọn asọye ati awọn ibeere nipa Eto Afihan Aṣiri yii jẹ itẹwọgba ati pe o yẹ ki o koju nipasẹ&nbsp;tabili alaye wa info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Eto imulo asiri yii ṣe alaye fun ọ alaye ti ara ẹni ti a gba, bawo ni a ṣe nlo ati pin alaye yẹn, ati awọn ọna ti o le ṣakoso bi a ṣe nlo ati pin alaye yẹn. O sọ fun ọ kini alaye ti Awọn alamọdaju Ilera tabi ọmọ ẹgbẹ miiran le rii nigbati o lo Awọn aaye ati Awọn Iṣẹ wa. O sọ fun ọ ti awọn ẹtọ ati yiyan rẹ pẹlu ọwọ si alaye ti ara ẹni ati bii o ṣe le kan si wa ti o ba ni awọn ibeere tabi awọn ifiyesi.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">KACI&nbsp;ALAGBEKA APPLICATION &amp; WEB&nbsp;SIT&nbsp;E&nbsp;YOO NGBA ATI JIJA TI ara ẹni, Isegun ati Alaye ti o jọmọ ILERA NIPA RẸ. NIPA LILO THE APP&nbsp;ÀTI ÌWÉ ÌWỌ́TỌ́WỌ́ WA, O GBA PÉ A LE GBA ÀTI LO TẸNI TẸNI ÀTI ALAYE MIRAN GẸ́GẸ́gẹ́ bí a ti sàpèjúwe rẹ̀ nínú ìlànà ìpamọ́ ojúlé yìí. TI O KO BA GBA, JOWO MAA LO APP ATI WEBSITETE WA.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>O gbọdọ jẹ ọdun 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;tabi agbalagba lati&nbsp;lo awọn iṣẹ KACI&nbsp;.</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2.&nbsp;Awọn itumọ pataki</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1&nbsp;“Alaye ti ara ẹni” ninu Ilana Aṣiri yii, tumọ si alaye nipa rẹ ti o jẹ idanimọ tikalararẹ fun ọ, gẹgẹbi alaye olubasọrọ rẹ (fun apẹẹrẹ orukọ, adirẹsi, adirẹsi imeeli, tabi nọmba tẹlifoonu), ilera ti ara ẹni tabi alaye iṣoogun (“ Alaye ilera ”),&nbsp;idanimọ ara ẹni&nbsp;awọn iwe aṣẹ (gẹgẹbi iwe-aṣẹ awakọ, kaadi oludibo ati bẹbẹ lọ)&nbsp;ati eyikeyi alaye ti kii ṣe ti gbogbo eniyan ti o ni nkan ṣe pẹlu iru alaye bẹẹ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">\"Iwifun ti a ko mọ\", tumọ si alaye ti a ko lo tabi ti a pinnu lati lo lati ṣe idanimọ ẹni kọọkan.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2&nbsp;Alaye A Gba tabi Gba lati ọdọ Rẹ</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Data Iforukọsilẹ: Nigbati o ba forukọsilẹ tabi ṣẹda akọọlẹ kan, o fun wa ni alaye kan, eyiti o pẹlu adirẹsi imeeli rẹ, nọmba tẹlifoonu, ọjọ ibi, akọ ati abo, ati zip tabi koodu ifiweranṣẹ (“Data Iforukọsilẹ”), bakanna bi ọrọ igbaniwọle fun akọọlẹ rẹ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Alaye Isanwo: Ti o ba yan lati lo Iṣẹ ti o da lori ọya&nbsp;gẹgẹbi ipolowo tabi ṣe ẹbun&nbsp;, ao beere lọwọ rẹ lati pese (ni o kere ju) orukọ rẹ ati alaye isanwo pẹlu alaye kaadi isanwo (“&nbsp;<em>Alaye Isanwo&nbsp;</em>“). Olupese iṣẹ ẹnikẹta ti o mu awọn sisanwo fun wa yoo tun gba alaye kaadi isanwo rẹ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Alaye ti O Yan lati Pese Fun Wa: O ni agbara lati pese ọpọlọpọ alaye lakoko awọn ibaraẹnisọrọ rẹ pẹlu wa ati oluranlọwọ Kaci Automated &amp; App, gẹgẹbi awọn imeeli ti o le firanṣẹ, alaye ti o dahun si, ati awọn imeeli tabi awọn iwe iroyin ti o forukọsilẹ lati gba. Iranlọwọ Kaci Automated &amp; App tabi awọn ẹgbẹ kẹta ti n ṣiṣẹ fun wa gba data lati ọdọ rẹ nigbakugba ti o fun wa ni alaye.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Alaye Olubasọrọ: Ti o ba yan lati kopa ninu awọn iwadii iwadii, tabi forukọsilẹ fun awọn ẹya kan, o le pese wa, ati pe a le gba, alaye olubasọrọ rẹ, pẹlu orukọ rẹ, adirẹsi ifiweranṣẹ, ati nọmba foonu (“Alaye Olubasọrọ” ).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;De-idanimọ Data. A lo data ti a ko mọ fun iwadii ati idagbasoke awọn ọja tabi awọn irinṣẹ tuntun, lati ṣatunṣe awọn algoridimu wa ati awọn ohun elo ikẹkọ ẹrọ, ati lati ṣe ilọsiwaju App ati awọn iṣẹ ti a pese. A le ṣe afihan iru alaye ni gbangba ati si awọn ẹgbẹ kẹta, fun apẹẹrẹ, ni awọn ijabọ gbangba nipa ilera, si awọn alabaṣiṣẹpọ labẹ adehun pẹlu wa, tabi ni alaye isamisi ti a pese si agbegbe iṣoogun.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3&nbsp;Alaye A Gba lati Awọn ẹgbẹ Kẹta</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Awọn akọọlẹ Media Awujọ: A le gba Alaye ti ara ẹni nipa rẹ&nbsp;nipasẹ Ohun elo Alagbeka, tabi&nbsp;awọn iṣẹ media awujọ ẹnikẹta miiran, bii Facebook ati Twitter, ti o ba yan lati sopọ Awọn iṣẹ wa pẹlu awọn akọọlẹ media awujọ ẹnikẹta (“Akọọlẹ Media Social ”) nipa boya: (i) pese alaye iwọle si Account Awujọ Media rẹ si wa nipasẹ Awọn iṣẹ naa; tabi (ii) gbigba wa laaye lati wọle si Akọọlẹ Media Awujọ rẹ, bi a ti gba laaye labẹ awọn ofin ati ipo to wulo ti o ṣakoso lilo rẹ ti Akọọlẹ Awujọ Media oniwun.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4&nbsp;Alaye ti a gba nipasẹ ọna ẹrọ</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Iṣẹ ṣiṣe lori ohun elo, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati awọn oju opo wẹẹbu wa: A le tọju abala diẹ ninu awọn iṣe ti o ṣe lori ohun elo naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati awọn oju opo wẹẹbu wa, gẹgẹbi akoonu ti awọn wiwa ti o ṣe nipasẹ Ohun elo Alagbeka&nbsp;tabi&nbsp;lori app naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati oju opo wẹẹbu wa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Wọle si Ẹrọ ati Alaye ẹrọ aṣawakiri: Nigbati o ba wọle si ohun elo naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati oju opo wẹẹbu wa lati kọnputa tabi ẹrọ miiran, a le gba alaye ailorukọ lati ẹrọ yẹn, gẹgẹbi adirẹsi Ilana Intanẹẹti rẹ, iru ẹrọ aṣawakiri, iyara asopọ ati iraye si igba (lapapọ, \"Anonymous Information\").</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Awọn kuki: A le lo awọn kuki igba mejeeji (eyiti o pari ni kete ti o ba tii ẹrọ aṣawakiri wẹẹbu rẹ) ati Awọn kuki itẹramọṣẹ lati jẹ ki ohun elo naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati oju opo wẹẹbu ati Awọn iṣẹ rọrun lati lo, lati jẹ ki ipolowo wa dara si, ati lati daabobo awọn mejeeji iwọ ati Kaci Aládàáṣiṣẹ Iranlọwọ &amp; App. O le kọ ẹrọ aṣawakiri rẹ, nipa yiyipada awọn aṣayan rẹ, lati da gbigba Awọn kuki duro tabi lati tọ ọ ṣaaju gbigba Kuki kan lati awọn oju opo wẹẹbu ti o ṣabẹwo. Ti o ko ba gba Awọn kuki, sibẹsibẹ, iwọ kii yoo ni anfani lati wọle si ohun elo naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati awọn oju opo wẹẹbu wa. A tun le lo Pixels lati jẹ ki app naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati awọn oju opo wẹẹbu ati Awọn iṣẹ wa rọrun lati lo ati lati jẹ ki ipolowo wa dara julọ nipasẹ, fun apẹẹrẹ, ṣe akopọ awọn ilana lilo. Lọwọlọwọ a ko bu ọla fun awọn ibeere “Maṣe Tọpinpin” ni gbogbo awọn apakan ti Awọn aaye wa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Ipo Akoko Gidi: Awọn ẹya kan ti ohun elo naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati oju opo wẹẹbu wa lo imọ-ẹrọ GPS lati gba alaye ni akoko gidi nipa ipo ẹrọ rẹ ki ohun elo naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati oju opo wẹẹbu wa le so ọ pọ si Aabo&nbsp;kan Ile-ibẹwẹ, Awọn iṣẹ&nbsp;Ọjọgbọn Itọju ilera&nbsp;tabi ọkọ alaisan&nbsp;iṣẹ&nbsp;ti&nbsp;ich&nbsp;ti&nbsp;ni iwe-aṣẹ tabi ni aṣẹ lati pese Awọn iṣẹ ni agbegbe tabi ẹjọ nibiti o wa. Nigbati o ba n wọle si awọn iṣẹ maapu Google lori Awọn aaye wa, o n gba si&nbsp;<u>Awọn ofin Iṣẹ ti Google&nbsp;</u>ati&nbsp;<u>Eto Aṣiri&nbsp;</u>.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Awọn iṣẹ Alagbeka: A le gba alaye ti kii ṣe ti ara ẹni lati ẹrọ alagbeka tabi kọnputa rẹ. Alaye yii ni gbogbogbo lo lati ṣe iranlọwọ fun wa lati fi alaye to wulo julọ fun ọ. Awọn apẹẹrẹ ti alaye ti o le gba ati lo pẹlu bi o ṣe nlo&nbsp;ohun elo Kaci,&nbsp;awọn ohun elo&nbsp;r&nbsp;ati alaye nipa iru ẹrọ tabi kọnputa ti o lo. Ni afikun, ninu iṣẹlẹ ti awọn ohun elo (awọn) wa kọlu lori ẹrọ alagbeka rẹ a yoo gba alaye nipa ẹya sọfitiwia awoṣe ẹrọ alagbeka rẹ ati ti ngbe ẹrọ, eyiti o fun wa laaye lati ṣe idanimọ ati ṣatunṣe awọn idun ati bibẹẹkọ mu iṣẹ ṣiṣe awọn ohun elo wa (awọn) dara si. .</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3.&nbsp;Bii A Ṣe Lo Alaye Ti A Gba tabi Gba</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1&nbsp;Ni gbogbogbo, Kaci Automated Iranlọwọ &amp; App nlo alaye ti a gba fun awọn idi wọnyi:</div><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Lati ṣiṣẹ, pese, ṣetọju, mu dara ati mu Awọn iṣẹ wa pọ si;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Lati loye ati itupalẹ bi o ṣe lo Awọn iṣẹ wa ati lati ṣe agbekalẹ awọn ọja, awọn iṣẹ, awọn ẹya, ati iṣẹ ṣiṣe tuntun;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Lati sọ iriri rẹ di ti ara ẹni lori Awọn iṣẹ wa, gẹgẹbi nipa ipese akoonu ti o baamu. Fun apẹẹrẹ, a lo adirẹsi imeeli rẹ lati ṣe iranlọwọ fun ọ lati ṣẹda, wọle, ati ṣakoso akọọlẹ rẹ lori Awọn iṣẹ wa. Eyi jẹ ki a ṣe adani iriri rẹ ki o fun ọ ni alaye ti o yẹ. O tun ṣe agbara awọn ẹya ti o ṣe iranlọwọ fun ọ lati ni oye daradara, ṣepọ pẹlu, ati tọpa ilera rẹ ati lati ṣafihan fun ọ pẹlu ti ara ẹni, alaye to wulo;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Fun tita ati awọn idi ipolowo, gẹgẹbi idagbasoke ati ipese ipolowo ati awọn ohun elo ipolowo ti o le ṣe pataki, niyelori tabi bibẹẹkọ ti iwulo si ọ. A tun le lo alaye ti a kọ nipa rẹ lati ṣe iranlọwọ fun wa ni ipolowo Awọn iṣẹ wa lori awọn oju opo wẹẹbu ẹnikẹta. Ni ibi ti o nilo labẹ ofin to wulo, a yoo fi awọn ibaraẹnisọrọ tita si ọ nikan pẹlu aṣẹ rẹ;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Lati ṣe ibasọrọ pẹlu rẹ nipasẹ imeeli, awọn ifọrọranṣẹ, awọn iwifunni titari ati awọn ipe foonu, lati le fun ọ ni awọn imudojuiwọn ati alaye miiran ti o jọmọ Awọn iṣẹ wa, pese alaye ti o beere, dahun si awọn asọye ati awọn ibeere, ati bibẹẹkọ pese atilẹyin alabara;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Lati dẹrọ awọn iṣowo ati awọn sisanwo;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Lati dẹrọ asopọ ti Awọn akọọlẹ Media Awujọ si Awọn iṣẹ wa lati pese alaye lati Awọn akọọlẹ Media Awujọ si Profaili rẹ. Da lori Awọn akọọlẹ Media Awujọ ti o yan ati koko-ọrọ si awọn eto ikọkọ ti o ti ṣeto ni iru Awọn akọọlẹ Media Awujọ, a yoo wọle si, jẹ ki o wa ati fipamọ (ti o ba wulo ati bi o ti gba laaye nipasẹ iṣẹ media awujọ ati aṣẹ nipasẹ rẹ) alaye naa ninu Awọn iroyin Awujọ Media rẹ ki o wa lori ati nipasẹ Profaili rẹ lori Awọn iṣẹ;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Fun awọn idi iṣowo wa, gẹgẹbi awọn iṣayẹwo, fun awọn idi idaniloju didara, lati wa ati dena ẹtan, ati dahun si igbẹkẹle ati awọn ọran ailewu ti o le dide;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Fun awọn idi ibamu, pẹlu imuse&nbsp;<u>Awọn ofin Lilo wa&nbsp;</u>tabi awọn ẹtọ ofin miiran, tabi bi o ṣe le nilo nipasẹ awọn ofin ati ilana to wulo tabi ti o beere lọwọ eyikeyi ilana idajọ tabi ile-iṣẹ ijọba;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Fun awọn idi miiran fun eyiti a pese akiyesi kan pato ni akoko ti a gba alaye naa; ati</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Lati ṣajọpọ tabi bibẹẹkọ de-idamọ alaye ti a gba nipasẹ Awọn iṣẹ naa ati lo ati ṣafihan rẹ fun awọn idi iṣowo miiran lẹhin data ko le ṣe sopọ mọ ni deede si eniyan idanimọ.</li></ul><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.2&nbsp;De - Idanimọ Alaye</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">A le lo alaye ti a ko mọ laisi awọn ihamọ eyikeyi.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.3&nbsp;Alaye ti O Pin pẹlu Awọn ẹgbẹ Kẹta.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ilana Aṣiri yii kan si alaye ti a gba nipasẹ Awọn aaye wa ati ni imeeli, ọrọ ati awọn ibaraẹnisọrọ itanna miiran ti a ṣeto nipasẹ tabi ni asopọ pẹlu Awọn aaye wa. Ilana yii KO kan alaye ti o gba nipasẹ ẹnikẹta. Nigbati o ba tẹ awọn ọna asopọ lori ohun elo naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe&nbsp;tabi&nbsp;oju opo wẹẹbu wa o le lọ kuro ni Aye wa. A ko ṣe iduro fun awọn iṣe aṣiri ti awọn aaye miiran, ati pe a gba ọ niyanju lati ka awọn alaye asiri wọn.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>4.&nbsp;Bii a ṣe pin Alaye ti ara ẹni ti a gba</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Oluranlọwọ adaṣe Kaci &amp; App le pin tabi bibẹẹkọ ṣe afihan Alaye Ti ara ẹni ni awọn ipo ti a ṣalaye ni isalẹ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.1&nbsp;Awọn alafaramo: A le ṣafihan Alaye ti ara ẹni si awọn alafaramo wa tabi awọn alabaṣiṣẹpọ lati pese Awọn iṣẹ tabi fun awọn idi miiran fun eyiti a gba alaye naa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.2&nbsp;Awọn olutaja ati Awọn Olupese Iṣẹ: A le pin Alaye ti ara ẹni ti a gba pẹlu awọn onijaja&nbsp;, aṣẹ ti o yẹ (awọn iṣẹ pajawiri tabi agbofinro lori ibeere rẹ)&nbsp;ati awọn olupese iṣẹ ni asopọ pẹlu ipese Awọn iṣẹ&nbsp;ati awọn ẹya ara ẹrọ ti Kaci&nbsp;. Ninu iṣẹlẹ ti Alaye ti ara ẹni jẹ (a) lati ṣee lo fun idi kan ti o yatọ si ohun elo si awọn idi ti eyiti a ti gba Alaye ti Ara ẹni ni akọkọ tabi ti o fun ni aṣẹ lẹhinna, tabi (b) gbe lọ si ẹnikẹta ti n ṣiṣẹ bi oluṣakoso data, Awọn ọmọ ẹgbẹ yoo fun ni, nibiti o wulo ati ti o yẹ, aye lati jade kuro ni nini Alaye Ti ara ẹni ti ko ni imọra ti a lo tabi gbe lọ. Fun alaye ifura, pẹlu alaye ti o ni ibatan ilera, awọn ọmọ ẹgbẹ yoo wọle ṣaaju lilo tabi gbigbe.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ni awọn igba miiran, Kaci Automated Automated &amp; App le ṣe idaduro awọn olupese iṣẹ miiran lati ṣe awọn iṣẹ fun wa, pẹlu, ṣugbọn kii ṣe opin si, awọn olupilẹṣẹ oju opo wẹẹbu ati awọn olupese iṣẹ IT.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.3&nbsp;: A le jẹ ki Alaye ti ara ẹni kan wa si awọn ẹgbẹ kẹta fun awọn idi atupale, pẹlu: (a) fun oluranlọwọ Automated Kaci &amp; Iṣowo Ohun elo tabi awọn idi titaja, tabi (b) lati lo awọn irinṣẹ ẹnikẹta lati loye awọn ifẹ ọmọ ẹgbẹ, awọn aṣa, ati awọn ilana lilo, ati/tabi iṣẹ ṣiṣe ti o wa nipasẹ Awọn iṣẹ wa. A pin Alaye Ti ara ẹni nikan pẹlu awọn alabaṣiṣẹpọ atupale lati mu ilọsiwaju Awọn iṣẹ tiwa ati/tabi lati fi ilera ranṣẹ si ọ. A ko ta Alaye Ti ara ẹni si awọn olupolowo.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.4&nbsp;Gẹgẹ bi Ofin ti beere fun ati Awọn ifihan ti o jọra: A le wọle, tọju, ati ṣafihan Alaye Ti ara ẹni ti a ba gbagbọ pe ṣiṣe bẹ nilo tabi yẹ, ninu lakaye wa nikan, lati: (a) ni ibamu pẹlu eyikeyi ofin to wulo, ilana, ilana ofin tabi awọn ibeere ijọba, gẹgẹbi aṣẹ ile-ẹjọ tabi awọn ipe, tabi bibẹẹkọ ṣe ifowosowopo pẹlu agbofinro tabi awọn ile-iṣẹ ijọba; (b) ṣe awọn iṣọra lodi si layabiliti; (c) daabobo ẹtọ rẹ, tiwa, tabi awọn ẹlomiran, ohun-ini, tabi ailewu; (d) ṣe iwadii ati daabobo ara wa lodi si awọn ẹtọ tabi awọn ẹsun ẹnikẹta; ati (e) daabobo aabo tabi iduroṣinṣin ti Awọn iṣẹ wa ati eyikeyi awọn ohun elo tabi ohun elo ti a lo lati jẹ ki Awọn iṣẹ wa wa. Fun yago fun iyemeji, ifihan ti Alaye ti ara ẹni le waye ti o ba fi akoonu eyikeyi atako sori tabi nipasẹ Awọn iṣẹ naa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.5&nbsp;Awọn iṣẹ Media Awujọ: Awọn iṣẹ wa le gba ọ laaye lati, lori itọsọna rẹ, pin Alaye ti ara ẹni pẹlu awọn iṣẹ media awujọ kan, bii Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, ati Google Plus. Jọwọ ṣe akiyesi ipa eyikeyi lori asiri ati ailorukọ rẹ nigbati o ba nfi akoonu ranṣẹ si eyikeyi ati gbogbo awọn iṣẹ media awujọ. O loye o si gba pe lilo Alaye Ti ara ẹni nipasẹ awọn iṣẹ media awujọ eyikeyi yoo jẹ ijọba nipasẹ awọn eto imulo aṣiri ti awọn iṣẹ media awujọ ati awọn eto rẹ lori awọn iru ẹrọ wọn. A gba ọ niyanju lati ṣe ayẹwo awọn eto imulo ipamọ wọn.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.6&nbsp;Titaja: A ko yalo, ta, tabi pin Alaye ti ara ẹni nipa rẹ pẹlu awọn ile-iṣẹ ti ko ni ibatan fun awọn idi titaja taara wọn, ayafi ti a ba ni igbanilaaye rẹ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.7&nbsp;Iṣakojọpọ, Titaja, tabi Awọn Gbigbe Dukia miiran: A le ṣafihan ati bibẹẹkọ gbe Alaye ti ara ẹni si awọn olupese iṣẹ, awọn oludamoran, awọn alabaṣiṣẹpọ iṣowo ti o pọju , tabi awọn ẹgbẹ kẹta miiran ni asopọ pẹlu ero, idunadura, tabi ipari iṣowo ile-iṣẹ ninu eyiti a wa ninu rẹ. ti gba nipasẹ tabi dapọ pẹlu ile-iṣẹ miiran tabi a ta, oloomi, tabi gbe gbogbo tabi ipin kan ti awọn ohun-ini wa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>5.&nbsp;Aabo ati Data iyege</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.1&nbsp;Aabo Data: Kaci Automated Automated &amp; App ṣe awọn ipa iṣowo ti iṣowo lati daabobo Alaye ti ara ẹni nipa lilo awọn aabo ti ara ati itanna ti a ṣe apẹrẹ lati daabobo iduroṣinṣin ati aabo ti Alaye Ti ara ẹni ti a ṣetọju. A ṣe awọn iṣọra ti o ni oye ti iṣowo, ni imọran awọn eewu ti o wa ninu sisẹ ati iru Alaye ti Ara ẹni, ti a ṣe apẹrẹ lati daabobo Alaye ti ara ẹni lati ipadanu, ilokulo ati iraye si laigba aṣẹ, ifihan, iyipada ati iparun. Bibẹẹkọ, bi ko si gbigbe itanna tabi ibi ipamọ ti Alaye Ti ara ẹni le ni aabo patapata, a ko le ṣe awọn iṣeduro bi aabo tabi aṣiri ti Alaye Ti ara ẹni.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.2&nbsp;Data Integrity: A lo alaye ti a gba ni awọn ọna ti o ṣe pataki ati ti o ni ibamu pẹlu idi ti a gba alaye naa tabi ti a pese fun wa gẹgẹbi a ti ṣafihan ninu eto imulo yii. A yoo ṣe awọn igbesẹ lati rii daju pe gbogbo alaye ti a gba, ti ṣiṣẹ, ati/tabi ti o fipamọ ni aabo lati iparun, ibajẹ, tabi lo ni ọna ti ko ni ibamu pẹlu awọn eto imulo wa tabi idi ti a gba.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>6.&nbsp;Ilana wa nipa Awọn ọmọde</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated Iranlọwọ &amp; App ni idinamọ iforukọsilẹ nipasẹ ati pe ko mọọmọ gba alaye ti ara ẹni lati ọdọ ẹnikẹni labẹ ọjọ-ori ọdun 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;.&nbsp;Sibẹsibẹ, ifarabalẹ,&nbsp;alaye ti ara ẹni ti o jọmọ ọmọde&nbsp;ti o kere ju&nbsp;ọdun 18 nikan ni&nbsp;lati&nbsp;gba ni lilo akọọlẹ ti a ṣeto ati iṣakoso nipasẹ obi agbalagba tabi alabojuto. Ni iṣẹlẹ ti a wa si imọ pe a ti gba alaye lati ọdọ ọmọde labẹ ọdun 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;a yoo ṣe gbogbo awọn igbese pataki lati yọ iru alaye bẹ lati awọn olupin wa. Ti o ba gbagbọ pe a le ni alaye ti ara ẹni eyikeyi lati ọdọ ọmọde labẹ 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;, jọwọ kan si ẹgbẹ wa&nbsp;ni info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>7.&nbsp;Idaduro Alaye</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">A ṣe awọn igbese lati ṣe idaduro Alaye Ti ara ẹni rẹ fun akoko ti ko gun ju iwulo lati mu awọn idi ti a ṣalaye ninu Eto Afihan Aṣiri yii ṣẹ, ayafi ti akoko idaduro gigun ba nilo tabi gba laaye nipasẹ ofin. Nigbati o ba pinnu akoko idaduro, a ṣe akiyesi ọpọlọpọ awọn ibeere, gẹgẹbi iru Awọn iṣẹ ti a pese fun ọ, iru ati ipari ti ibatan wa pẹlu rẹ, ipa lori Awọn iṣẹ ti a pese fun ọ ti a ba paarẹ Alaye Ti ara ẹni lati tabi nipa rẹ, ati awọn akoko idaduro dandan ti a pese nipasẹ ofin ati ilana ti o yẹ ti awọn idiwọn.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>8.&nbsp;Awọn ẹtọ ati Awọn aṣayan Aṣiri Rẹ</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Pipin Awọn ayanfẹ.&nbsp;</strong>A fun ọ ni awọn eto lati gba ọ laaye lati ṣeto awọn ayanfẹ pinpin rẹ fun akoonu ti o firanṣẹ si Awọn iṣẹ wa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.1&nbsp;Alaye Profaili Aṣayan: O le ṣafikun, ṣatunkọ, tabi paarẹ Alaye Ti ara ẹni yiyan ti o han ninu Profaili rẹ nigbakugba ninu awọn eto akọọlẹ rẹ labẹ ọna asopọ profaili satunkọ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.2&nbsp;Alaye Iwe-ipamọ ti a beere: Alaye ti ara ẹni kan nilo fun iṣẹ ṣiṣe akọọlẹ ati pe o le ṣatunkọ ṣugbọn kii ṣe paarẹ. Fun apẹẹrẹ, o le ṣatunkọ, ṣugbọn kii ṣe yọkuro, adirẹsi imeeli ati ọrọ igbaniwọle ti o nilo fun wiwọle.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.3Awọn igbasilẹ Ilera: O le ṣe atunṣe alaye ilera rẹ ati pe o le ṣafikun alaye lati jẹ ki alaye rẹ jẹ deede tabi pipe. Nitorinaa, ti o ba fẹ lati beere iraye si, tabi lati fi opin si lilo tabi ifihan ti Alaye Ti ara ẹni, jọwọ kan si&nbsp;wa&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.4&nbsp;Akoonu Gbogbo eniyan: O le beere yiyọkuro Akoonu Gbogbo eniyan nipa kikan si&nbsp;wa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.5&nbsp;Awọn ibaraẹnisọrọ Titaja: O le yọkuro kuro ninu awọn ibaraẹnisọrọ tita wa, gẹgẹbi awọn ikede ti awọn ẹya tuntun tabi awọn ipese pataki, nipasẹ ọna asopọ ti a pese ni awọn imeeli ipolowo.&nbsp;A&nbsp;kii yoo pin adirẹsi imeeli rẹ tabi alaye olubasọrọ miiran si awọn ẹgbẹ kẹta fun awọn idi titaja tiwọn laisi igbanilaaye ti o fojuhan. Paapa ti o ba jade kuro ni gbigba awọn ifiranṣẹ igbega lati ọdọ wa, iwọ yoo tẹsiwaju lati gba awọn ifiranṣẹ iṣakoso lati ọdọ wa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.6&nbsp;Awọn iwifunni: A yoo beere lọwọ rẹ boya o fẹ gba awọn iwifunni nigbati o ṣii akọọlẹ kan pẹlu wa. Ti o ba gba, a le fi imeeli ranṣẹ si ọ, SMS, tabi awọn akiyesi titari alagbeka, pese awọn olurannileti ti o jọmọ akọọlẹ tabi awọn imudojuiwọn, tabi jẹ ki o mọ pe o ni ifiranṣẹ kan lori Awọn iṣẹ wa. O le jade nigbakugba nipa ṣiṣatunṣe awọn eto ifitonileti rẹ ni oju-iwe eto.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.7&nbsp;Maṣe Tọpa: Ko si boṣewa ti o gba lori bi o ṣe le dahun si Maa ṣe Tọpinpin awọn ifihan agbara, ati pe a ko dahun si iru awọn ifihan agbara.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.8&nbsp;Jade Ninu&nbsp;Akọọlẹ Rẹ: o le mu maṣiṣẹ akọọlẹ rẹ nigbakugba. Lati ṣe eyi, wọle, lọ si oju-iwe eto, ki o yan aṣayan&nbsp;ifilọlẹ naa&nbsp;. Awọn ibeere ti gbogbo eniyan ti o ti gba awọn idahun yoo tẹsiwaju lati han ni ailorukọ lori Awọn iṣẹ wa paapaa ti o ba mu akọọlẹ rẹ ṣiṣẹ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>9.&nbsp;Ayipada si yi Afihan</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.1&nbsp;A yoo tẹsiwaju lati ṣe iṣiro eto imulo yii lodi si awọn imọ-ẹrọ tuntun, awọn iṣe iṣowo, awọn iyipada ninu ofin, ati awọn iwulo ọmọ ẹgbẹ wa, ati pe o le ṣe awọn ayipada si eto imulo ni ibamu. Jọwọ ṣayẹwo oju-iwe yii lorekore fun awọn imudojuiwọn. Ti a ba ṣe awọn ayipada ohun elo eyikeyi si eto imulo yii, a yoo fi awọn ofin imudojuiwọn ti eto imulo sori Awọn iṣẹ naa, ati pese akiyesi iru awọn ayipada, eyiti o le pẹlu akiyesi nipasẹ imeeli nipasẹ ifiranṣẹ ti a fi ranṣẹ si adirẹsi imeeli ti o lo lati wọle si Awọn iṣẹ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.2&nbsp;Eyikeyi awọn ayipada ohun elo si eto imulo yii yoo munadoko laarin ọgbọn (30) awọn ọjọ kalẹnda ti o tẹle fifiranṣẹ akiyesi imeeli si ọ. Awọn ayipada wọnyi yoo munadoko lẹsẹkẹsẹ fun awọn olumulo titun ti Awọn iṣẹ naa.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.3&nbsp;Jọwọ ṣe akiyesi pe ni gbogbo igba o ni iduro fun imudojuiwọn alaye rẹ lati pese adirẹsi imeeli rẹ lọwọlọwọ julọ. Ni iṣẹlẹ ti adirẹsi imeeli ti o kẹhin ti o pese fun wa ko wulo, tabi fun eyikeyi idi ko lagbara lati jiṣẹ si ọ ni akiyesi ti a ṣalaye loke, fifiranṣẹ imeeli wa ti o ni iru akiyesi yoo jẹ akiyesi imunadoko ti awọn ayipada ti a ṣalaye. ninu akiyesi.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.4&nbsp;Ti o ko ba fẹ lati gba awọn ayipada laaye ni lilo alaye rẹ, o gbọdọ sọ fun wa ṣaaju ọjọ to munadoko ti awọn ayipada ti o fẹ lati mu maṣiṣẹ akọọlẹ rẹ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.5&nbsp;Ilọsiwaju lilo Awọn iṣẹ ti o tẹle akiyesi iru awọn ayipada yoo ṣe afihan ifọwọsi rẹ ti iru awọn iyipada ati adehun lati di alaa nipasẹ awọn ofin ati ipo ti iru awọn ayipada.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>10.&nbsp;Ijoba</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.1&nbsp;Imudaniloju: Kaci Automated Iranlọwọ &amp; App yoo ṣe awọn iṣayẹwo ibamu ti awọn iṣe aṣiri ti o yẹ lati jẹrisi ifaramọ si eto imulo yii. Siwaju sii, a yoo ṣe awọn iwadii atẹle lati rii daju pe awọn ijẹrisi ati awọn iṣeduro nipa awọn iṣe aṣiri wa jẹ deede. O le beere nipa aiṣedeede tabi ṣe ẹdun kan nipa irufin ti o pọju si wa nipasẹ alaye olubasọrọ ti a pese ni isalẹ. A ṣe ikẹkọ ni ikẹkọ lati ṣe atilẹyin imuse ati ibamu pẹlu awọn iṣe aṣiri wa; oṣiṣẹ eyikeyi ti a pinnu pe o ṣẹ si eto imulo yii le jẹ labẹ ilana ibawi.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.2&nbsp;Ipinnu Iyanju: Awọn ibeere tabi awọn ifiyesi nipa lilo wa tabi sisọ alaye le jẹ itọsọna si ẹgbẹ wa&nbsp;ni info@kaci.help&nbsp;.&nbsp;A&nbsp;yoo ṣe iwadii ati gbiyanju lati yanju awọn ẹdun ọkan ati awọn ariyanjiyan nipa lilo ati ṣiṣafihan alaye ni ibamu pẹlu awọn ipilẹ ti o wa ninu eto imulo yii. Eyikeyi ifarakanra nipa Ilana yii ni yoo yanju ni atẹle awọn ọna ṣiṣe ipinnu ijiyan ti o ṣe ilana ni Awọn ofin Lilo.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>11.&nbsp;Atilẹyin ati esi</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ti o ba ni ibeere eyikeyi tabi yoo fẹ alaye siwaju sii nipa ohun elo naa, oluranlọwọ adaṣe ati awọn oju opo wẹẹbu wa tabi Awọn iṣẹ, jọwọ kan si wa ni&nbsp;info@kaci.help.&nbsp;A nifẹ lati gbọ lati ọdọ rẹ. Ti o ba ni imọran ti o le jẹ ki Kaci dara si eyikeyi esi nipa awọn iṣẹ wa, kan si&nbsp;wa&nbsp;ni&nbsp;info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 10:18:19');
INSERT INTO `setting` (`id`, `language`, `type`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(34, 'Arabic', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-right\">Kaci&nbsp;الإلكتروني ، تطبيق الهاتف المحمول&nbsp;(\"&nbsp;<strong>نحن&nbsp;</strong>\" ، \"&nbsp;<strong>خاصتنا&nbsp;</strong>\"&nbsp;، \"&nbsp;<strong>Kaci&nbsp;</strong>\"&nbsp;\"&nbsp;<strong>Kaci App&nbsp;</strong>\"&nbsp;أو \"&nbsp;<strong>نحن&nbsp;</strong>\") والشركات التابعة لها تقدر خصوصية الأفراد الذين يصلون إلى مواقعنا ويستخدمون خدماتنا&nbsp;، وبالتالي فإن&nbsp;تناوب بياناتك وخصوصيتك وبياناتك الشخصية أمر مهم جدًا&nbsp;بالنسبة لنا&nbsp;. من المهم للغاية بالنسبة لنا أن يشعر عملاؤنا (\"&nbsp;<strong>المستخدمون&nbsp;</strong>\") بالأمان عند استخدام منتجاتنا وخدماتنا.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">تحدد سياسة الخصوصية هذه (\"&nbsp;<strong>سياسة الخصوصية&nbsp;</strong>\") ، جنبًا إلى جنب مع الشروط والأحكام الخاصة بنا ، وسياسة ملفات تعريف الارتباط الخاصة بنا وأية مستندات أخرى مشار إليها هنا ، الأساس الذي تستند إليه أي بيانات شخصية نجمعها منك ، أو تقدمها لنا ، تتم معالجتها. يرجى قراءة سياسة الخصوصية هذه بعناية لفهم أنواع البيانات التي نجمعها منك ، وكيف نستخدمها ، والظروف التي سنشاركها فيها مع أطراف ثالثة ، وحقوقك فيما يتعلق ببياناتك الشخصية.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">يمكنك استخدام \"Kaci\" من خلال تطبيق الهاتف المحمول الخاص بنا (\"&nbsp;<strong>التطبيق&nbsp;</strong>\")&nbsp;.&nbsp;تصف سياسة الخصوصية هذه معالجة البيانات الخاصة بنا عند استخدام&nbsp;تطبيقنا ،&nbsp;أو ببساطة الوصول إلى موقعنا على الويب Kaci.help (\"&nbsp;<strong>الموقع&nbsp;</strong>\") أو أي خدمة و / أو منتج قد نقدمه لك (موقع الويب مع تطبيق الهاتف المحمول وأي من منتجاتنا و الخدمات ، \"&nbsp;<strong>الخدمات&nbsp;</strong>\"). عندما تتعلق أنشطة معالجة معينة فقط بمنتج معين مثل التطبيق أو حل Enterprise ، فسيتم توضيح ذلك بوضوح.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>1. من نحن</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">تنطبق سياسة الخصوصية هذه على أي بيانات شخصية تتم معالجتها بواسطة Kaci&nbsp;أو Factcheck Initiative ،&nbsp;كونها المتحكم في البيانات لجميع أنشطة المعالجة فيما يتعلق بالخدمات&nbsp;المقدمة على تطبيق Kaci Mobile ، أو موقع Kaci الإلكتروني&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">نرحب بالأسئلة والتعليقات والطلبات المتعلقة بسياسة الخصوصية هذه ويجب معالجتها من خلال&nbsp;مكتب المعلومات الخاص بنا info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">تشرح لك سياسة الخصوصية هذه المعلومات الشخصية التي نجمعها ، وكيف نستخدم هذه المعلومات ونشاركها ، والطرق التي يمكنك من خلالها التحكم في كيفية استخدامنا لتلك المعلومات ومشاركتها. يُعلمك بالمعلومات التي يمكن لأخصائيي الرعاية الصحية أو أي عضو آخر رؤيتها عند استخدامك لمواقعنا وخدماتنا. يُعلمك بحقوقك وخياراتك فيما يتعلق بمعلوماتك الشخصية وكيف يمكنك الاتصال بنا إذا كان لديك أي أسئلة أو مخاوف.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">KACI MOBILE والموقع&nbsp;الإلكتروني E&nbsp;سوف يجمعان وينقلان المعلومات الشخصية والطبية والصحية عنك. عن طريق استخدام التطبيق&nbsp;وموقعنا على الويب ، أنت توافق على أنه يمكننا جمع واستخدام معلوماتك الشخصية وغيرها من المعلومات كما هو موضح في سياسة خصوصية هذا الموقع. إذا كنت لا توافق ، فيرجى عدم استخدام التطبيق وموقعنا الإلكتروني.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>يجب أن يكون عمرك عام واحد&nbsp;أو&nbsp;أكثر لاستخدام خدمات&nbsp;KACI .</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>2.&nbsp;تعريفات مهمة</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">2.1&nbsp;\"المعلومات الشخصية\" الواردة في سياسة الخصوصية هذه ، تعني المعلومات المتعلقة بك والتي يمكن تحديد هويتك الشخصية ، مثل معلومات الاتصال الخاصة بك ( مثل الاسم أو العنوان أو عنوان البريد الإلكتروني أو رقم الهاتف) أو المعلومات الصحية أو الطبية التي يمكن تحديدها شخصيًا (\"المعلومات الصحية\" \") ،&nbsp;الهوية الشخصية&nbsp;المستندات (مثل رخصة القيادة وبطاقة الناخب وما إلى ذلك)&nbsp;وأي معلومات أخرى غير عامة مرتبطة بهذه المعلومات.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">\"المعلومات مجهولة الهوية\" ، تعني المعلومات التي لا تُستخدم ولا يُقصد استخدامها لتحديد هوية الفرد بشكل شخصي.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">2.2&nbsp;المعلومات التي نتلقاها أو نجمعها منك</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">أ)&nbsp;بيانات التسجيل: عندما تقوم بالتسجيل أو إنشاء حساب ، فإنك تزودنا بمعلومات معينة ، والتي تشمل عنوان بريدك الإلكتروني ورقم هاتفك وتاريخ الميلاد والجنس والرمز البريدي أو الرمز البريدي (\"بيانات التسجيل\") ، وكذلك ككلمة مرور لحسابك.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">ب)&nbsp;معلومات الدفع: إذا اخترت استخدام خدمة خاضعة للرسوم&nbsp;مثل الإعلان أو التبرع&nbsp;، فسيُطلب منك تقديم (على الأقل) اسمك ومعلومات الدفع بما في ذلك معلومات بطاقة الدفع (\"&nbsp;<em>معلومات الدفع&nbsp;</em>\"). سيتلقى أيضًا موفر خدمة تابع لجهة خارجية يتولى عمليات الدفع لنا معلومات بطاقة الدفع الخاصة بك.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">ج)&nbsp;المعلومات التي تختار تقديمها لنا: لديك القدرة على تقديم مجموعة متنوعة من المعلومات أثناء تفاعلك معنا ومع تطبيق ومساعد Kaci الآلي ، مثل رسائل البريد الإلكتروني التي قد ترسلها إلينا ، والمعلومات التي ترد عليها ، ورسائل البريد الإلكتروني أو الرسائل الإخبارية التي قمت بالتسجيل لتلقيها. يتلقى تطبيق Kaci Automated &amp; App أو الأطراف الثالثة التي تعمل بالنيابة عنا بيانات منك كلما زودتنا بمعلومات.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">د)&nbsp;معلومات الاتصال: إذا اخترت المشاركة في دراسات بحثية ، أو الاشتراك في ميزات معينة ، فيمكنك تزويدنا ، وقد نقوم بجمع معلومات الاتصال الخاصة بك ، بما في ذلك اسمك وعنوانك البريدي ورقم هاتفك (\"معلومات الاتصال\" ).</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">هـ)&nbsp;بيانات مجهولة الهوية. نستخدم البيانات غير المحددة للبحث وتطوير منتجات أو أدوات جديدة ، لتحسين الخوارزميات وتطبيقات التعلم الآلي ، وتحسين التطبيق والخدمات التي نقدمها. قد نكشف عن هذه المعلومات علنًا ولأطراف ثالثة ، على سبيل المثال ، في التقارير العامة حول الصحة ، أو للشركاء بموجب اتفاق معنا ، أو في قياس المعلومات التي نقدمها للمجتمع الطبي.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">2.3&nbsp;المعلومات التي نتلقاها من الأطراف الثالثة</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">أ)&nbsp;حسابات وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي: قد نحصل على معلومات شخصية عنك&nbsp;من خلال تطبيق الهاتف المحمول ، أو&nbsp;خدمات الوسائط الاجتماعية الأخرى التابعة لجهة خارجية ، مثل Facebook و Twitter ، إذا اخترت ربط خدماتنا بحسابات وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي الخاصة بطرف ثالث (\"حساب وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي\" \") إما عن طريق: (1) تقديم معلومات تسجيل الدخول إلى حساب الوسائط الاجتماعية الخاص بك إلينا من خلال الخدمات ؛ أو (2) السماح لنا بالوصول إلى حساب الوسائط الاجتماعية الخاص بك ، كما هو مسموح به بموجب الشروط والأحكام المعمول بها والتي تحكم استخدامك لحساب الوسائط الاجتماعية المعني.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">2.4&nbsp;المعلومات التي نجمعها عبر التكنولوجيا</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">أ)&nbsp;النشاط على التطبيق والمساعد الآلي ومواقع الويب الخاصة بنا: قد نتتبع بعض الإجراءات التي تتخذها على التطبيق والمساعد الآلي ومواقع الويب الخاصة بنا ، مثل محتوى عمليات البحث التي تجريها عبر تطبيق الهاتف المحمول&nbsp;أو&nbsp;على التطبيق والمساعد الآلي وموقع الويب الخاص بنا.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">ب)&nbsp;الوصول إلى معلومات الجهاز والمتصفح: عند الوصول إلى التطبيق والمساعد الآلي وموقع الويب الخاص بنا من جهاز كمبيوتر أو جهاز آخر ، يجوز لنا جمع معلومات مجهولة المصدر من هذا الجهاز ، مثل عنوان بروتوكول الإنترنت ونوع المتصفح وسرعة الاتصال والوصول مرات (إجمالاً ، \"معلومات مجهولة\").</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">ج)&nbsp;ملفات تعريف الارتباط: قد نستخدم ملفات تعريف الارتباط للجلسة (التي تنتهي صلاحيتها بمجرد إغلاق متصفح الويب الخاص بك) وملفات تعريف الارتباط الدائمة لجعل التطبيق والمساعد الآلي وموقعنا الإلكتروني وخدماتنا أسهل في الاستخدام ، ولجعل إعلاناتنا أفضل ، ولحماية كليهما أنت ومساعد Kaci الآلي والتطبيق. يمكنك توجيه متصفحك ، من خلال تغيير خياراته ، إلى التوقف عن قبول ملفات تعريف الارتباط أو مطالبتك قبل قبول ملف تعريف ارتباط من مواقع الويب التي تزورها. ومع ذلك ، إذا كنت لا تقبل ملفات تعريف الارتباط ، فلن تتمكن من تسجيل الدخول إلى التطبيق والمساعد الآلي ومواقعنا الإلكترونية. قد نستخدم أيضًا وحدات البكسل لتسهيل استخدام التطبيق والمساعد الآلي ومواقعنا الإلكترونية وخدماتنا ولجعل إعلاناتنا أفضل من خلال ، على سبيل المثال ، تلخيص أنماط الاستخدام. نحن في الوقت الحالي لا نحترم طلبات \"عدم التعقب\" عبر جميع أجزاء مواقعنا.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">د)&nbsp;الموقع في الوقت الفعلي: تستخدم بعض ميزات التطبيق والمساعد الآلي وموقع الويب الخاص بنا تقنية GPS لجمع معلومات في الوقت الفعلي حول موقع جهازك بحيث يمكن للتطبيق والمساعد الآلي وموقع الويب الخاص بنا توصيلك&nbsp;بأمان وكالة أو خدمات&nbsp;الرعاية الصحية المهنية&nbsp;أو سيارة إسعاف&nbsp;خدمة&nbsp;wh&nbsp;ich&nbsp;مرخصون&nbsp;أو مصرح لهم بتقديم الخدمات في المنطقة أو الولاية القضائية التي تتواجد فيها. عند الوصول إلى خدمات خرائط Google على مواقعنا ، فإنك توافق على&nbsp;<u>شروط خدمة Google&nbsp;</u>وسياسة&nbsp;<u>الخصوصية&nbsp;</u>.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">هـ)&nbsp;خدمات الهاتف المحمول: قد نجمع معلومات غير شخصية من جهازك المحمول أو الكمبيوتر. تُستخدم هذه المعلومات بشكل عام لمساعدتنا في تقديم المعلومات الأكثر صلة بك. تتضمن أمثلة المعلومات التي يمكن جمعها واستخدامها كيفية استخدامك&nbsp;لتطبيق Kaci ، أو التطبيق&nbsp;( التطبيقات) والمعلومات حول نوع الجهاز أو الكمبيوتر الذي تستخدمه. بالإضافة إلى ذلك ، في حالة تعطل تطبيقنا (تطبيقاتنا) على جهازك المحمول ، فسوف نتلقى معلومات حول إصدار برنامج طراز جهازك المحمول ومشغل الجهاز ، مما يتيح لنا تحديد الأخطاء وإصلاحها وتحسين أداء تطبيقنا (تطبيقاتنا). .</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>3.&nbsp;كيف نستخدم المعلومات التي نتلقاها أو نجمعها</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">3.1&nbsp;بشكل عام ، يستخدم التطبيق والمساعد الآلي لـ Kaci المعلومات التي نجمعها للأغراض التالية:</div><ul><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لتشغيل خدماتنا وتوفيرها وصيانتها وتحسينها وتعزيزها ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لفهم كيفية استخدامك لخدماتنا وتحليلها ولتطوير منتجات وخدمات وميزات ووظائف جديدة ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لإضفاء الطابع الشخصي على تجربتك في خدماتنا ، مثل توفير محتوى مخصص. على سبيل المثال ، نستخدم عنوان بريدك الإلكتروني لمساعدتك في إنشاء حسابك وتسجيل الدخول إليه وإدارته على خدماتنا. يتيح لنا ذلك تخصيص تجربتك وإعطائك المعلومات ذات الصلة. كما أنه يدعم الميزات التي تساعدك على فهم صحتك والتفاعل معها وتتبعها بشكل أفضل وتقديم معلومات مخصصة وذات صلة لك ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لأغراض التسويق والإعلان ، مثل تطوير وتوفير المواد الترويجية والإعلانية التي قد تكون ذات صلة أو قيّمة أو تهمك بأي شكل آخر. يجوز لنا أيضًا استخدام المعلومات التي نعرفها عنك لمساعدتنا في الإعلان عن خدماتنا على مواقع الويب الخاصة بأطراف أخرى. عند الاقتضاء بموجب القانون المعمول به ، لن نرسل لك اتصالات تسويقية إلا بموافقتك ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">للتواصل معك عبر البريد الإلكتروني والرسائل النصية وإشعارات الدفع والمكالمات الهاتفية ، من أجل تزويدك بالتحديثات والمعلومات الأخرى المتعلقة بخدماتنا ، وتوفير المعلومات التي تطلبها ، والرد على التعليقات والأسئلة ، وتقديم دعم العملاء بطريقة أخرى ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لتسهيل المعاملات والمدفوعات ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لتسهيل اتصال حسابات وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي بخدماتنا لتوفير معلومات من حسابات وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي إلى ملفك الشخصي. اعتمادًا على حسابات وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي التي تختارها وتخضع لإعدادات الخصوصية التي قمت بتعيينها في حسابات الوسائط الاجتماعية هذه ، سنصل إلى المعلومات ونوفرها ونخزنها (إن أمكن ووفقًا لما تسمح به خدمة الوسائط الاجتماعية وتفوضك بذلك) في حسابات وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي الخاصة بك بحيث تكون متاحة في ومن خلال ملف التعريف الخاص بك على الخدمات ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لأغراض أعمالنا ، مثل عمليات التدقيق ، ولأغراض ضمان الجودة ، للعثور على الاحتيال ومنعه ، والاستجابة لقضايا الثقة والسلامة التي قد تنشأ ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لأغراض الامتثال ، بما في ذلك إنفاذ&nbsp;<u>شروط الاستخدام الخاصة بنا&nbsp;</u>أو الحقوق القانونية الأخرى ، أو حسبما تقتضيه القوانين واللوائح المعمول بها أو حسب طلب أي عملية قضائية أو وكالة حكومية ؛</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">للأغراض الأخرى التي نقدم من أجلها إشعارًا محددًا في وقت جمع المعلومات ؛ و</li><li class=\"ql-align-right\">لتجميع أو إلغاء تحديد المعلومات التي تم جمعها من خلال الخدمات واستخدامها والإفصاح عنها لأغراض تجارية أخرى بعد أن لم يعد من الممكن ربط البيانات بشكل معقول بشخص يمكن التعرف عليه.</li></ul><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">3.2&nbsp;دي - المعلومات المحددة الهوية</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">يجوز لنا استخدام المعلومات مجهولة الهوية دون أي قيود.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">3.3&nbsp;المعلومات التي تشاركها مع جهات خارجية.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">تنطبق سياسة الخصوصية هذه فقط على المعلومات التي نجمعها من خلال مواقعنا وفي البريد الإلكتروني والرسائل النصية وغيرها من الاتصالات الإلكترونية التي يتم تعيينها من خلال مواقعنا أو فيما يتعلق بها. لا تنطبق هذه السياسة على المعلومات التي يتم جمعها من قبل أي طرف ثالث. عند النقر فوق الروابط الموجودة في التطبيق أو المساعد الآلي&nbsp;أو&nbsp;موقعنا الإلكتروني ، يمكنك مغادرة موقعنا. نحن لسنا مسؤولين عن ممارسات الخصوصية للمواقع الأخرى ، ونشجعك على قراءة بيانات الخصوصية الخاصة بها.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>4.&nbsp;كيف نشارك المعلومات الشخصية التي نجمعها</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">يجوز لـ Kaci Automated Assistant &amp; App مشاركة المعلومات الشخصية أو الكشف عنها بطريقة أخرى في الظروف الموضحة أدناه.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">4.1&nbsp;الشركات التابعة: قد نكشف عن المعلومات الشخصية للشركات التابعة لنا أو شركائنا لتقديم الخدمات أو للأغراض الأخرى التي تم جمع المعلومات من أجلها.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">4.2&nbsp;البائعون ومقدمو الخدمات: يجوز لنا مشاركة المعلومات الشخصية التي نتلقاها مع البائعين&nbsp;والسلطة ذات الصلة (خدمات الطوارئ أو تطبيق القانون بناءً على طلبك)&nbsp;ومقدمي الخدمات فيما يتعلق بتوفير خدمات&nbsp;وميزات Kaci&nbsp;. في حالة (أ) استخدام المعلومات الشخصية لغرض يختلف جوهريًا عن الأغراض التي تم من أجلها جمع المعلومات الشخصية في الأصل أو التصريح بها لاحقًا ، أو (ب) نقلها إلى طرف ثالث يعمل كمراقب للبيانات ، الأعضاء سيتم منحك فرصة ، حيثما كان ذلك عمليًا ومناسبًا ، لإلغاء الاشتراك في استخدام المعلومات الشخصية غير الحساسة أو نقلها. للحصول على معلومات حساسة ، بما في ذلك المعلومات المتعلقة بالصحة ، سيختار الأعضاء قبل هذا الاستخدام أو النقل.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">في بعض الحالات ، قد يحتفظ تطبيق Kaci Automated &amp; App بموفري خدمة آخرين لأداء وظائف نيابة عنا ، بما في ذلك ، على سبيل المثال لا الحصر ، مطوري مواقع الويب ومقدمي خدمات تكنولوجيا المعلومات.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">4.3&nbsp;شركاء التحليلات: قد نجعل بعض المعلومات الشخصية متاحة لأطراف ثالثة لأغراض التحليلات ، بما في ذلك: (أ) لأغراض الأعمال أو التسويق والمساعد الآلي لـ Kaci ، أو (ب) للاستفادة من أدوات الطرف الثالث لفهم اهتمامات الأعضاء ، العادات وأنماط الاستخدام و / أو الوظائف المتاحة من خلال خدماتنا. نحن نشارك معلوماتك الشخصية فقط مع شركاء التحليلات لتحسين خدماتنا و / أو تقديم الرعاية الصحية لك. نحن لا نبيع معلوماتك الشخصية للمعلنين.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">4.4&nbsp;وفقًا لما يقتضيه القانون والإفصاحات المماثلة: يجوز لنا الوصول إلى المعلومات الشخصية وحفظها والإفصاح عنها إذا كنا نعتقد أن القيام بذلك مطلوب أو مناسب ، وفقًا لتقديرنا الخاص ، من أجل: (أ) الامتثال لأي قانون أو لائحة أو إجراء قانوني معمول به أو الطلبات الحكومية ، مثل أمر المحكمة أو الاستدعاء ، أو التعاون مع جهات إنفاذ القانون أو الوكالات الحكومية ؛ (ب) اتخاذ الاحتياطات ضد المسؤولية ؛ (ج) حماية حقوقك أو حقوقنا أو ممتلكات الآخرين أو سلامتهم ؛ (د) التحقيق والدفاع عن أنفسنا ضد أي ادعاءات أو ادعاءات من طرف ثالث ؛ و (هـ) حماية أمن أو سلامة خدماتنا وأي مرافق أو معدات مستخدمة لإتاحة خدماتنا. لتجنب الشك ، قد يحدث الكشف عن المعلومات الشخصية إذا قمت بنشر أي محتوى مرفوض على الخدمات أو من خلالها.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">4.5&nbsp;خدمات الوسائط الاجتماعية: قد تسمح لك خدماتنا ، بناءً على توجيهاتك ، بمشاركة المعلومات الشخصية مع بعض خدمات الوسائط الاجتماعية ، مثل Facebook و Twitter و Pinterest و Google Plus. يرجى مراعاة أي تأثير على خصوصيتك وإخفاء هويتك عند نشر محتوى على أي وجميع خدمات الوسائط الاجتماعية. أنت تدرك وتوافق على أن استخدام المعلومات الشخصية من قبل أي خدمات وسائط اجتماعية سيخضع لسياسات الخصوصية الخاصة بخدمات وسائل التواصل الاجتماعي تلك وإعداداتك على منصاتها. نحن نشجعك على مراجعة سياسات الخصوصية الخاصة بهم.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">4.6&nbsp;التسويق: نحن لا نؤجر أو نبيع أو نشارك المعلومات الشخصية الخاصة بك مع الشركات غير التابعة لأغراض التسويق المباشر ، ما لم نحصل على إذن منك.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">4.7&nbsp;عمليات الاندماج أو المبيعات أو عمليات نقل الأصول الأخرى: قد نكشف عن المعلومات الشخصية وننقلها بطريقة أخرى إلى موفري الخدمات أو المستشارين أو شركاء المعاملات المحتملين أو الأطراف الثالثة الأخرى فيما يتعلق بالنظر أو التفاوض أو إتمام معاملة الشركة التي نحن فيها تم الاستحواذ عليها أو دمجها مع شركة أخرى أو نقوم ببيع أو تصفية أو نقل كل أو جزء من أصولنا.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>5.&nbsp;الأمن وسلامة البيانات</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">5.1&nbsp;أمن البيانات: يبذل مساعد وتطبيق Kaci الآلي جهودًا معقولة تجاريًا لحماية المعلومات الشخصية باستخدام الضمانات المادية والإلكترونية المصممة لحماية سلامة وأمن المعلومات الشخصية التي نحتفظ بها. نحن نتخذ الاحتياطات المعقولة تجاريًا ، مع الأخذ في الاعتبار المخاطر التي تنطوي عليها المعالجة وطبيعة المعلومات الشخصية ، وهي مصممة لحماية المعلومات الشخصية من الضياع وسوء الاستخدام والوصول غير المصرح به والكشف والتعديل والتدمير. ومع ذلك ، نظرًا لأنه لا يمكن أن يكون النقل الإلكتروني أو التخزين الإلكتروني للمعلومات الشخصية آمنًا تمامًا ، فلا يمكننا تقديم أي ضمانات فيما يتعلق بأمان أو خصوصية المعلومات الشخصية.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">5.2&nbsp;تكامل البيانات: نستخدم المعلومات التي نجمعها بطرق ملائمة ومتوافقة مع الغرض الذي من أجله تم جمع هذه المعلومات أو توفيرها لنا كما هو موضح في هذه السياسة. سنتخذ خطوات لضمان حماية جميع المعلومات التي تم جمعها ومعالجتها و / أو تخزينها من التدمير أو الفساد أو الاستخدام بطريقة لا تتوافق مع سياساتنا أو الغرض الذي تلقيناها من أجله.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>6.&nbsp;سياستنا المتعلقة بالأطفال</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">يحظر تطبيق Kaci Automated Assistant &amp; App التسجيل عن طريق ولا يقوم عن قصد بجمع معلومات شخصية من أي شخص يقل عمره عن عام&nbsp;واحد&nbsp;.&nbsp;ومع ذلك ، فإن المعلومات الحساسة والشخصية&nbsp;المتعلقة بطفل&nbsp;أقل من&nbsp;18 عامًا لا&nbsp;يتم&nbsp;جمعها إلا باستخدام حساب تم إعداده وإدارته بواسطة أحد الوالدين أو الوصي البالغين. في حالة علمنا بأننا قمنا بجمع معلومات من طفل يقل عمره عن عام واحد ،&nbsp;فسوف&nbsp;نتخذ جميع التدابير اللازمة لإزالة هذه المعلومات من خوادمنا. إذا كنت تعتقد أنه قد يكون لدينا أي معلومات شخصية من طفل أقل من 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;، فيرجى الاتصال بفريقنا&nbsp;على info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>7.&nbsp;الاحتفاظ بالمعلومات</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">نتخذ تدابير للاحتفاظ بمعلوماتك الشخصية لفترة لا تزيد عن الضرورة للوفاء بالأغراض الموضحة في سياسة الخصوصية هذه ، ما لم يكن هناك حاجة إلى فترة احتفاظ أطول أو يسمح بها القانون. عند تحديد فترة الاستبقاء ، نأخذ في الاعتبار معايير مختلفة ، مثل نوع الخدمات المقدمة لك ، وطبيعة علاقتنا بك ومدتها ، والتأثير على الخدمات التي نقدمها لك إذا قمنا بحذف بعض المعلومات الشخصية من أو عنك ، وفترات الاحتفاظ الإلزامية التي ينص عليها القانون وقانون التقادم ذي الصلة.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>8.&nbsp;حقوق الخصوصية الخاصة بك وخياراتك</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>تفضيلات المشاركة.&nbsp;</strong>نوفر لك الإعدادات للسماح لك بتعيين تفضيلات المشاركة الخاصة بك للمحتوى الذي تنشره على خدماتنا.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">8.1&nbsp;معلومات الملف الشخصي الاختيارية: يمكنك إضافة أو تحرير أو حذف المعلومات الشخصية الاختيارية التي تظهر في ملف التعريف الخاص بك في أي وقت في إعدادات حسابك ضمن رابط تعديل الملف الشخصي.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">8.2&nbsp;معلومات الحساب المطلوبة: بعض المعلومات الشخصية مطلوبة لوظيفة الحساب ويمكن تحريرها ولكن لا حذفها. على سبيل المثال ، يمكنك تعديل عنوان البريد الإلكتروني وكلمة المرور المطلوبين لتسجيل الدخول ، وليس إزالتهما.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>8.3</strong>السجلات الصحية: يمكنك تعديل معلوماتك الصحية وإضافة معلومات لجعل معلوماتك أكثر دقة أو اكتمالاً. وفقًا لذلك ، إذا كنت ترغب في طلب الوصول إلى المعلومات الشخصية أو الحد من استخدامها أو الكشف عنها ، فيرجى الاتصال&nbsp;بنا&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>8.4</strong>&nbsp;المحتوى العام: يمكنك طلب إزالة المحتوى العام عن طريق الاتصال&nbsp;بنا.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>8.5</strong>&nbsp;الاتصالات التسويقية: يمكنك إلغاء الاشتراك في مراسلاتنا التسويقية ، مثل إعلانات الميزات الجديدة أو العروض الخاصة ، عبر الرابط الموجود في رسائل البريد الإلكتروني الترويجية.&nbsp;لن&nbsp;نشارك أبدًا عنوان بريدك الإلكتروني أو معلومات الاتصال الأخرى مع أطراف ثالثة لأغراض التسويق الخاصة بهم دون إذن صريح منك. حتى إذا اخترت عدم تلقي رسائل ترويجية منا ، فستستمر في تلقي رسائل إدارية منا.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>8.6</strong>&nbsp;الإخطارات: سنطلب منك ما إذا كنت ترغب في تلقي إشعارات عند فتح حساب معنا. إذا وافقت ، فقد نرسل إليك إخطارات عبر البريد الإلكتروني أو الرسائل النصية القصيرة أو الهاتف المحمول ، ونزودك بالتذكيرات أو التحديثات المتعلقة بالحساب ، أو نخبرك أن لديك رسالة على خدماتنا. يمكنك إلغاء الاشتراك في أي وقت عن طريق ضبط إعدادات الإشعارات في صفحة الإعدادات.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>8.7</strong>&nbsp;عدم التعقب: لا يوجد معيار مقبول حول كيفية الاستجابة لإشارات عدم التعقب ، ولا نستجيب لمثل هذه الإشارات.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>8.8</strong>&nbsp;تسجيل الخروج من&nbsp;حسابك: يمكنك إلغاء تنشيط حسابك في أي وقت. للقيام بذلك ، قم بتسجيل الدخول ، وانتقل إلى صفحة الإعدادات ، واختر خيار&nbsp;تسجيل الخروج&nbsp;. ستستمر أسئلتك العامة التي تلقت إجابات في الظهور بشكل مجهول على خدماتنا حتى إذا قمت بإلغاء تنشيط حسابك.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>9.&nbsp;التغييرات في هذه السياسة</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">9.1&nbsp;سنواصل تقييم هذه السياسة مقابل التقنيات الجديدة وممارسات الأعمال والتغييرات في القانون واحتياجات أعضائنا ، وقد نقوم بإجراء تغييرات على السياسة وفقًا لذلك. يرجى مراجعة هذه الصفحة بشكل دوري للحصول على التحديثات. إذا أجرينا أي تغييرات جوهرية على هذه السياسة ، فسننشر الشروط المحدثة للسياسة على الخدمات ، ونقدم لك إشعارًا بهذه التغييرات ، والتي قد تتضمن إشعارًا عبر البريد الإلكتروني من خلال رسالة يتم إرسالها إلى عنوان البريد الإلكتروني الذي تستخدمه للوصول إلى خدمات.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">9.2&nbsp;تسري أي تغييرات جوهرية على هذه السياسة في غضون ثلاثين (30) يومًا تقويميًا بعد إرسال إشعار بالبريد الإلكتروني إليك. ستكون هذه التغييرات سارية على الفور للمستخدمين الجدد للخدمات.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">9.3&nbsp;يرجى ملاحظة أنك مسؤول في جميع الأوقات عن تحديث معلوماتك لتزويدنا بأحدث عنوان بريد إلكتروني لك. في حالة أن عنوان البريد الإلكتروني الأخير الذي قدمته لنا غير صالح ، أو لأي سبب من الأسباب غير قادر على تسليم الإشعار الموضح أعلاه إليك ، فإن إرسالنا للبريد الإلكتروني الذي يحتوي على هذا الإشعار سيشكل إشعارًا فعالاً بالتغييرات الموضحة في الإشعار.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">9.4&nbsp;إذا كنت لا ترغب في السماح بإجراء تغييرات في استخدامنا لمعلوماتك ، فيجب عليك إخطارنا قبل تاريخ سريان التغييرات التي ترغب في إلغاء تنشيط حسابك.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">9.5&nbsp;يجب أن يشير استمرار استخدام الخدمات بعد الإشعار بهذه التغييرات إلى إقرارك بهذه التغييرات وموافقتك على الالتزام بشروط وأحكام هذه التغييرات.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>10.&nbsp;الحوكمة</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">10.1&nbsp;الإنفاذ: سيجري تطبيق Kaci Automated Assistant &amp; App عمليات تدقيق الامتثال لممارسات الخصوصية ذات الصلة للتحقق من الالتزام بهذه السياسة. علاوة على ذلك ، سنجري تحقيقات متابعة للتحقق من دقة الشهادات والتأكيدات المتعلقة بممارسات الخصوصية الخاصة بنا. يمكنك الاستفسار عن عدم الدقة أو تقديم شكوى بشأن انتهاك محتمل لنا عبر معلومات الاتصال الواردة أدناه. نشارك في التدريب لدعم التنفيذ والامتثال لممارسات الخصوصية الخاصة بنا ؛ قد يخضع أي موظف نقرر أنه ينتهك هذه السياسة لإجراء تأديبي.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">10.2&nbsp;حل النزاع: قد يتم توجيه الأسئلة أو المخاوف المتعلقة باستخدامنا للمعلومات أو الكشف عنها إلى فريقنا&nbsp;على info@kaci.help&nbsp;.&nbsp;سنحقق&nbsp;ونحاول حل الشكاوى والنزاعات المتعلقة باستخدام المعلومات والكشف عنها وفقًا للمبادئ الواردة في هذه السياسة. يجب حل أي نزاع يتعلق بهذه السياسة باتباع آليات حل النزاعات الموضحة في شروط الاستخدام.</div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><strong>11.&nbsp;الدعم وردود الفعل</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-right\">إذا كانت لديك أي أسئلة أو ترغب في مزيد من التوضيح حول التطبيق والمساعد الآلي ومواقعنا الإلكترونية أو خدماتنا ، فيرجى الاتصال بنا على&nbsp;info@kaci.help.&nbsp;نحن نحب أن نسمع منك. إذا كانت لديك فكرة يمكن أن تجعل Kaci أفضل من أي تعليقات تتعلق بخدماتنا ، فاتصل&nbsp;بنا&nbsp;على&nbsp;info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 05:10:21'),
(35, 'Chinese', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci網站、移動應用程序（“<strong>我們</strong>”、“<strong>我們的</strong>”&nbsp;、“&nbsp;<strong>Kaci&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;“&nbsp;<strong>Kaci App&nbsp;</strong>”或“<strong>我們</strong>”）及其附屬公司重視訪問我們網站和使用我們服務的個人的隱私，因此保護您的數據、隱私和個人數據對我們非常重要。讓我們的客戶（“<strong>用戶</strong>”）在使用我們的產品和服務時感到安全對我們來說至關重要。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">本隱私政策（“<strong>隱私政策</strong>”）以及我們的條款和條件、我們的 Cookie 政策以及其中提及的任何其他文件，規定了我們從您那裡收集或您向我們提供的任何個人數據的基礎。被處理。請仔細閱讀本隱私政策，以了解我們向您收集的數據類型、我們如何使用這些數據、我們將在什麼情況下與第三方共享這些數據，以及您對個人數據的權利。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>應用程序</strong>”）使用“Kaci”&nbsp;。本隱私政策描述了我們在使用我們的應用程序或僅訪問我們的網站 Kaci.help（“<strong>網站</strong>”）或我們可能為您提供的任何服務和/或產品（網站以及移動應用程序和我們的任何產品和服務，簡稱“<strong>服務</strong>”）。如果某些處理活動僅與特定產品（例如應用程序或企業解決方案）相關，則會明確指出。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. 我們是誰</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">本隱私政策適用於 Kaci或 Factcheck Initiative 處理的任何個人數據， Kaci 或 Factcheck Initiative 是與Kaci 移動應用程序或 Kaci 網站上提供的服務相關的所有處理活動的數據控制者。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">歡迎就本隱私政策提出問題、評論和請求，並應通過我們的信息諮詢台 info@kaci.help予以解決。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">本隱私政策向您解釋我們收集的個人信息、我們如何使用和共享該信息，以及您可以控制我們如何使用和共享該信息的方式。它告知您當您使用我們的網站和服務時，醫療保健專業人員或其他成員可以看到哪些信息。它告知您有關您的個人信息的權利和選擇，以及如果您有任何問題或疑慮，如何联系我們。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">KACI移動應用程序和網站將收集和傳輸有關您的個人、醫療和健康相關信息。通過使用應用程序&nbsp;和我們的網站，您同意我們可以按照本網站隱私政策中的描述收集和使用您的個人信息和其他信息。如果您不同意，請不要使用該應用程序和我們的網站。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>您必須年滿 1&nbsp;0歲才能使用 KACI 的服務。</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2.重要定義</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1本隱私政策中的“個人信息”是指可識別您個人身份的信息，例如您的聯繫信息（例如姓名、地址、電子郵件地址或電話號碼）、可識別個人身份的健康或醫療信息（“健康信息”）。 ”），個人身份證明&nbsp;文件（例如駕駛執照、選民卡等）以及與此類信息相關的任何其他非公開信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">“去識別化信息”是指既不用於也不打算用於識別個人身份的信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2我們從您那裡收到或收集的信息</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)註冊數據：當您註冊或創建帳戶時，您向我們提供某些信息，其中包括您的電子郵件地址、電話號碼、出生日期、性別以及郵政編碼（“註冊數據”）作為您帳戶的密碼。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)付款信息：如果您選擇使用廣告或捐款等收費服務，您將被要求（至少）提供您的姓名和付款信息，包括支付卡信息（“<em>付款信息</em>”）。為我們處理付款的第三方服務提供商也將收到您的支付卡信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)您選擇向我們提供的信息：您可以在與我們和 Kaci 自動助理及應用程序互動期間提供各種信息，例如您可能向我們發送的電子郵件、您回复的信息以及電子郵件或新聞通訊您註冊接收的。每當您向我們提供信息時，Kaci Automated Assistant 和應用程序或代表我們行事的第三方都會收到您的數據。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)聯繫信息：如果您選擇參與研究或註冊某些功能，您可以向我們提供並且我們可能會收集您的聯繫信息，包括您的姓名、郵寄地址和電話號碼（“聯繫信息” ）。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)去識別化數據。我們使用去識別化數據來研究和開發新產品或工具，完善我們的算法和機器學習應用程序，並改進我們提供的應用程序和服務。我們可能會公開或向第三方披露此類信息，例如在有關健康的公開報告中、向與我們達成協議的合作夥伴或在我們向醫學界提供的基准信息中披露。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3我們從第三方收到的信息</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)社交媒體帳戶：如果您選擇將我們的服務與第三方社交媒體帳戶（“社交媒體帳戶”）關聯，我們可能會通過移動應用程序或其他第三方社交媒體服務（例如Facebook 和Twitter&nbsp;）獲取有關您的個人信息。&nbsp;”) 通過以下任一方式：(i) 通過服務向我們提供您的社交媒體帳戶登錄信息； (ii) 允許我們訪問您的社交媒體帳戶（根據管理您使用相應社交媒體帳戶的適用條款和條件的允許）。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4我們通過技術收集的信息</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)應用程序、自動助手和我們的網站上的活動：我們可能會跟踪您在應用程序、自動助手和我們的網站上執行的一些操作，例如您通過移動應用程序或在應用程序、自動化助手和我們的網站。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)訪問設備和瀏覽器信息：當您從計算機或其他設備訪問應用程序、自動助手和我們的網站時，我們可能會從該設備收集匿名信息，例如您的互聯網協議地址、瀏覽器類型、連接速度和訪問權限次（統稱為“匿名信息”）。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Cookie：我們可能會使用會話Cookie（一旦您關閉網絡瀏覽器就會過期）和持久Cookie，以使應用程序、自動助手以及我們的網站和服務更易於使用，使我們的廣告效果更好，並保護兩者您和 Kaci 自動化助手和應用程序。您可以通過更改選項來指示您的瀏覽器停止接受 Cookie，或在接受您訪問的網站的 Cookie 之前提示您。但是，如果您不接受 Cookie，您將無法保持應用程序、自動助手和我們網站的登錄狀態。我們還可能使用 Pixels 使應用程序、自動化助手以及我們的網站和服務更易於使用，並通過總結使用模式等方式更好地宣傳我們的廣告。目前，我們不接受我們網站所有部分的“請勿跟踪”請求。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)實時位置：應用程序、自動助理和我們網站的某些功能使用 GPS 技術來收集有關您設備位置的實時信息，以便應用程序、自動助理和我們網站可以將您連接到安全中心代理機構、醫療保健專業服務或救護車&nbsp;服務_&nbsp;_&nbsp;被許可或授權在您所在的地區或司法管轄區提供服務。當訪問我們網站上的 Google 地圖服務時，即表示您同意 Google 的<u>服務條款</u>和<u>隱私政策</u>。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)移動服務：我們可能會從您的移動設備或計算機收集非個人信息。該信息通常用於幫助我們向您提供最相關的信息。可能收集和使用的信息示例包括您如何使用Kaci 應用程序、其他應用程序以及有關您使用的設備或計算機類型的信息。此外，如果我們的應用程序在您的移動設備上崩潰，我們將收到有關您的移動設備型號、軟件版本和設備運營商的信息，這使我們能夠識別和修復錯誤，並以其他方式提高我們的應用程序的性能。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3.我們如何使用我們收到或收集的信息</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1一般情況下，Kaci自動化助手及應用程序將我們收集的信息用於以下目的：</div><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">運營、提供、維護、改進和增強我們的服務；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">了解和分析您如何使用我們的服務以及開發新產品、服務、特性和功能；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">個性化您對我們服務的體驗，例如提供定制內容。例如，我們使用您的電子郵件地址來幫助您在我們的服務上創建、登錄和管理您的帳戶。這使我們能夠個性化您的體驗並為您提供相關信息。它還支持一些功能，幫助您更好地了解、參與和跟踪您的健康狀況，並向您提供個性化的相關信息；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">用於營銷和廣告目的，例如開發和提供與您相關、有價值或您感興趣的促銷和廣告材料。我們還可能使用我們了解到的有關您的信息來協助我們在第三方網站上宣傳我們的服務。根據適用法律的要求，我們只會在您同意的情況下向您發送營銷信息；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">通過電子郵件、短信、推送通知和電話與您溝通，以便為您提供與我們的服務相關的更新和其他信息、提供您請求的信息、回複評論和問題以及以其他方式提供客戶支持；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">促進交易和支付；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">促進社交媒體帳戶與我們的服務的連接，以將社交媒體帳戶中的信息提供給您的個人資料。根據您選擇的社交媒體帳戶並根據您在此類社交媒體帳戶中設置的隱私設置，我們將訪問、提供和存儲（如果適用且經社交媒體服務允許並經您授權）信息在您的社交媒體帳戶中，以便可以通過您在服務上的個人資料查看該信息；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">出於我們的業務目的，例如審計、質量保證目的、發現和防止欺詐以及應對可能出現的信任和安全問題；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">出於合規目的，包括執行我們的<u>使用條款</u>或其他合法權利，或根據適用法律和法規的要求或任何司法程序或政府機構的要求；</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">用於我們在收集信息時提供具體通知的其他目的；和</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">匯總或以其他方式消除通過服務收集的信息，並在數據無法再合理地與可識別的個人關聯後將其用於其他商業目的。</li></ul><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.2去——識別信息</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">我們可以不受任何限制地使用去識別化信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.3您與第三方分享的信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">本隱私政策僅適用於我們通過我們的網站以及通過我們的網站設置或與我們的網站相關的電子郵件、文本和其他電子通信收集的信息。本政策不適用於任何第三方收集的信息。當您點擊應用程序、自動助手或我們網站上的鏈接時，您可能會離開我們的網站。我們不對其他網站的隱私慣例負責，我們鼓勵您閱讀他們的隱私聲明。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>4.我們如何分享我們收集的個人信息</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated Assistant &amp; App 可能會在下述情況下共享或以其他方式披露個人信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.1關聯公司：我們可能會向我們的關聯公司或合作夥伴披露個人信息，以提供服務或用於收集信息的其他目的。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.2供應商和服務提供商：我們可能會與供應商、相關機構（根據您的要求提供緊急服務或執法部門）和與提供服務和 Kaci 功能相關的服務提供商共享我們收到的個人信息。如果個人信息 (a) 用於與個人信息最初收集或隨後授權的目的有重大不同的目的，或 (b) 轉移給充當數據控制者的第三方，則會員在實際和適當的情況下，我們將有機會選擇不使用或傳輸非敏感個人信息。對於敏感信息，包括健康相關信息，會員將在此類使用或轉讓之前選擇加入。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">在某些情況下，Kaci Automated Assistant &amp; App 可能會聘請其他服務提供商代表我們履行職能，包括但不限於網站開發商和 IT 服務提供商。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.3分析合作夥伴：我們可能會出於分析目的向第三方提供某些個人信息，包括：(a) 用於Kaci Automated 助手和應用程序業務或營銷目的，或(b) 利用第三方工具了解會員的興趣，習慣、使用模式和/或通過我們的服務提供的功能。我們僅與分析合作夥伴共享您的個人信息，以改進我們自己的服務和/或為您提供醫療保健。我們不會將您的個人信息出售給廣告商。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.4根據法律和類似披露的要求：如果我們認為這樣做是必要的或適當的，我們可以自行決定訪問、保存和披露個人信息，以便：(a) 遵守任何適用的法律、法規、法律程序或政府請求，例如法院命令或傳票，或以其他方式與執法機構或政府機構合作； (b) 採取預防措施避免責任； (c) 保護您、我們或他人的權利、財產或安全； (d) 針對任何第三方索賠或指控進行調查並為自己辯護； (e) 保護我們的服務以及用於提供我們的服務的任何設施或設備的安全性或完整性。為避免疑義，如果您在服務上或通過服務發布任何令人反感的內容，則可能會披露個人信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.5社交媒體服務：我們的服務可能允許您根據您的指示與某些社交媒體服務（例如 Facebook、Twitter、Pinterest 和 Google Plus）共享個人信息。在任何及所有社交媒體服務上發佈內容時，請考慮對您的隱私和匿名的任何影響。您理解並同意任何社交媒體服務對個人信息的使用將受這些社交媒體服務各自的隱私政策以及您在其平台上的設置的約束。我們鼓勵您查看他們的隱私政策。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.6營銷：除非獲得您的許可，否則我們不會出於直接營銷目的向非關聯公司出租、出售或分享您的個人信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.7合併、銷售或其他資產轉讓：我們可能會在考慮、談判或完成我們參與的公司交易時向服務提供商、顧問、潛在交易夥伴或其他第三方披露或以其他方式轉讓個人信息。被另一家公司收購或與另一家公司合併，或者我們出售、清算或轉讓我們的全部或部分資產。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>5.安全性和數據完整性</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.1數據安全：Kaci Automated Assistant 和應用程序通過使用旨在保護我們維護的個人信息的完整性和安全性的物理和電子保護措施，做出商業上合理的努力來保護個人信息。考慮到處理個人信息所涉及的風險和個人信息的性質，我們採取商業上合理的預防措施，旨在保護個人信息免遭丟失、濫用和未經授權的訪問、披露、更改和破壞。然而，由於個人信息的電子傳輸或存儲不可能完全安全，因此我們無法保證個人信息的安全或隱私。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.2數據完整性：我們以與本政策中披露的收集或提供給我們的信息的目的相關且兼容的方式使用我們收集的信息。我們將採取措施確保收集、處理和/或存儲的所有信息免遭破壞、損壞或以不符合我們政策或我們收到信息的目的的方式使用。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>6.我們關於兒童的政策</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated Assistant &amp; App 禁止 1 0 歲以下的任何人註冊，並且不會故意收集任何 1&nbsp;0歲以下的人的個人信息。然而，與 18 歲以下兒童相關的敏感個人信息只能使用由成年父母或監護人設置和管理的帳戶來收集。如果我們得知我們收集了 1&nbsp;0歲以下兒童的信息，我們將採取一切必要措施從我們的服務器中刪除此類信息。如果您認為我們可能擁有 1&nbsp;0 歲以下兒童的任何個人信息，請通過 info@kaci.help聯繫我們的團隊。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>7.信息保留</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">我們採取措施將您的個人信息保留的期限不超過實現本隱私政策中概述的目的所需的期限，除非法律要求或允許更長的保留期限。在確定保留期限時，我們會考慮各種標準，例如向您提供的服務類型、我們與您關係的性質和長度、如果我們刪除或刪除某些個人信息對我們向您提供的服務的影響。關於您的信息，以及法律和相關時效法規規定的強制保留期限。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>8.您的隱私權和選擇</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>共享偏好設置。</strong>我們為您提供設置，允許您設置您發佈到我們服務的內容的共享首選項。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.1可選個人資料信息：您可以隨時在編輯個人資料鏈接下的帳戶設置中添加、編輯或刪除個人資料中顯示的可選個人信息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.2所需的帳戶信息：帳戶功能需要某些個人信息，並且可以編輯但不能刪除。例如，您可以編輯但不能刪除登錄所需的電子郵件地址和密碼。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.3健康記錄：您可以修改您的健康信息，並可以添加信息以使您的信息更加準確或完整。因此，如果您想請求訪問、限制使用或披露個人信息，請聯繫我們。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.4&nbsp;公共內容：您可以聯繫我們請求刪除公共內容。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.5&nbsp;營銷通訊：您可以通過促銷電子郵件中提供的鏈接取消訂閱我們的營銷通訊，例如新功能或特別優惠的公告。未經您的明確許可，我們絕不會出於第三方自身的營銷目的而向第三方共享您的電子郵件地址或其他聯繫信息。即使您選擇不接收我們的促銷消息，您仍將繼續收到我們的管理消息。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.6&nbsp;通知：當您在我們這裡開設賬戶時，我們會詢問您是否希望收到通知。如果您同意，我們可能會向您發送電子郵件、短信或移動推送通知，向您提供與帳戶相關的提醒或更新，或讓您知道您有關於我們服務的消息。您可以隨時通過在設置頁面中調整通知設置來選擇退出。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.7&nbsp;請勿跟踪：關於如何響應“請勿跟踪”信號，沒有公認的標準，並且我們不會響應此類信號。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">8.8&nbsp;註銷您的帳戶：您可以隨時停用您的帳戶。為此，請登錄，轉到設置頁面，然後選擇註銷選項。即使您停用您的帳戶，已收到答案的您的公開問題仍將繼續以匿名方式顯示在我們的服務上。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>9.本政策的變更</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.1我們將繼續根據新技術、商業慣例、法律變化和我們的會員需求評估本政策，並可能對本政策進行相應的更改。請定期查看此頁面以獲取更新。如果我們對本政策做出任何重大變更，我們將在服務上發布更新後的政策條款，並向您提供此類變更的通知，其中可能包括通過發送到您用於訪問服務的電子郵件地址的電子郵件通知服務。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.2對本政策的任何重大變更將在我們向您發送電子郵件通知後三十 (30) 個日曆日內生效。這些更改將立即對服務的新用戶生效。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.3請注意，您始終有責任更新您的信息，以便向我們提供您最新的電子郵件地址。如果您向我們提供的最後一個電子郵件地址無效，或出於任何原因無法向您發送上述通知，我們發送的包含此類通知的電子郵件仍將構成所述變更的有效通知通知中。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.4如果您不希望允許我們更改您的信息的使用方式，您必須在更改生效日期之前通知我們您希望停用您的帳戶。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">9.5在收到此類變更通知後繼續使用服務應表明您承認此類變更並同意受此類變更的條款和條件的約束。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>10.治理</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.1執行：Kaci自動化助手和應用程序將對我們的相關隱私實踐進行合規審計，以驗證對本政策的遵守情況。此外，我們將進行後續調查，以驗證有關我們隱私實踐的證明和斷言是否準確。您可以通過下面提供的聯繫信息向我們詢問不准確之處或對潛在違規行為進行投訴。我們確實參與培訓以支持我們隱私實踐的實施和遵守；我們確定違反本政策的任何員工可能會受到紀律處分。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">10.2爭議解決：有關我們使用或披露信息的問題或疑慮可通過 info@kaci.help直接聯繫我們的團隊。我們將根據本政策中包含的原則調查並嘗試解決有關信息使用和披露的投訴和爭議。有關本政策的任何爭議均應按照使用條款中概述的爭議解決機制解決。</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>11.支持和反饋</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">如果您有任何疑問或想進一步了解該應用程序、自動化助手以及我們的網站或服務，請通過info@kaci.help 與我們聯繫。我們很高興收到您的來信。如果您有任何想法可以讓 Kaci 做得更好，請提供有關我們服務的任何反饋，請通過info@kaci.help 聯繫我們。</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 05:18:59');
INSERT INTO `setting` (`id`, `language`, `type`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(36, 'Igbo', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci&nbsp;, Ngwa mkpanaaka&nbsp;(“&nbsp;<strong>anyị&nbsp;</strong>”, “&nbsp;<strong>anyị&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;, “&nbsp;<strong>Kaci&nbsp;</strong>”&nbsp;\"&nbsp;<strong>Kaci App&nbsp;</strong>\"&nbsp;ma ọ bụ \"&nbsp;<strong>anyị&nbsp;</strong>\") na ndị mmekọ na-eji nzuzo nke ndị na-abanye na saịtị anyị na-eji ọrụ anyị&nbsp;, si otú a na -agbanwe data gị, nzuzo na data nkeonwe dị anyị&nbsp;mkpa . Ọ dị anyị ezigbo mkpa na ndị ahịa anyị (“&nbsp;<strong>ndị ọrụ&nbsp;</strong>”) nwee ahụ iru ala mgbe ha na-eji ngwaahịa na ọrụ anyị.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Amụma nzuzo a (“&nbsp;<strong>Amụma Nzuzo&nbsp;</strong>”), yana Usoro &amp; Ọnọdụ anyị, Amụma Kuki anyị na akwụkwọ ndị ọzọ e zoro aka na ya, na-ewepụta ndabere nke data nkeonwe ọ bụla anyị na-anakọta n\'aka gị, ma ọ bụ nke ị nyere anyị, ga- a ga-edozi. Biko gụọ amụma nzuzo a nke ọma ka ị ghọta ụdị data anyị na-anakọta n\'aka gị, otu anyị si eji ya, ọnọdụ anyị ga-ekekọrịta ya na ndị ọzọ, yana ikike gị n\'ihe gbasara data nkeonwe gị.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ị nwere ike iji \"Kaci\" site na ngwa mkpanaaka anyị (\"&nbsp;<strong>ngwa&nbsp;</strong>\")&nbsp;.&nbsp;Amụma nzuzo a na-akọwa nhazi data anyị mgbe ị na-eji&nbsp;ngwa anyị,&nbsp;ma ọ bụ na-abanye na webụsaịtị anyị Kaci.help (“&nbsp;<strong>Webụsaịtị&nbsp;</strong>”) ma ọ bụ ọrụ ọ bụla na/ma ọ bụ ngwaahịa anyị nwere ike inye gị (webụsaịtị yana ngwa Mobile na ngwaahịa ọ bụla na ngwaahịa anyị. ọrụ, \"&nbsp;<strong>Ọrụ&nbsp;</strong>\"). Ebe ụfọdụ mmemme nhazi metụtara naanị otu ngwaahịa dị ka ngwa ngwa ma ọ bụ ngwa ụlọ ọrụ, nke a ga-egosipụta nke ọma.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Onye anyi bu</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Amụma nzuzo a na-emetụta data nkeonwe ọ bụla nke Kaci&nbsp;ma ọ bụ Factcheck Initiative na-ahazi,&nbsp;ịbụ onye na-ahụ maka data nke ọrụ nhazi niile metụtara ọrụ ndị&nbsp;a na-enye na Kaci Mobile Application, ma ọ bụ weebụsaịtị Kaci&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">A na-anabata ajụjụ, nkwupụta na arịrịọ gbasara amụma nzuzo a, a ga-agwakwa ya site na&nbsp;desk ozi anyị info@kaci.help&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Amụma nzuzo a na-akọwara gị ozi nkeonwe anyị na-anakọta, otu anyị si eji na kesaa ozi ahụ, yana ụzọ ị ga-esi ejikwa otu anyị si eji na kesaa ozi ahụ. Ọ na-agwa gị ozi ndị ọkachamara ahụike ma ọ bụ onye ọzọ nwere ike ịhụ mgbe ị na-eji saịtị na Ọrụ anyị. Ọ na-agwa gị ikike na nhọrọ gị gbasara ozi nkeonwe gị yana otu ị nwere ike isi kpọtụrụ anyị ma ọ bụrụ na ị nwere ajụjụ ma ọ bụ nchegbu ọ bụla.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">KACI&nbsp;MOBILE APPLICATION &amp; WEB&nbsp;SIT&nbsp;E&nbsp;ga-anakọta ma bufee ozi nkeonwe, ahụike na ahụike gbasara gị. Site n\'iji ngwa&nbsp;NA webụsaịtị anyị, unu kwenyere na anyị nwere ike ịnakọta ma jiri ozi nkeonwe gị na ndị ọzọ dị ka akọwara na iwu nzuzo saịtị a. Ọ BỤRỤ NA Ị KWESỊTAGHỊ, Biko ejikwala ngwa na webụsaịtị anyị. Ị ga-abụrịrị 1&nbsp;0&nbsp;afọ ma ọ bụ karịa ka ị&nbsp;jiri ọrụ KACI&nbsp;.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2.&nbsp;Nkọwa dị mkpa</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1&nbsp;\"Ozi nkeonwe\" na amụma nzuzo a, pụtara ozi gbasara gị nke a ga-amata gị, dị ka ozi kọntaktị gị ( dịka aha, adreesị, adreesị ozi-e, ma ọ bụ nọmba ekwentị), ahụike ma ọ bụ ozi ahụike egosipụtara (\"Health information). ”),&nbsp;njirimara onwe onye&nbsp;akwụkwọ (dị ka akwụkwọ ikike ịnya ụgbọ ala, kaadị ntuli aka wdg)&nbsp;yana ozi ọ bụla ọzọ na-abụghị nke ọha na-ejikọta na ozi dị otú ahụ.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">“ Ozi ewepụrụ achọpụtara”, pụtara ozi anaghị eji ma ọ bụ bu n’obi ka ejiri ya mata onye n’onwe ya.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2&nbsp;Ozi Anyị na-anata ma ọ bụ na-anakọta n\'aka gị</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Data Ndebanye aha: Mgbe ị debanyere aha ma ọ bụ mepụta akaụntụ, ị na-enye anyị ụfọdụ ozi, nke gụnyere adreesị email gị, nọmba ekwentị, ụbọchị ọmụmụ, okike, na zip ma ọ bụ koodu nzi ozi (\"Data Ndebanye aha\"), yana dị ka paswọọdụ maka akaụntụ gị.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Ozi Ịkwụ Ụgwọ: Ọ bụrụ na ị họrọ iji ọrụ dabeere na ego&nbsp;dị ka mgbasa ozi ma ọ bụ inye onyinye&nbsp;, a ga-arịọ gị ka ịnye (ma ọ dịkarịa ala) aha gị na ozi ịkwụ ụgwọ gụnyere ozi kaadị ịkwụ ụgwọ (\"&nbsp;<em>Ozi Ịkwụ Ụgwọ&nbsp;</em>\"). Onye na-ahụ maka ọrụ ndị ọzọ na-ahụ maka ịkwụ ụgwọ maka anyị ga-anatakwa ozi kaadị ịkwụ ụgwọ gị.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Ozi ị na-ahọrọ inye anyị: Ị nwere ike ịnye ozi dị iche iche n\'oge mmekọrịta gị na anyị yana onye enyemaka Kaci Automated &amp; App, dị ka ozi ịntanetị ị nwere ike iziga anyị, ozi ị zara, na ozi-e ma ọ bụ akwụkwọ akụkọ. nke ị debanyere aha iji nweta. Onye enyemaka Kaci Automated &amp; App ma ọ bụ ndị ọzọ na-anọchite anya anyị na-enweta data n\'aka gị mgbe ọ bụla ị nyere anyị ozi.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Ozi kọntaktị: Ọ bụrụ na ị họrọ isonye na ọmụmụ nyocha, ma ọ bụ debanye aha maka ụfọdụ atụmatụ, ị nwere ike ịnye anyị, anyị nwere ike ịnakọta ozi kọntaktị gị, gụnyere aha gị, adreesị ozi-e, na nọmba ekwentị gị (\"Kpọtụrụ Ozi\" ).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;De-achọpụtara data. Anyị na-eji data akọwapụtaghị maka nyocha na mmepe nke ngwaahịa ma ọ bụ ngwaọrụ ọhụrụ, iji mezie algọridim anyị na ngwa mmụta igwe, yana kwalite ngwa na ọrụ anyị na-enye. Anyị nwere ike ikpughere ụdị ozi a n\'ihu ọha yana ndị ọzọ, dịka ọmụmaatụ, na akụkọ ọha gbasara ahụike, nye ndị mmekọ n\'okpuru nkwekọrịta anyị na anyị, ma ọ bụ na ozi benchmarking anyị na-enye obodo ahụike.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3&nbsp;Ozi Anyị na-enweta n\'aka ndị ọzọ</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Akaụntụ Mgbasa Ozi Ọha: Anyị nwere ike nweta ozi nkeonwe gbasara gị&nbsp;site na ngwa mkpanaaka, ma ọ bụ&nbsp;ọrụ mgbasa ozi mmekọrịta ndị ọzọ, dị ka Facebook na Twitter, ma ọ bụrụ na ịhọrọ ijikọ ọrụ anyị na akaụntụ mgbasa ozi mmekọrịta nke ndị ọzọ (“Akaụntụ Social Media). ”) site na nke ọ bụla: (i) ịnye anyị ozi nbanye akaụntụ Social Media gị site na Ọrụ; ma ọ bụ (ii) na-enye anyị ohere ịnweta Akaụntụ Mgbasa Ozi Ọha na-elekọta mmadụ, dị ka enyere ikike n\'okpuru usoro na ọnọdụ dị mkpa na-achịkwa ojiji nke Akaụntụ Social Media dị iche iche.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4&nbsp;Ozi anyị na-anakọta site na teknụzụ</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a)&nbsp;Arụmọrụ na ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka na-akpaghị aka na webụsaịtị anyị: Anyị nwere ike idobe ụfọdụ omume ị na-eme na ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka akpaaka na webụsaịtị anyị, dị ka ọdịnaya ọchụchọ ị na-eme site na ngwa Mobile ma ọ bụ na&nbsp;ya&nbsp;. ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka na-akpaghị aka na webụsaịtị anyị.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b)&nbsp;Ịnweta ozi ngwaọrụ na ihe nchọgharị: Mgbe ịbanye na ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka na-akpaghị aka na webụsaịtị anyị site na kọmpụta ma ọ bụ ngwaọrụ ọzọ, anyị nwere ike ịnakọta ozi na-amaghị aha na ngwaọrụ ahụ, dị ka adreesị protocol ịntanetị gị, ụdị ihe nchọgharị, ọsọ njikọ na ịnweta. ugboro (mkpokọta, \"Anonymous Ozi\").</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c)&nbsp;Kuki: Anyị nwere ike iji kuki nnọkọ abụọ ahụ (nke na-agwụ ozugbo imechi ihe nchọgharị weebụ gị) yana kuki na-adịgide adịgide iji mee ka ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka na-akpaghị aka na webụsaịtị na Ọrụ anyị dị mfe iji, iji mee ka mgbasa ozi anyị ka mma, yana iji chebe ha abụọ. gi na onye enyemaka Kaci Automated &amp; App. Ị nwere ike ịkụziri ihe nchọgharị gị, site n\'ịgbanwe nhọrọ ya, kwụsị ịnakwere kuki ma ọ bụ kpalie gị tupu ịnakwere kuki site na weebụsaịtị ị gara. Ọ bụrụ na ịnaghị anabata kuki, agbanyeghị, ị gaghị enwe ike ịbanye na ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka akpaaka na webụsaịtị anyị. Anyị nwekwara ike iji Pixels mee ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka akpaaka yana webụsaịtị na ọrụ anyị dị mfe iji yana mee ka mgbasa ozi anyị ka mma site na ọmụmaatụ, ichikota ụkpụrụ ojiji. Ugbu a, anyị anaghị asọpụrụ arịrịọ \"Esochiela\" n\'akụkụ niile nke saịtị anyị.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d)&nbsp;Ebe ezigbo oge: ụfọdụ atụmatụ nke ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka na-akpaghị aka na webụsaịtị anyị na-eji teknụzụ GPS na-anakọta ozi ozugbo gbasara ọnọdụ ngwaọrụ gị ka ngwa ahụ, onye enyemaka akpaghị aka na webụsaịtị anyị nwee ike jikọọ gị na nchekwa&nbsp;. Agency, Ọrụ&nbsp;ndị ọkachamara ahụike ma ọ bụ ụgbọ ihe mberede&nbsp;ọrụ&nbsp;nke&nbsp;ich&nbsp;enyere&nbsp;ikike ma ọ bụ ikike ịnye ọrụ na mpaghara ma ọ bụ ikike ebe ị nọ. Mgbe ị na-enweta ọrụ Google Maps na saịtị anyị, ị na-ekwenye na&nbsp;<u>Usoro Ọrụ&nbsp;</u>na&nbsp;<u>Amụma Nzuzo&nbsp;</u>Google .</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e)&nbsp;Ọrụ mkpanaaka: Anyị nwere ike ịnakọta ozi na-abụghị nkeonwe site na ekwentị mkpanaaka ma ọ bụ kọmputa gị. A na-ejikarị ozi a enyere anyị aka ibugara gị ozi kachasị mkpa. Ọmụmaatụ nke ozi enwere ike ịnakọta ma jiri ya gụnyere otu i si eji&nbsp;ngwa Kaci, o&nbsp;the&nbsp;r&nbsp;application na ozi gbasara ụdị ngwaọrụ ma ọ bụ kọmputa ị na-eji. Na mgbakwunye, ọ bụrụ na ngwa (s) anyị daa na ekwentị mkpanaaka gị, anyị ga-enweta ozi gbasara ụdị sọftụwia ngwaọrụ mkpanaka gị yana onye na-ebu ngwaọrụ, nke na-enye anyị ohere ịchọpụta na idozi ahụhụ yana ma melite arụmọrụ nke ngwa anyị. .</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3.&nbsp;Otu anyị si eji ozi anyị na-anata ma ọ bụ na-anakọta</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1&nbsp;N\'ozuzu, onye enyemaka Kaci Automated &amp; App na-eji ozi anyị na-anakọta maka ebumnuche ndị a:</div><ul><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Iji rụọ ọrụ, nye, jikwaa, melite ma kwalite ọrụ anyị;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Iji ghọta na nyochaa otu i si eji Ọrụ anyị na ịmepụta ngwaahịa, ọrụ, atụmatụ na arụmọrụ ọhụrụ;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Iji hazie ahụmịhe gị na ọrụ anyị, dị ka ịnye ọdịnaya ahaziri. Dịka ọmụmaatụ, anyị na-eji adreesị ozi-e gị iji nyere gị aka ịmepụta, banye na jikwaa akaụntụ gị na Ọrụ anyị. Nke a na-ahapụ anyị ka anyị hazie ahụmịhe gị wee nye gị ozi dabara adaba. Ọ na-enyekwa njirimara ndị na-enyere gị aka ịghọta nke ọma, soro na soro ahụike gị na iji gosi gị ozi ahaziri ahazi;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Maka ebumnuche ịzụ ahịa na mgbasa ozi, dị ka ịmepụta na ịnye ihe nkwado na mgbasa ozi nwere ike ịbara gị uru, bara uru ma ọ bụ ihe ọzọ masịrị gị. Anyị nwekwara ike iji ozi anyị mụtara gbasara gị nyere anyị aka n\'ịkpọsa ọrụ anyị na webụsaịtị ndị ọzọ. Ebe achọrọ n\'okpuru iwu dị, anyị ga-ezitere gị ozi mgbasa ozi naanị site na nkwenye gị;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ka gị na gị kparịta ụka site na ozi-e, ozi ederede, ọkwa ntanye na oku ekwentị, iji nye gị mmelite na ozi ndị ọzọ metụtara Ọrụ anyị, nye ozi nke ị rịọrọ, zaa ajụjụ na ajụjụ, ma ọ bụghị nye nkwado ndị ahịa;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Iji kwado azụmahịa na ịkwụ ụgwọ;</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ka ikwado njikọ nke Social Media Akaụntụ na Ọrụ anyị iji nye ozi sitere na Akaụntụ Mgbasa Ozi na Profaịlụ gị. Dabere na Akaụntụ Social Media ị họọrọ ma dabere na ntọala nzuzo ị debere na akaụntụ Social Media dị otú ahụ, anyị ga- enweta ozi ahụ, mee ka ọ dị ma chekwaa (ọ bụrụ na ọdabara yana dịka ndị ọrụ mgbasa ozi kwadoro yana